\id MAT - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Matthew 1 20/3/91 Macnaughtan
\h MAęž‰TIU
\toc1 Maęž‰tiumaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\toc2 Maęž‰tiu
\toc3 Maęž‰tiu
\mt1 Maęž‰tiumaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\c 1
\s1 Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ bikimanu
\r (Luku 3ęž‰23-28)
\p 
\v 1 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ bikimanu wape paęž‰laęž‰ekie. Deipiditaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ meiyeke hayekeme. Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ meiyeke hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 2 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Diuda hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 3 Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ Petese pitaęž‰ Seta yaapo mondu wiekeme. Ipilikaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Tama.
\q1 Petesemaęž‰taęž‰ Hesotono mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Hesotonomaęž‰taęž‰ Laęž‰mi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 4 Laęž‰mimaęž‰taęž‰ Aminaęž‰daęž‰be mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Aminaęž‰daęž‰bemaęž‰taęž‰ Naęž‰sioni mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Naęž‰sionimaęž‰taęž‰ Saęž‰limoni mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 5 Saęž‰limonimaęž‰taęž‰ Boaęž‰si mondu wiekeme. Boaęž‰sinaęž‰ amaęž‰taęž‰ Leihaęž‰pe hayekeme.
\q1 Boaęž‰simaęž‰taęž‰ Obedi mondu wiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰taęž‰ Luti hayekeme.
\q1 Obedimaęž‰taęž‰ Diesi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 6 Diesimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kini halo pieke hali Deipidi mondu wiekeme.
\b
\q1 Deipidimaęž‰taęž‰ Solomono mondu wiekeme. Koto Solomono ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ Yutaeyamaęž‰ miekeme.
\q1 
\v 7 Solomonomaęž‰taęž‰ Leoboeme mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Leoboememaęž‰taęž‰ Abidia mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Abidiamaęž‰taęž‰ Asa mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 8 Asamaęž‰taęž‰ Diaęž‰hosapaęž‰ti mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Diaęž‰hosapaęž‰timaęž‰taęž‰ Diehotami mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Diehotamimaęž‰taęž‰ Asaiya mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 9 Asaiyamaęž‰taęž‰ Diotaęž‰mi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Diotaęž‰mimaęž‰taęž‰ Eihaęž‰si mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Eihaęž‰simaęž‰taęž‰ Hesikaiyaęž‰ mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 10 Hesikaiyaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰se mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Maęž‰naęž‰semaęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰mono mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Aęž‰monomaęž‰taęž‰ Diosaiya mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 11 Diosaiyamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Isulai wandaęž‰hali Baęž‰biloni dipula hatuku peme natenaęž‰taęž‰ Diaęž‰hoyaęž‰kini hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ mondu wiekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 12 Baęž‰biloni nane hataęž‰taęž‰ Diaęž‰hoyaęž‰kinimaęž‰taęž‰ Sieletieli mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Sieletielimaęž‰taęž‰ Setubabele mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 13 Setubabelemaęž‰taęž‰ Abiudi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Abiudimaęž‰taęž‰ Eliakimi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Eliakimimaęž‰taęž‰ Aso mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 14 Asomaęž‰taęž‰ Saęž‰doki mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Saęž‰dokimaęž‰taęž‰ Akimi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Akimimaęž‰taęž‰ Eliudi mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 15 Eliudimaęž‰taęž‰ Eliasa mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Eliasamaęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰tani mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Maęž‰tanimaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 16 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Meti mieke hali Diosepe mondu wiekeme.
\q1 Metimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Yesu biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Ketiso lo pieke hali mondu wiekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ kini pu mea pua Deipidimaęž‰ tombo wia koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke apaęž‰meitaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ tonkopu haemekeme. Deipidimaęž‰ kini pu mea pua Baęž‰biloni pemeke ekimaęž‰ tombo wia koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke apaęž‰meitaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ tonkopu haemekeme. Kutaa make mo Baęž‰biloni pemeke ekimaęž‰ kini pu mea pua Ketisomaęž‰ tombo wia koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke apaęž‰meitaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ tonkopu ombu haemekeme.
\s1 Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Luku 2ęž‰1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ Metitaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ tome wandiki hayekepate ipikaęž‰ da aĚ±iĚ± na peke hataęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ pitayeke weki mendiaęž‰peke yekeeki hando wiekeme.
\v 19 Diosepe epeke hali yaalo mo Meti yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ hone na wieke handaa ipilikaęž‰ tome haepekeeki aęž‰mbao minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke hone wiekeme.
\v 20 Diosepemaęž‰ koto piki honemanu witolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ timba maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ upa paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo homeke opolo aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ weki Diosepeo. Meti nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo weki pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kone peawalaęž‰me.
\v 21 Mo wekitaęž‰ hali weki mendilieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea daęž‰taalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki Yesue lelipipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Meti paęž‰taęž‰ do haumanu peayeke ekitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potopede hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimanu paeyao peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ yeke piekeme.
\v 23 Mo potopede halimaęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Mo halimaęž‰ na watake wandikinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ weki weleke lombaataęž‰ hali weki mendilieke. Koto wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Imanuaęž‰le lelieke leekeme. Koto bikinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 24 Diosepe tiaotaęž‰ mo hande enisolomaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ miekeme.
\v 25 Kutu piekepate mo weki pa pitaęž‰ paleke haenaęž‰taęž‰ loke na apaęž‰taepekeme. Mo weki hambaęž‰ mieketaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Yesue leekeme.
\c 2
\s1 Nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane haemeke kimisu haliweki
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande Hetodi kini hayeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Diudia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke da Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ nane mendiekeme. Hosiki hao hoki nanetaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ yataęž‰pu haemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ yamaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane aęž‰pa
\v 2 lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini halo paęž‰laęž‰ panake weki maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ wekitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe. Ipikaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ opeeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ epomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 3 Kini Hetodimaęž‰ koto lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipiki make mo Diutuseleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ make penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 4 Hetodimaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make mandane pi ulaęž‰eki walo halaęž‰ haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea mombaęž‰laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo Ketisotaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mendiliaęž‰pe laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 5 Mo hande Diudia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ daoni Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mendilieke laa hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo ambaęž‰ haemeke potopede haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ dupa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 6 Diudia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ daoni Betelehaęž‰maęž‰o. Neketaęž‰ mo Diudianaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ daoni manunaęž‰ hoki nane na haleme.
\q1 Pa ekipeke. Neke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo You hali homeke ya Isulai wandaęž‰hali handeteke hawaluekemaęž‰ ipilieke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ mo hombulankaęž‰ otaęž‰ kini pea opeeke nate weiluekemaęž‰ mo hande nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ epemeke kimisu haliweki aęž‰mbao wi laęž‰ mea pi hotimikime.
\v 8 Ikaęž‰ pimanu opuaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande weki yopu siki weilu pupe la alotaęž‰ Mo weki handaęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ pulu puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa la kiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 9-10 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opuaa Diutuseleme minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hande handemeke hombulankaęž‰ kone paa handemekeme. Koto hande hombulankaęž‰ paa handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu homemekeme. Mo hombulankaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popeleke nanemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± puaataęž‰ mo weki wia pitieke da holu manda handaęž‰niao hayekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pieke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua mo wekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki Metimaęž‰ wia pitiekeeki handaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ tumiki yotuao pandaęž‰ puniao pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laemekeme. Kutu polo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰ mendimiki yenki tieke alemanu kolo make mo lankaęž‰ yankeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ totopopiki lumu opaęž‰laęž‰ lankaęž‰ siki make mo totopo yolepiki ti pankeke ale make toku mea ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halemekeme.
\v 12 Kutaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ paa na puaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leeke handataęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ pakaęž‰lao ikaęž‰ da yu nane laęž‰kaęž‰la pemeekeme.
\s1 Idiepi nane pindipa pemekeeki
\p 
\v 13 Mo hande kimisu haliweki pemeke hoki nanetaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ upanaęž‰ walolo alotaęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ mo wekisiki luluekemaęž‰ weilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ tiao mo weki ankulaęž‰ hatuku mea Idiepi nane pindipa pua IĚ±maęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaęž‰paęž‰peke lolo poloeki handeteke hapaęž‰peke.
\v 14 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ tiao ipikaęž‰ weki ankulaęž‰ hatuku mea koto timba kone mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao Idiepi nane pemekeme.
\v 15 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ Hetodi homenaęž‰ yeke yu wia haemekeme. Kutu pimiki ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potopede hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Ya wekio. Idiepi kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao epoe laa laęž‰ uaęž‰ pi yaaluekemaęž‰ piekeme.
\s1 Wekiwandiki liaęž‰peke pi
\p 
\v 16 Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane hao epemeke kimisu hali wekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki makeao pemekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mineke tieke pankeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰ make nepoko nepoko haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ bapi yaapo lombei na piki wekitonu paeyao homenaęž‰ lu paeyaapaęž‰peke laa laęž‰ wiekeme. Mo hande kimisu haliwekimaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ opeeke nate ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeeki Hetodimaęž‰ hone puaataęž‰ dupiki wekitonu homeke liaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 17 Do hau paeyao pieke ekitaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ potopede Dietemaiyamaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki yaeyekeme. Koto ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 
\v 18 Mo Lama kenke nanetaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make maęž‰ndaęž‰ opitelememe.
\q1 Wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke alaęž‰me.
\q1 Leisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ eĚ± tieke alaęž‰me.
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki paeyao homemeke handaa wandaęž‰weki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰tiao tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ lapeketaęž‰ kiaasaęž‰me laa leekeme.
\s1 Idiepi minaęž‰paęž‰lao paa epemekeeki
\p 
\v 19 Mo hande Kini Hetodi homeekeeki hoki nanetaęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pa haenaęž‰ mo enisolo homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ upa paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa alotaęž‰
\v 20 Mo hande weki luluekemaęž‰ taapeme haliwekitaęž‰ homememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ neketaęž‰ tiao mo weki ankulaęž‰ hatuku Idiepi minaęž‰paęž‰lao Isulai kenke nane paa puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 21 Koto leeke Diosepemaęž‰ tiao mo weki ankulaęž‰ hatuku mea minaęž‰ Isulai kenke nane pemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Pate Akelosimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke Hetodi mo Diudia kenke Kini halinaęž‰ anketeke maęž‰laęž‰me pi Diosepemaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ koto kenke nane puaęž‰peke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ upa paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki mandaneeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa waleekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili kenke nane hayeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰
\v 23 Naęž‰saęž‰tete halo pemekeme. Koto halo pemeke ekitaęž‰ mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki yaeyekeme. Koto ikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki dupa Ipikitaęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali halaęž‰me lelieke leekeme.
\c 3
\s1 Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰1-18, Luku 3ęž‰1-18, Dioni 1ęž‰19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ mo Diudianaęž‰ hapiki kenke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ pi kini pea walolo alotaęž‰
\v 2 Mo hande hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao hoki walaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 3 Do Dioni paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeme. Koto laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ dupa.
\q1 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo hapiki kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pi takaęž‰lake lo halaęž‰me.
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ potaęž‰ pilaowapaęž‰peke.
\q1 Ipiki epeke alenaęž‰ yapenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ wopu tikitiki yawapaęž‰peke alaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Dioni ipikaęž‰ yameeke dautaęž‰ mo kemolo itikimaęž‰ wepiki dau yameekeme. Ipikaęž‰ hakotaęž‰ kao yonkeleke wepiki hako yameekeme. Ipikaęž‰ ne manutaęž‰ odouwamanu make mo pole pukini hapeke hanimanu make no hayekeme.
\v 5 Mo Diutuseleme da wandaęž‰hali make Diudia kenke wandaęž‰hali make mo Diodani ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ pelia peeke wandaęž‰hali make otaęž‰ paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tayaemekeme.
\v 6 Kutupataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu kaęž‰laęž‰polo liaenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ mo Diodani ikali paęž‰taęž‰ bapitaisi peayekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi tapake make Saęž‰dusi tapake make koto tapake yaaponaęž‰ haliweki wopu Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaenaęž‰ epemekeeki handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ketomaęž‰ handeke some hombo iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± taapolo paęž‰laęž‰ panisi tieke wendiaęž‰pekee pitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ lakiaęž‰pe.
\v 8 Mo ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu hoki walaa otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laaseme hau peneme yaasaęž‰ ekimanu homeke pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 9 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ meie lomekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ wendulumekee hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Lono opie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do ulaęž‰ toopimanu mea Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki au lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me alome.
\v 10 Mo timanu ikaęž‰ teke yokaęž‰ pokaęž‰ bepe peaapeke teitaęž‰ do tikitiki yao ulaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ti homeke homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke kiliki na eiyo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pokaa tinaęž‰ yankilieke.
\p 
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu minaęž‰paęž‰laemekeeki peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaowalopate mo ya hoki nane ipiliaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi pitaęž‰ ti talaęž‰eki yaapomaęž‰ iki bapitaisi pealieke. Mo sometaęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ lombeipiki some halekenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke dake kone IĚ±maęž‰ mea tiaapeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 12 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande widi kilikinaęž‰ ambuku napeke yaapo putupa alu puluekemaęž‰ panaęž‰pulu paęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰sataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ miniki halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ widi kiliki epekeeki paeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ widi napeke u halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la wilieke. Pate mo ambuku paeyaotaęž‰ tinaęž‰ panaęž‰pu yankilieke. Koto titaęž‰ na paeyeke pa to halieke. Koto pi manutaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ leekeme.
\s1 Yesu bapitaisi peayekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰9-11, Luku 3ęž‰21-22)
\p 
\v 13 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Yesu mo Kaęž‰lili kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao Dionimaęž‰ ipiki bapitaisi peaenaęž‰ mo Diodani ikali paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme.
\v 14 Kutu piekepate Yesunaęž‰ hone topo pinaęž‰yeke Dionimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± bapitaisi peapekealeo. Pa neketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ bapitaisi peano IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epekaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\v 15 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pinaęž‰maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki. Do pulu polopaęž‰ hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ pitolo pitolopaęž‰me. Koto leekeeki Dionimaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me bapitaisi peanoe leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Yesu bapitaisi peao paeyeketaęž‰ koto kone mo ikali minaęž‰paęž‰lao teaęž‰ nane yapeekeme. Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone oli ya akolopa wiaataęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi melipu tupaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao ipikaęž‰ loke manda tapepeekeeki handeekeme.
\v 17 Kutaa oli ya nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make homekemaęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ ya pukipiki wekie. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolome laa pi laęž‰niaeyekeme.
\c 4
\s1 Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu la handeeke ekimanu
\r (Maka 1ęž‰12-13, Luku 4ęž‰1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Koto pieke hoki nanetaęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu la handenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ Yesu mo hapu hayeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku peekeme.
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hali tieke yaapo natenaęž‰ timbaęž‰ nate yaaponaęž‰ ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ na neke hayeke ekimaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 3 Koto teaęž‰maęž‰ homolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do toopimanu kone palaowa au lapeke leekeme.
\v 4 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolomaęž‰taęž‰ Halimaęž‰ palaowa homeke naa na hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi paeyao miniki halie ekimaęž‰ homeke epeke tupaęž‰ halieke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutaataęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu mo yako piki daoni Diutuseleme nane hatuku peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo tembolo da holu manda mea hao hataęž‰
\v 6 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ hao oni kenkenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone lopaęž‰niae. Pa ekipeke. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo enisolo tonumaęž‰ neke handeteke haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi lelieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo toopi manumaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke naapaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo enisolotonu ikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ neke miniliao handeteke halimikie laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 7 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ alepate mo Baibolomaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Tekehali nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ la handaęž‰laęž‰eki na piaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto leeketaęž‰ mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu pa hatuku pote tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ manda hatuku puaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke paeyaonaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki make ikaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki au epeke epeke make waleekeme.
\v 9 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tumiki yotuao pandaęž‰puniao pitaęž‰ yeni pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto handele ale paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke Sadanimaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 10 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Sadani neke puma. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homeke homo hapaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Koto pi leeketaęž‰ mo Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ enisolo tonumaęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ epemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane hataęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰14-15, Luku 4ęž‰14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Dioni dipula mea pitaeyekeeki opuaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Kaęž‰lili nane peekeme.
\v 13 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete da na hao hake mo ikali leke Kaęž‰lili teaęž‰ nane hayeke da homeke bikitaęž‰ Kapeneami halo peekeme. Koto dataęž‰ mo Sebuloni kenke pitaęž‰ Naęž‰petali kenke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 14 Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki yaaluekemaęž‰ piekeme. Koto laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 
\v 15 Mo Diodani ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ mo ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pulaęž‰ potaęž‰ ulaęž‰ Sebuloni kenkeo o Naęž‰petali kenkeo mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke Kaęž‰lilio
\q1 
\v 16 mo timbaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ hao haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke handilimikie.
\q1 Mo homo halaęž‰ timbaęž‰ leke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaalieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Koto tomonaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi walolotaęž‰ dupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu hoki walaa laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰peke lo hayekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ tonkopu hali wi leekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰16-20, Luku 5ęž‰1-11)
\p 
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande Kaęž‰lili ikali leke hounaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰peli mu haepeke hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ yaapo Saimono biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Pida make hameke Aęž‰ndutu yaapomaęž‰ mo hande ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ tenki nunaęž‰ taęž‰peli minolo haepekeeki handeekeme.
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mu hapenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ walaęž‰tialuekemaęž‰ ya hoki nane teli mea ipupe leekeme.
\v 20 Koto leeketaęž‰ koto kone ipilikaęž‰ tenki numanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipiki teli mea pepekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Mo pate leke pulu hataęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Dioni yaapo handeekeme. Ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ Sepedie. Ipilikitaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± kawaso manda pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tenki numanu epeaaso pitimikime. Kutu polo pitinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki wi leekeme.
\v 22 Kutu pieketaęž‰ koto kone ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰ make mo kawaso make minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesu teli mea pepekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰hali wamo pu pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo
\r (Luku 6ęž‰17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapomanu walolo hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki yeni ki paeyao wamo peayekeme.
\v 24 Koto ipikaęž‰ pieke hau manunaęž‰taęž‰ Sitia kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ kende tupaęž‰ wiekeme. Koto pi opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yeni taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ hake tanda mu haemeke wandaęž‰hali make hoke temokomanu pitu make lu keaaso hataęž‰ lopo haemeke wandaęž‰hali make kiki anke lupa wiki wandaęž‰hali make otaęž‰ paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea epemekeme.
\v 25 Wandaęž‰hali wopu Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ teli mea pemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili kenke nanemaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make Diudia kenke nanemaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make mo Diodani mone teaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make iki paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki teli mea pemekeme.
\c 5
\s1 Potenaęž‰ hataęž‰ waleeke pi
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ mo mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali handaataęž‰ oli peiyene aęž‰meiya pua pitiekeme. Kutu pinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki aęž‰pa ipiki hopaęž‰liao haemeketaęž‰
\v 2 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi kini pu mea walolo alotaęž‰
\s1 Otaęž‰ epeke taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰20-23)
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Mandane wandaęž‰hali epi ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ Ya temoko teketaęž‰ natehali halome hone u haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekie.
\q1 
\v 4 Mo eĚ± tapu tapu hataęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Ikaęž‰ pukitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaalieke.
\q1 
\v 5 Homu pea hao haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ milimikie.
\q1 
\v 6 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ anaęž‰ lawaalieke.
\q1 
\v 7 Mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homilieke.
\q1 
\v 8 Ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na talenaęž‰ leke wamo pea haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ handilimikie.
\q1 
\v 9 Aęž‰ndaęž‰ ape kakeneli homao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Ya wekiwandikie lelieke.
\q1 
\v 10 Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki peaaseme ekinaęž‰ kone mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tandamanu halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\q1 kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halememe.
\q1 Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekie.
\p 
\v 11 Ikitaęž‰ ya hoki nane tolu haleme ekinaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ iki yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homao make iki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda ku make ikaęž‰ biki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ hoke baęž‰saęž‰ pitolo yayapiki pimanu saęž‰mbaęž‰lao pitolo haenaęž‰ kone kotaęž‰
\v 12 pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa epeke puki haaso hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ mulu peleme yenki tieketaęž‰ oli hepeni nane wiawalaęž‰me. Do iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ tanda tupaęž‰ kone mo hande ambaęž‰ haemeke potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make tanda halo haemekeme.
\s1 Epi pitaęž‰ PaĚ±aĚ± yaapo
\r (Maka 9ęž‰50, Luku 14ęž‰34-35)
\p 
\v 13 Ikitaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ epi halememe. Koto pelemepate mo epinaęž‰ tende paęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ alu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo epinaęž‰ tende paa peaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo tende alu paęž‰laęž‰ epitaęž‰ pa alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ bao wandaęž‰hali ankemaęž‰ tumba tumba pea pomu halimikie.
\v 14 Ikitaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± halememe. Mo peiyene elininaęž‰ halaęž‰ daonitaęž‰ aęž‰mbao hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 15 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake kaęž‰wataęž‰ mo disi kawaso tiekemaęž‰ aęž‰mbao na wilieke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaenaęž‰ mo teipolo manda wilieke.
\v 16 Koto tupaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke haumanu handolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lawaenaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ handenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peapeke haumanu pu hapaęž‰peke.
\s1 Pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\p 
\v 17 Mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ Pi Ulaęž‰ ekimanu make o Potopede haliwekimaęž‰ walemeke pimanu make paeyaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto ikaęž‰ walemeke manaęž‰ pimanu paeyaaluekemaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰pate pa yawaluekemaęž‰ epolome.
\v 18 Otaęž‰ pi alome. Oli hepeni do kenke yaapo aĚ±iĚ± na paeke pa ulaęž‰ tomonaęž‰taęž‰ mo Mosesimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pi ulaęž‰eki wape pea ulaęž‰ pi homeke siki make o tombo hodikali siki make maęž‰ndaęž‰ ambaęž‰la otaęž‰ na alu pilieke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ do kenke ya yaapo paeliaęž‰ natenaęž‰ mandake paeyaenaęž‰ pa wilieke.
\v 19 Kutu piliepate pa hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lo Pi Ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hosiki pi siki kone yokaęž‰ mea bao make o mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make kutu pinaęž‰ walaęž‰ tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ oli hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hosiki siki yaęž‰lieke. Pate pa hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lo Pi Ulaęž‰eki miniki hataęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make kutu pinaęž‰ walaęž‰ tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ biki tieke milieke.
\v 20 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikaęž‰ haunaęž‰ tikitiki paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ mo Lo Pi Ulaęž‰eki walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰eki make otaęž‰ lombei na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yelimikie.
\s1 Mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\p 
\v 21 Ambaęž‰ hande ikaęž‰ mei tonu paęž‰taęž‰ la haleeke yeke opu haleme pitaęž‰ dupa. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na lu homaapeke. Lu homaekenaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea halieke leekepate
\v 22 Pa ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lelieke. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dopi taapeke ekie leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ KaĚ±leĚ±sete tieke paęž‰taęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lelieke. Kutaa make maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ you hoke hone wopu na wiki someo leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki teke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰pekeeki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ oloda paęž‰taęž‰ mea ipulu hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ Ya kamemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alaęž‰me hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 24 kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mo pa hameke halaęž‰pekeeki koto paęž‰taęž‰ kone minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ koto kone aĚ±iĚ± laęž‰kaęž‰la pua nakaęž‰ kame yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa mo nakaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰pekeeki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 25 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke yaapo pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ hatuku peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ kone ipiki yaapo koto kone tikitiki yao epeapaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ mo pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ halieke. Kutaa mo you halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo polisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ neke halieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo polisi haliwekimaęž‰ neke dipula mea pitalieke.
\v 26 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pu haunaęž‰ yenki paeyao otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na halekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa pitu halipikie.
\s1 Tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wimiki pi opu haleme pitaęž‰ dupa. Tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau na peaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 28 Pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Hali epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ handolo ipikaęž‰taęž‰ ya meawee la honemaęž‰ we pambeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ hakopu ambaęž‰ tunkululaęž‰me.
\v 29 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ popeke nane lekemaęž‰ neke hoke hau puelenaęž‰ yeke neke yoleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto leke yokaa baapeke. Pa ekipeke. Nakaęž‰ loke tieke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ puaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ lokesiki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ alupao haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epilieke.
\v 30 Kutaa make nakaęž‰ popeke kikimaęž‰ neke hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kikitaęž‰ tunkulu baapeke. Pa ekipeke. Nakaęž‰ loke tieke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ puaamaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ paleke homeke alupao haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epilieke.
\s1 Tooli kiaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰9, Maka 10ęž‰11-12, Luku 16ęž‰18)
\p 
\v 31 Mo ambaęž‰ pi wieke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make leeke pitaęž‰ dupa. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kiao otaęž‰ baalueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ baasome pi wape paęž‰laęž‰ wape miniki haenaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 32 Pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ hali na yolo haliaęž‰pate pa hameke kone kiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰maęž‰ wetepe hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo kiao baeyaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hali yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau pinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ hali halaęž‰me. Kutaa mo koto wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali make yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau kone pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Pi laęž‰ witolo hali keke witaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\p 
\v 33 Ambaęž‰ hande ikaęž‰ meitonu paęž‰taęž‰ la haleeke yeke opu haleme pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa. Nakaęž‰ laęž‰ wili pi na yambeleketaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hali keke witolo laęž‰ wilieki paeyao otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 34 Pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hali keke witolo pimanu apaęž‰tao na laęž‰ wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa mo Hepeninaęž‰ biki laa hali keke witaęž‰laęž‰ pi na lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Hepenitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitu halaęž‰ ale yeleke loaęž‰me.
\v 35 Do kekenaęž‰ biki lo make na lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Do kenketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ anke ulaęž‰ ale yeleke loaęž‰me. Mo hande Diutuseleme lo make na lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo dataęž‰ mo Kini tiekenaęž‰ daoni yeleke loaęž‰me.
\v 36 Ikaęž‰ you lo kone otaęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ itiki homeke siki kone topo pea hake o punu na peapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 37 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa Aowe o Diaęž‰me homeke lapaęž‰peke. Mandane pi apaęž‰taemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ hoke Sadanimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ pie.
\s1 Hoke ekimaęž‰ hombo peaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰29-30)
\p 
\v 38 Ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wimiki pi opu haleme pitaęž‰ dupa. Leke hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ paa leke hoeyapaęž‰peke. Kake hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ paa kake hoeyapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 39 Pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke tekipuleke laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo na peapeke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ popeke nanemaęž‰ pakenaęž‰ dakapomaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hoe nane pakenaęž‰ make linaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰lapeke.
\v 40 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ sedi muluekemaęž‰ neke pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kosaęž‰ akaęž‰ make minaęž‰ halaęž‰peke.
\v 41 Handeteke halaęž‰ hali tieke homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hakoto mea tia polenaęž‰e alo hataęž‰ potaęž‰ tombo dupanaęž‰ tia puaęž‰peke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki hakaęž‰taęž‰pao tia puaęž‰peke.
\v 42 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke. Kutupa make nakaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ taęž‰kaęž‰li kie leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa taęž‰kaęž‰li halaęž‰peke.
\s1 Aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰27-28,32-36)
\p 
\v 43 Ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wimiki pi opu haleme pitaęž‰ dupa. Tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolotaęž‰ tunkuliki halitaęž‰ honditi piaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 44 Pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo make mo iki tanda kiteme wandaęž‰hali epeaenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 45 Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke tonu halimikie. Pa ekipeke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ natenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ mo hoke wandaęž‰hali epeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandake piki nate paĚ±aĚ± kone peaasaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo epeke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lako iki paeyao mandake tupaęž‰ kone anaęž‰naęž‰ halo halaęž‰me.
\v 46 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke yenki kinaęž‰pe. Mo hande dakisi mu halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ kone kutu piki hau pu halememe.
\v 47 Ikaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni paęž‰taęž‰manu homeke mo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu lo haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitolomaęž‰me laa hone witelemepe. Diaęž‰me. Mo pi na miki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone kutu piki hau pu halememe.
\v 48 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tondepe wopu pea halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make tondepe pea hao hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 6
\s1 Diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi miniki haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu peaęž‰pekeeki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰ handaenaęž‰ tupaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ hone otaęž‰ na wiki yopu kone peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰yeke handaenaęž‰ hau pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mulu peleme epeke yenkitaęž‰ homeke siki aęž‰ndaęž‰ make otaęž‰ na milimikie.
\p 
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande natehali wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ walaęž‰ walaęž‰ pea na halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo hande yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ oni hande potaęž‰ hopiki ninaęž‰ make yeni da paęž‰taęž‰manu make kutu piki walaęž‰ walaęž‰ piki haumanu pu halememe. Koto hau pimiki ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰ yeke pu halememe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Koto tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi haunaęž‰ yenki manutaęž‰ ame do hataęž‰ mu paeyaasememe.
\v 3 Mo natehali wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ eki sikimaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ na handenaęž‰ leke halaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 4 Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ mone honemaęž‰ aęž‰mbao hataęž‰ halaęž‰paęž‰peke alee. Kutaa make mo ikaęž‰ mone honemaęž‰ piteme hau handaęž‰laęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke yenki kilieke.
\s1 Yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu waleekeeki
\r (Luku 11ęž‰2-4)
\p 
\v 5 Yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekinaęž‰ hau na hondaęž‰paęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki handenaęž‰ hone hone witolo hataęž‰ mandane potaęž‰ hopiki ninaęž‰ make yeni da paęž‰taęž‰manu make tialiao hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu halememe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi haunaęž‰ yenki manutaęž‰ ame do hataęž‰ mu paeyaasememe.
\v 6 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ pokaęž‰neao pua pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yeke Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ mone honemaęž‰ piteme hau handaęž‰laęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke yenki kilieke.
\p 
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande yayapiki kodaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ napeke na pitiki pi eleke eleke wopu lo haleme tupaęž‰ yeni na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ yeni hokulu peaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ opilieke hone witelememe.
\v 8 Ikitaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali leke na hapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ honke aĚ±iĚ± na leke hamenaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ handa hone ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9 Yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\q1 Nikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰o.
\q1 Nakaęž‰ yako piki bikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ manda wia haenaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 10 Nakaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Haleeki do ane opolo epenaęž‰e.
\q1 Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki oli hepeni nane peao haleme tupaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ make peawaenae.
\q1 
\v 11 Do ame nolo polomaęž‰ ne anaęž‰naęž‰ kiaęž‰peke.
\q1 
\v 12 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pimi ekimanu nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaaso hamono nikaęž‰ hoke hau pumaęž‰ ekimanu make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ pa paeyawapeke.
\q1 
\v 13 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki ekimaęž‰ niki na la handaęž‰peke.
\q1 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ hoke Sadanimaęž‰ niki hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hapeke laa yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pimiki wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu pa paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi hoke haumanu make pa paeyawalieke.
\v 15 Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pimiki wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hoke hau pa na paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ make mo ikaęž‰ pimi hoke haumanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ pa na paeyawalieke.
\s1 Nee pi witaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰manu waleekeeki
\p 
\v 16 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nee pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ haumanu aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ mo makeaaso hau piteme haliweki ikaęž‰ hoke wenoko haseme tupaęž‰ na hapaęž‰peke. Mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ nee pi ulaęž‰ some yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone winaęž‰ ikaęž‰ loke handeteke halaęž‰ hau minaęž‰paęž‰latiki pu halememe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Koto haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mulumeke hone wilimi aletaęž‰ ame do hataęž‰ mu paeyaasememe.
\v 17 Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nee pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰
\v 18 ikaęž‰ leke popeleke tandaęž‰pa itiki yola hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ handaa hone wilieke. Kutaa mo nakaęž‰ honumake siki pitele hau handaęž‰laęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenki wialieke.
\s1 Hepeni paęž‰taęž‰ hamoko hapekeeki
\r (Luku 12ęž‰33-34)
\p 
\v 19 Mo makaęž‰taęž‰ ikiki pu o bisapu inkikimaęž‰ no o haliwekimaęž‰ pake no kutu pulu peleme kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ alemanu na amu pikitaęž‰
\v 20 pa mo makaęž‰taęž‰ ikiki na pu bisapu inkikimaęž‰ na no make haliwekimaęž‰ pake na mulu peleme Hepeni nane ikaęž‰ alemanu amu piaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 21 Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ alemanu amu peleme paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemanu make mandake winaęž‰ lo halimikie.
\s1 Lokenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±
\r (Luku 11ęž‰34-36)
\p 
\v 22 Mo leketaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ olaęž‰pakee. Nakaęž‰ leke yaapo telipinaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke paeyaotaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ tumbilieke.
\v 23 Pate nakaęž‰ leke yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ loke paeyaotaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambilieke. Koto mo nakaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ timbaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pee kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ timbaęž‰ tiekee.
\s1 Homeke halimaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki you hali yaaponaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu homeke dinaęž‰ na piaęž‰pekeeki
\r (Luku 16ęž‰13, 12ęž‰22-31)
\p 
\v 24 Homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo you hali yaaponaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Puluekemaęž‰ taapo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ honditi pilieke o maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kiaalieke. Kutaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo mani pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you hali yaapo haenaęž‰ laa ipilikaęž‰ e homeke dinaęž‰ pokaapaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Wetepe epolo paęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 25 Do ekinaęž‰ yeke iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa la kitolome. IĚ± homaamaęž‰naęž‰ ikali ne aleke noluaęž‰pe laa make ya yamaęž‰peke ale tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ekipa muluaęž‰pe laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo ikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ne na lombei pu make o ikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰taęž‰ mo akaęž‰manu otaęž‰ na lombei paęž‰lekeyeke yekea.
\v 26 Mo bitutu laa pomineleme bamanu handaęž‰pe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ nolo peleme ne waemanu nokopa kilikimanu talaataęž‰ mo ne amu pu halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu na amu pu halememe. Koto hau na pu halemepate pa mo hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ nemanu anaęž‰naęž‰ halo halaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone umanaęž‰e. Kotaęž‰ iki make mo bamanu otaęž‰ lombei na pelemekeyeke yekea.
\v 27 Ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo halemeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ halo peleme nate leke hokulu peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\p 
\v 28 Ikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu ekipa muluepe laa pa ekipeke kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo halemepe. Mo si ale manunaęž‰ momamanu opaęž‰laęž‰eki hone wipee. Koto moma manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yamaęž‰peke akaęž‰manu muluekemaęž‰ e na poko halememe. Koto hau na pu halemepate
\v 29 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Kini Solomonomaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ mani tieke tiekemaęž‰ mo moma manunaęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke akaęž‰manu na hambo yameekeme alome.
\v 30 Mo ame homeke opa haenaęž‰ laa tunkula hapuao beliataęž‰ tinaęž‰ yankaęž‰peke yeke moma manunaęž‰ autaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ lawao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pee kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hodikale siki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki make otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone handeteke halieke.
\v 31 Kutu piliekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ya nolo polo ne ikali make akaęž‰ peaataęž‰ hanemaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ muluaęž‰pe laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 32 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki na opimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao koto ale manunaęž‰ anke wopu tolu haleme. Pate mo ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto alemanu nate paeyao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mu hapaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me.
\v 33 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki make ipikaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau make epenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ yeke titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la weiyu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo koto ikaęž‰ hone peleme ale manutaęž‰ iki anaęž‰lao ku halieke.
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ belianaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ ame kone na miaęž‰paęž‰peke. Belianaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ beliaeki ipikaęž‰ ale homekee. Mandane nate manunaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ ame do natenaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ taapunaęž‰ apaęž‰taapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 7
\s1 Pi yokaalu teli pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰37-38)
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu kiaapaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu na halaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 2 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi yokaalu pimi tupaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandake piki pi yokaalu kone kilieke. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰ mineme mandaęž‰maęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki make homeke mandaęž‰maęž‰ kone milieke.
\v 3 Ekipeke nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolo siki hone wopu witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake tieketaęž‰ hone na u halepe.
\v 4 Mo ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake tieke nakaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ pa winaęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰ ekipa nakaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ Nakaęž‰ leke ulaęž‰ dokolo siki meanoe lelipikipe.
\v 5 Aa yapi pi miki some. Titinaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ leke ulaęž‰ ti takaęž‰laęž‰pake kiake ambaęž‰la mea baekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolo siki mea waluekemaęž‰taęž‰ epeke handilipikie.
\p 
\v 6 Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ wiaęž‰ haleme alemanu kika paęž‰taęž‰ na halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la iki lu naamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa ikaęž‰ yenki tiekemaęž‰ hambeeke munduku teke manutaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ na lopa moneaapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto munduku manutaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu ikaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ pa tombua tombua piliekee.
\s1 Honke alaęž‰eki Weitaęž‰laęž‰eki Kilikili laasaęž‰eki
\r (Luku 11ęž‰9-13)
\p 
\v 7 Honke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kilieke. Weikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ wilipikie. Kilikili laekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ lombawalieke.
\v 8 Homeke epimaęž‰ honke laęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ milieke. Kutaa make maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ weiyaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ wilieke. Epimaęž‰ potaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo potaęž‰taęž‰ koto some paęž‰taęž‰ lombawalieke.
\p 
\v 9 Wekinaęž‰ ateke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ tia honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki epi amedamaęž‰ toopi mea halimikipe
\v 10 o taęž‰peli honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke keto mea halimikipe.
\v 11 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke epeke alemanu halaęž‰pekeeki hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ piteme hau otaęž‰ lombei peao koto honke lo haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke epeke alemanu halieke.
\v 12 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mandane haumanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ pinaęž‰e laa hone peleme tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto haumanu kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ mo Lo Pi wiekeeki make potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wimiki manaęž‰ pi make do koto hau peomono loluekemaęž‰ wieke pie.
\s1 Dekepeke potaęž‰ petipeke potaęž‰ yaapo
\r (Luku 13ęž‰24)
\p 
\v 13 Mo dekepeke potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ puaęž‰peke potaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ peo tieke la make ipikaęž‰ polo paęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ make aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wieke handaa wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki puaęž‰tiki pu halememe.
\v 14 Kutu pu halemepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ otaęž‰ dekepeke potaęž‰ kakee. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰leke handaa wandaęž‰hali hosikimaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰ u halememe.
\s1 Tinaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilikinaęž‰ hau yaapo
\r (Luku 6ęž‰43-44)
\p 
\v 15 Mo yayapiki potopede haliwekimaęž‰ iki makeaamaęž‰naęž‰ leke leke lo hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki makealuekemaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ manda hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ sipisipi nono pilimipate ikaęž‰ puki tukiki nanetaęž‰ hali lu no halaęž‰ tikene kikamanu leke kone halememe.
\v 16 Ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pu halemeeki handuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiliki manumaęž‰ peneme yaemekaęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰ wilimikie. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ waini kiliki taluekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo taolaęž‰ punaęž‰ eiyo haleke talo halaęž‰pe o nose kiliki taluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kaĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ talo halaęž‰pe.
\v 17 Kutaa make mandane ipi saosao liki timaęž‰taęž‰ epeke kilikimanu aęž‰iliaęž‰pate pa hakaęž‰teke timaęž‰taęž‰ hoke kilikimanu aęž‰ilieke.
\v 18 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate ipi saosao liki timaęž‰taęž‰ hoke kiliki aęž‰eyaęž‰peke na yelieke. Kutaa make hakaęž‰teke timaęž‰ epeke kiliki aęž‰eyo peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Hande ti maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke kiliki na aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo titaęž‰ yankuluekemaęž‰ pokilieke.
\v 20 Kutaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande yayapiki potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kilikimanu peneme yaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ wilimikie.
\s1 Tekehali Tekehalio alemeeki
\r (Luku 13ęž‰25-27)
\p 
\v 21 Mo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali Tekehali lo haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ oli hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na pelimikie. Kotoeki na pulu pelemepate mo ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali homeke homeke hondaęž‰ pambaa pelimikie.
\v 22 Mo hande wandaęž‰hali paeyao mombaęž‰lalo paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ dupiki pimanu IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ lelimikie. Tekehalio. Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ biki alo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu walao halomaęž‰me. O Nakaęž‰ biki lomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hoke temokomanu wopu tolu lu make taęž‰taęž‰ piki na handeke haumanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ wopu pumaęž‰me lelimikie.
\v 23 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kutu piki pimanu lelimipate IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimanu hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ hosiki make otaęž‰ na handoaęž‰maęž‰ iki hoke wandaęž‰hali IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ na hake pupama laa tolu lueke.
\s1 Hali yaapomaęž‰ da yaapo aęž‰epekeeki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰47-49)
\p 
\v 24 Kutaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ do ya pimanu opuaataęž‰ koto alo ekimanu otaęž‰ pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo hande hone wopu wia toopi manda da aęž‰eyeke hali tupaęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\v 25 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ lako tieke lopeeke ekimaęž‰ ikalimanu paeyao too make po tilipu tiekemaęž‰ mo danaęž‰ ambula ambula piekepate mo dataęž‰ toopi manda aęž‰eyeke ekimaęž‰ na lombiekeme.
\v 26 Pate wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ do ya pimanu opuaataęž‰ koto alo ekimanu na pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo hande hone wopu na wiki hou manda da aęž‰eyeke hali tupaęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\v 27 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ lako tieke lopeeke ekimaęž‰ ikalimanu paeyao too make po tilipu tiekemaęž‰ mo danaęž‰ ambula ambula pieke ekimaęž‰ mo dataęž‰ mea lombayekeme. Otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰hapu mea lombao hoeyaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ do koto pimanu walo paeyaeyeketaęž‰ mo hande mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ leke opo handaake wimikime.
\v 29 Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ walo haemeke tupaęž‰ na waleekeme. Pate ipikitaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ halimaęž‰ waleke nono pieke handaa pimikime.
\c 8
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ kindi yeni hake hali epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 1ęž‰40-45, Luku 5ęž‰12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ oli hande pote paęž‰taęž‰ hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao epeeke handaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tieke ipikaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea epemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa Yesu opolo ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ kindi yeni hake hali homeke ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neke hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya yeni epeawalenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 3 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao wataaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. IĚ± hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ kindi yenitaęž‰ epeao epeke loke halenaęž‰ alome leekeme. Koto leeke tomonaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo somenaęž‰ kindi yenitaęž‰ hapua mateekeme.
\v 4 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo some paęž‰taęž‰ Opie la alotaęž‰ Doeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la na leketaęž‰ pa mo yeni peao halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la nakaęž‰ yeni otaęž‰ paelaęž‰pe laa handenaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke. Kutaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paelaęž‰me hone winaęž‰ mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia halaęž‰laęž‰ ale lia halaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Ami you halinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ some epeaeyekeeki
\r (Luku 7ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 5 Yesu mo hande Kapeneami daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua haenaęž‰ mo hande Lomaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ami haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ Yesu mandaęž‰ hande pitolo honke alo alotaęž‰
\v 6 Tekehalio. Ya e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ kiki anke lupa wiki yeni mea potaęž‰ pomuaęž‰peke na yaalo tanda tieke mea ya da paęž‰taęž‰ u peli pelia halaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Epeaalo pulueke leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leeke handaataęž‰ mo somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ O diaęž‰me. Neke ya da paęž‰taęž‰ epo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epeke hali diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni pa paenaęž‰e pi homeke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ya e pokaasaęž‰ hali tialieke.
\v 9 Pa ekipeke. IĚ±taęž‰ mandane ami you haliweki oto paęž‰taęž‰ halome. Kutaa IĚ± oto paęž‰taęž‰ make mandane ami haliweki halememe. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Pue loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pelieke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make Epoe loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa ya pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ Do e pokae loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pealieke leekeme.
\v 10 Koto leekeeki Yesumaęž‰ opuolotaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo Isulai tapake tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki hone tulaake some homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome.
\p 
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa alome. Mo nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ make pambaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ make wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yawe lulu paęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke make Dieikope ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tao pitaęž‰ nelimikie.
\v 12 Pate mo hande Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pua hapaęž‰peke yolo peleme wandaęž‰hali kone pa mo timbaęž‰ laęž‰papeke paęž‰taęž‰ yolo baalieke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ eĚ± tieke alo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kake nokopa hataęž‰ kake lenkenaęž‰ tieke lo halimikie laa
\v 13 Yesumaęž‰ mo ami you hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekimaęž‰ kone pealiekemaęž‰ da pue leekeme. Mo ami you halinaęž‰ e pokaeyeke halitaęž‰ koto kone tiaeyekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰hali wopu Yesumaęž‰ epeaeyekeme
\r (Maka 1ęž‰29-34, Luku 4ęž‰38-41)
\p 
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ Pidanaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Pidanaęž‰ meiyeke wandaęž‰ hoputiti yeni hao ipikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polu pitiekeeki handeekeme.
\v 15 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ kiki wataaso haenaęž‰ mo yeni tandeleekeme. Kutu pieke handaa ipiki tiao hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ nemanu haleekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Nate pambolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu pitiki wandaęž‰hali wopu Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mea epemekeme. Mo hoke temoko manutaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ tolu liaataęž‰ yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ yenimanu make tandelaeyekeme.
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali epeaeyeke hau manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone nikaęž‰ ki yenimanu meao make mo biki ulaęž‰ yeni tekemanu make yokaęž‰ mea baeyekeme laa laęž‰ wieke pi yaaluekemaęž‰ yeke piekeme.
\s1 Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± poluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki
\r (Luku 9ęž‰57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande ipiki aęž‰pa ambulaemeke wandaęž‰hali handaa hone wiaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ikali leke mone teaęž‰naęž‰ baape leekeme.
\v 19 Mo hande wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ halio. IĚ±taęž‰ neke hando paęž‰taęž‰ pekaęž‰naęž‰ make otaęž‰ teli mea pomuluekemaęž‰ yeke IĚ±maęž‰ tikitiki yao halome.
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Keao halaęž‰ kika manumaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ polu peleme ale ulaęž‰me. Kutaa ba manumaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ peliaęž‰paęž‰peke dakemanu hao halaęž‰me. Pate mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you wia peliaęž‰peke da pandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\v 21 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teliaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ kone Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ya apaęž‰ mea hoiluekemaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ponoe leekeme.
\v 22 Pate Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ toko manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hoinaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ IĚ± teli mea epoe leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ pimaęž‰ po tilipu tunkulaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 4ęž‰35-41, Luku 8ęž‰22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ kawaso homeke paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pitulu peeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make telimea pemekeme.
\v 24 Mo kawaso pua ikali leke tukiki tukikinaęž‰ haenaęž‰ penkilipake po tilipu tiekemaęž‰ mo ikali lekenaęž‰ ambulaeyekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ mo kawasotaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ honki lapeke yekepate Yesutaęž‰ u peliekeme.
\v 25 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipiki mea tiaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nikitaęž‰ ikali naa homaęž‰pekeeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ ta yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ekipeke handa paalaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homelemepe. Ikitaęž‰ hone wotu na tulake some hombo yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laataęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tia liao hataęž‰ mo hande po tilipu pitaęž‰ ikali ho yaapo tunkulinaęž‰ pi leekeme. Koto leeketaęž‰ mo hande po ikali yaapo tunkula laęž‰maęž‰ na piki e pondo na leke wiekeme.
\v 27 Kutu piekeeki handolo hataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime. Mo ikali pitaęž‰ po tilipu yaapomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ opitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do sometaęž‰ eki piki some yekea lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ yaapo halinaęž‰ hoke temoko tolu liekeeki
\r (Maka 5ęž‰1-20, Luku 8ęž‰26-39)
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande ikali leke mone teaęž‰naęž‰ wieke kenke Kedata nane opolo ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ hali hoiyu hayeke tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ haepeke hali yaapomaęž‰ Yesu aęž‰pa mandaęž‰ hande pipikime. Mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke temokomanu pitieke ekimaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰taęž‰ wopu piki some yaapo haepekeme. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hali yaapo haepeke ale teke paęž‰taęž‰ wieke potaęž‰naęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yekeme.
\v 29 Koto hali yaapomaęž‰ Yesu handolo hataęž‰ koto kone wi la alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekeo. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau puluekemaęž‰ ipulipe laa Mo hande niki hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ nate aĚ±iĚ± na epeke haenaęž‰ niki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe lemekeme.
\v 30 Iki haemeke ale mo pate leketaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ titimaęž‰ ne nalo haemekeme.
\v 31 Kutaataęž‰ mo hande hoke temoko manumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki tolueke hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ titi paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pomono tapaapeke laa honke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ koto hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ pupee leeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapo minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo maęž‰naęž‰ titi paęž‰taęž‰ pua hondaęž‰ pambemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ titi paeyaotaęž‰ mo lombeeke alenaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya holaęž‰paęž‰niao ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ lopaataęž‰ ikali naa homaęž‰ pitaemekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutupa mo maęž‰naęž‰ titi handeteke haemeke hali manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ teke da nane pindipa puaataęž‰ mo hande pieke hau paeyao make hande hoke temoko pitiki hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pieke haumanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ paeyao wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mokaęž‰laemekeme.
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali otaęž‰ paeya tapaomaęž‰ Yesu mandaęž‰ hande pulu pemekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu handaa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ da yu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pue lemekeme.
\c 9
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ dolaęž‰pake piki hali homeke epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 2ęž‰1-12, Luku 5ęž‰17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ mo kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pua mo ikali leke tunkula paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mone teaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme.
\v 2 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ dolaęž‰pake piki hali homeke ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tilinaęž‰ mea tia epemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki handaa mo dolaęž‰pake piki hali handolo alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epolo pilaęž‰taa. Nakaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ pa paeyaasome leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Mandane wape pea walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opua ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do somemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki hoeyake pi alaęž‰me hone wimikime.
\p 
\v 4-5 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ hone wimikieki handaa Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kokele pea hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke handa ikaęž‰ puki manumaęž‰ koto hoke honemanu miniki halemepe laa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki hone witemepe. IĚ±maęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ paeyaasome alo pi yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o Neke tiao pue alo pi yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa
\v 6 iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyaapeke wele wia halo ekitaęž‰ ame pene yanomaęž‰ handaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto laataęž‰ mo hande dolaęž‰pake some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao. Nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea mina da pue leekeme.
\v 7 Mo halimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ tiao ipikaęž‰ da peekeme.
\v 8 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto hau handolotaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Do epeaasaęž‰ weletaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ halaa piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa ipikaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laemekeme.
\s1 Maęž‰tiu paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± telimea epoe leekeeki
\r (Maka 2ęž‰13-17, Luku 5ęž‰27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mu hayeke hali bikitaęž‰ Maęž‰tiu ipikaęž‰ mani yataęž‰po hayeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeeki handeekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± teli mea epoe leekeme. Koto leeke Maęž‰tiu tiao ipiki telimea peekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ Maęž‰tiunaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ne nalo pitinaęž‰ dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki wopu make hoke haliweki wopu make Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pitimikime.
\v 11 Kutu pimikieki mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke mo ikaęž‰ disamaęž‰ mo dakisi mani mu haleme haliweki mo hoke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne no pilimipe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ koto lemeke pi opua iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yeni na hasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ dokeda hali paęž‰taęž‰ na polo pelemepate pa yeni hasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ dokeda paęž‰taęž‰ pelimikie.
\v 13 Hande Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hoteke lia halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰pate aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo hasaęž‰ hau homeke hone paęž‰laęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ tekemanu ambaęž‰la hone uemenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pua weiyaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pu halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰yeke wi loluekemaęž‰ na epoaęž‰pate pa hoke hau pu halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰yeke wi loluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Nee pi witaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maka 2ęž‰18-22, Luku 5ęž‰33-39)
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo hande bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dioninaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make tanaęž‰ eleke elekenaęž‰ nee pi u moneao halomaęž‰pate nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ nee pi otaęž‰ na wilimime leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰ panake taęž‰maęž‰ni pitaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ tekehalimaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wi leeke epemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mandake hao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo halimikie hone witemepe. Diaęž‰me. Koto peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate ipiki mea polo paęž‰laęž‰ nate ipiliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ teke halitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± na halieke. Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nee pi wilimikie.
\p 
\v 16 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ dau tombulu epeaaluekemaęž‰ mo panake dau sinkipikieki mea talao na tombulu halaęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ panake dau sinkipiki talaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ dau paa sinkipa kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ tieke wilieke.
\v 17 Koto tupaęž‰ kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ panake waini ikalitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ipi kanake manunaęž‰ na holo pambo halaęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo waini ikali hoelolu baalieke. Kutu piliaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke make otaęž‰ hoeya pa wilieke. Kutu piliepate panake maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ kanakemanu mea panake waini ikali holo pambeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikali kanake yaapotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ endialipipikie laa leekeme.
\s1 Homaęž‰pa wieke wandiki pitaęž‰ yeni hao hayeke wandaęž‰ yaapo
\r (Maka 5ęž‰21-43, Luku 8ęž‰40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ do koto pimanu alo haenaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni danaęž‰ you hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa tumiki yotuao pitaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wandikitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kiki aęž‰pa wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tiaalieke leekeme.
\v 19 Koto leeke Yesu tiao ipiki telimea peeke ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make mandake pemekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ homeke Yesunaęž‰ hoki nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ dopieke dau nepoko wataeyekeme. Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ bapi 12 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke andusaęž‰ we wopu yopu lombei peao hayekeme.
\v 21 Koto wandaęž‰naęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau watawaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ya yeni paelieke hone wiekeme.
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰moneao ipiki handolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone tulaale ekimaęž‰ neke epeleme leekeme. Koto leeke paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ yeni paeyao epea hayekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu mo hande you halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeekeme. Koto homaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemeke pe kanake litaęž‰laęž‰ tapake make homaęž‰ witolo eĚ± alaęž‰ tapake wopu make pitimikieki handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 24 Koto wandiki sikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰pate pa u paęž‰elaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ iki paeyao hama pupe leekeme. Koto leeketaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki kitaemekemepate
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali tolu lia hama nane haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ kiki mieketaęž‰ mo wandiki koto kone tiaeyekeme.
\v 26 Koto wandiki mea tiaeyeke ekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ koto kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ kende tupaęž‰ wiekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ leke holupiki hali yaapo epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu haenaęž‰ leke holu piki hali yaapomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane wi tieke laęž‰ paleke teli mea pulu alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekeo. Diki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke laęž‰tia pepekeme.
\v 28 Yesu da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo haenaęž‰ koto leke holu piki hali yaapotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epepekeme. Kutu pipiki Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipiliki epeapeke wele ulaęž‰me hone witolo hone ti lalepepe leekeme. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe lepekeme.
\v 29 Koto lepeke pi Yesumaęž‰ opua ipilikaęž‰ leke wataaso alotaęž‰ Koto ipilikaęž‰ hone ti lalepe tupaęž‰ kone pinaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 30 Koto pi alo haenaęž‰ kone ipilikaęž‰ leke ki leekeme. Kutu pieke Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na pua lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 31 Koto leekepate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ mo Yesumaęž‰ pieke hautaęž‰ koto haepeke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ lepekeme.
\s1 Pi na leke hali epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 32 Mo hande leke holu piki hali yaapo mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ pa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi na leke hali homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epemekeme. Mo halinaęž‰ pi na leeke ekitaęž‰ hoke temoko pitaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande hoke temoko tolu lieketaęž‰ koto kone mo hande pi na leke halimaęž‰ pi paa leekeme. Koto piekeeki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handolo tolaęž‰tia pominolo alotaęž‰ Dupiki hau homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ Isulai kenke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na handomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 34 Koto lemekepate mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hoke you temokonaęž‰ wele mea koto hande hoke temokomanu tolu lia piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeeki
\p 
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu pomu lopeekeme. Ikaęž‰ teke da tieke paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰manu make pomu lopo piekeme. Kutaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni pu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ make pi walo hayekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapomanu walolo hataęž‰ make mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki yeni haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni tekemanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ wamo peatiki pomu hayekeme.
\v 36 Koto pomieke ale paęž‰taęž‰manu mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali tieke handaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ tieke otaęž‰ wopu homeekeme. Pa ekiepinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo handeteke halaęž‰ hali na hake sipisipimanu hataęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke na yo make hone mataalo hone ti yoko haemeke haumanu handolo kutu piekeme.
\v 37 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki handolo alotaęž‰ Ne napeke tieke wopu potaęž‰laęž‰pate mo mea mombaęž‰laapeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ aneke diaęž‰me.
\v 38 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ ne napeke mea mombaęž‰laalo peleme haliweki anaęž‰naęž‰ tapaenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 10
\s1 Mo 12 Aposolo haliwekinaęž‰ bikimanu
\r (Maka 3ęž‰13-19, Luku 6ęž‰12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki 12 haliweki wi laęž‰ mea mombaęž‰lao hataęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu tolu liaęž‰peke welemanu make hoke yeni tekemanu make wamo peaęž‰peke welemanu make iki paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ haleekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Koto 12 Aposolo haliwekinaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ doe. Titinaęž‰taęž‰ Saimono biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Pida kutupataęž‰ Pida ipikaęž‰ hameke Aęž‰ndutu make Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi Dioni hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ make
\v 3 Pilipi make Badolomiu make Tomasi make mo hande dakisi mu hayeke some Maęž‰tiu make Aęž‰lopiaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi make Taęž‰diaęž‰si make
\v 4 Saimono Seloti make mo hande Yesu linaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeaęž‰ hali Diudasi Isekatioti make ikaęž‰ biki paeyaotaęž‰ koto wape pea ulaęž‰ handaęž‰pe.
\s1 Mo 12 haliwekimaęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ tapaa tapaa piekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰7-13, Luku 6ęž‰12-16)
\p 
\v 5 Koto 12 haliweki tapaaluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi leekeme. Mo Diendaili tapakenaęž‰ da yu paęž‰taęž‰manu o Sametia tapakenaęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰manu make na puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 6 Pate kutu piteleme tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo Isulainaęž‰ alu peleme sipisipimaęž‰ handeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa iki puaataęž‰ dupiki pi lapaęž‰peke Mo hande Hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ ta aęž‰pa halaęž‰ handaęž‰pe lapaęž‰peke.
\v 8 Koto alo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni wamo peao make mo homemeke tokomanu mea daęž‰tao make wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ halaęž‰ kindi yenimanu epeaaso hataęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu tolu lu piaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do koto peaęž‰paęž‰peke alo ekitaęž‰ pa hameke mimi ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pa hameke halaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 9 Ikaęž‰ pausa paęž‰taęž‰ kolo mani o silipa mani o wepiki toeamanu make na mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 10 Ta potaęž‰naęž‰ poluekemaęž‰taęž‰ nu o topo dau o topo ankedake o tumapu make na mea pu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ alemanu kone halaęž‰peke yaęž‰lieke.
\p 
\v 11 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu o da teke paęž‰taęž‰manu opolo pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke tikitiki piki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ weiya handaataęž‰ koto somenaęž‰ da topo na piki pa pelia haotaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 12 Da homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo hataęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi lapaęž‰peke Do da paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaenaęž‰e lapaęž‰peke.
\v 13 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ halimi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ epoe lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto epeaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ u pelia haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Pate iki taęž‰naęž‰ na homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto epeaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ paa yokaęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 14 Kutaa make mandane daoni o da teke manumaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Epeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa na handaęž‰ mu make o ikaęž‰ pi na opu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da yu minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ dokolo tande laa minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 15 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate tieke ipiliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Sodomo da pitaęž‰ Komoto da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke mulu pelepepate pa koto ikanaęž‰maęž‰ walimi pi kiaalimi wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mulu peleme yenkitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao halieke alome leekeme.
\s1 Tanda meaęž‰pekeeki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰9-13, Luku 21ęž‰12-17)
\p 
\v 16 Opuaęž‰pe. Ikitaęž‰ mo honkopu wopu na hake sipisipimanu tupaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ iki mo tikene iyamanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hamenaęž‰ tapaasome. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande ketomaęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ pomuaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make kimelemaęž‰ pomuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutaa make mo hande dokolo ba manumaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitu haleme tupaęž‰ iki make sembepela hao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 17 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pulu peleme ekimanu wopu handeteke hao hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea pua make mo ikaęž‰ pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu iki yombilimikie.
\v 18 Paa yanaaso ya biki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo kapomani tumiki haliwekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo kinimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make hatuku pelimikie. Kutu pilimi tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ koto kapomani tumiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make waloemenaęž‰ waleke wilieke.
\v 19 Iki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minilimi pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Do pi yokaalu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki pi loluaęž‰pe o eki pa hombo pealuaęž‰pe laa hone ti na yoko hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo pi yokaalu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi kini pilimi tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ lolo peleme pitaęž‰ pa peneme yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ mea lelimikie.
\v 20 Koto mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ lolo peleme pi manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimanu diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lelimi pi paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ laęž‰naęž‰ yeke epenaęž‰ alaęž‰ekie.
\p 
\v 21 Haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamekemanu kone lia homaenaęž‰ mea halimikie. Ateke tonumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ weki wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke hau kone pinaęž‰ lelimikie. Mo wekiwandikimaęž‰ make paa ateke inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneao aęž‰ndaęž‰ litolo hataęž‰ mo ateke inkiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lia homaenaęž‰ halimikie.
\v 22 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ya e pokaaseme haliweki hataęž‰ ya biki miniki haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ iki hoki wala kialimikie. Kutu pilimipate kone mo haumanu ipulu haenaęž‰ kone mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epenaęž‰ yu wia hataęž‰ honkopu hao bepolatiki pu haliaęž‰ sometaęž‰ daęž‰taa haenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 23 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ daoni homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halimipate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pindipa puaęž‰paęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Isulainaęž‰ daoni paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pokolo peleme emanu paeyao titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la na minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie alome.
\p 
\v 24 Mo sukulu pitaęž‰laęž‰ weki o wandikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ disa some lombei peao na halaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some make ipikaęž‰ e teke hali lombei peao na halaęž‰me.
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo sukulu pitaęž‰laęž‰ wekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yaka disa some tupaęž‰ halueke laa hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo e pokaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰ make Ya e teke hali tupaęž‰ kone halueke laa hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto make anaęž‰ pilieke. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo da homeke paęž‰taęž‰ pambo haleme tapakenaęž‰ Ateke paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hoke biki Bielisibulu laęž‰ wiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make koto biki otaęž‰ lombei piki otaęž‰ hoke bikimanu kone laęž‰tiki pilimikie.
\v 26 Kutu pu halimipate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\s1 Epi paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe
\r (Luku 12ęž‰2-7)
\p Mo ame do aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ paa lumbaęž‰pa wilieke. Kutupa mo aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ aleme pi paeyao make wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ paa peneme yaalieke.
\v 27 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ timba nane la kitolo pimanu paeyao natepa nane ikanaęž‰maęž‰ peneme yao wilimikie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ honumake siki pitaęž‰ opimi pimanu paeyaotaęž‰ mo da holu manda ninaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ peneme yao la halimikie.
\v 28 Mo ikaęž‰ loke lia homalo paęž‰lemepate ikaęž‰ temoko lia homaaluekemaęž‰ wataapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke. Pate mo ikaęž‰ loke pitaęž‰ temoko yaapo ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ tapao hoeyaapeke Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke otaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 29 Hosiki ba siki yaapotaęž‰ makedinaęž‰ yenki 10 toea sikimaęž‰ hambaęž‰peke ba siki yaapo yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo basunu homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa pene waleke na winaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa na lopilieke.
\v 30 Kutaa ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make dupa alome Ikaęž‰ you itiki paeyaotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone yataęž‰pa anaęž‰ lao ulaęž‰me.
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ koto hosiki basunu wopunaęž‰ yenki otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ biki peneme yaasaęž‰eki
\r (Luku 12ęž‰8-9)
\p 
\v 32 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ peneme yaaso hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ halie leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make mo ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ leke poto poto hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke hau kone pulueke.
\v 33 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke poto poto hataęž‰ yaka biki na leke IĚ± hoki wala hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make mo ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ leke poto poto hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make kutu pulueke.
\s1 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰pekeeki
\r (Luku 12ęž‰51-53, 14ęž‰26-27)
\p 
\v 34 Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki mea epeaęž‰me hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Diaęž‰me. Aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki na mea epoaęž‰pate pa aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ kepete mea epoaęž‰me.
\v 35 IĚ± epolo haumaęž‰taęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hali haenaęž‰ lo make wandikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkikinaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandiki haenaęž‰ lo make aeyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halikinaęž‰ inkikinaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ lo make
\v 36 kutupa hali homekenaęž‰ titinaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haleme tapake kone yaęž‰lieke.
\p 
\v 37 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ puki wiliaęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ya disaipolo hali haenaęž‰ lapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ puki wiliaęž‰pate kone pa ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ u hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ya disaipolo hali haenaęž‰ lapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 38 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mea tia ya hau hondaęž‰ mea na telia piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ya disaipolo hali haenaęž‰ lapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 39 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ taapo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki alupalieke. Pate ya e ambaęž‰la pokaaluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰la hone na wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somenaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa u halieke.
\p 
\v 40 Wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ iki ya disaipolo haliweki handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ IĚ± kone handaęž‰ minelememe. Koto tupaęž‰ kone epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ mo IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone pitememe.
\v 41 Wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali homeke handaataęž‰ Do sometaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ somee hone witolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ yenki putu piliki kone milimikie. Wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ mo epeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ epeke hau handaa Ipikitaęž‰ epeke halie laa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto epeke somemaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ yenki putu piliki kone milimikie.
\v 42 Epimaęž‰ do ya hoki nane tolu halaęž‰ you hali diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone pa ya hoki nane tolu halaęž‰ hali yaęž‰leke handaa mo hande ipi kanake homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ halo haeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ikali haliaęž‰ somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yenki putu piliki otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ milieke hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke alome leekeme.
\c 11
\s1 Dionimaęž‰ dipula pitaęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki
\r (Luku 7ęž‰18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ 12 disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ koto manaęž‰ pimanu la hala paeyeke hoki nanetaęž‰ koto kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao pa mo teke paęž‰taęž‰manu haemeke daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu walo mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiao make mo Pi Seliapo walo hayekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ mo hande bapitaisi peao hayeke some Dionimaęž‰ mo dipula pitaęž‰ mo Ketisomaęž‰ kutupiki haumanu pitaęž‰laęž‰me leekeeki opuataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimanu Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 3 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Do nikaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ la kuelenaęž‰e. Dionimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipilieke leaęž‰ halitaęž‰ nekepe o maęž‰ndaęž‰ epenaęž‰ yu wia hamonope leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua do ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handeleme ekimanu make katakemaęž‰ opiteleme ekimanu make Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ dupa pua la halaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 5 Hande leke holu piki wandaęž‰hali ametaęž‰ ki lelememe. Dolaęž‰pake wandaęž‰hali make tiao pominelememe. Kindi yeni haeme wandaęž‰hali make ametaęž‰ epea halememe. Katake pokeme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ katake make lumbulaęž‰me. Homeaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make paa daęž‰taa tiao haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ do IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo haumanu handaa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰me laa pua lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa mo Dioninaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki laęž‰kaęž‰la paa pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ pi dupa lawaeyekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pulutaęž‰ aleke handulumeke hone wimipe. Pomaęž‰ hambe make mea aneya moneya pu tonkuaęž‰laęž‰eki handulumeke hone wimipe. Diaęž‰me.
\v 8 Koto alenaęž‰ pulutaęž‰ aleke handulumeke hone wimipe. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ epeke akaęž‰ seliapo yameke hali haliaęž‰eki handulumeke hone wimipe. Diaęž‰me. Akaęž‰ seliapo yameke haliwekitaęž‰ mo kini haliwekinaęž‰ pitu halaęž‰ aleninaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate
\v 9 IĚ± opuono aĚ±iĚ± la kipaęž‰e. Koto pemeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ aleke handulumeke hone wimipe. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halaasaęž‰ potopede hali yekepe. Aowe. Ipikitaęž‰ potopede hali yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa potopede halinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei piki some halaęž‰me.
\v 10 Koto some Dionitaęž‰ mo hande Baibolonaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Ya pi lawalo pulaęž‰ hali ambaęž‰la mo nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ tiki tiki yawaenaęž‰e tapaalueke
\m leeke pitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo hande bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hali Dionitaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ haemeke hali paeyao otaęž‰ lombei piki some halaęž‰me. Pate mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ biki na ulaęž‰ some aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Dioni lombei paęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 12 Dionimaęž‰ mo hande pimanu waleaęž‰ natenaęž‰ kini pu mea aęž‰pa ame do natenaęž‰ kone mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ lombei lombei puaęž‰tiki ipu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo honkopu hao haleme haliwekimaęž‰ koto hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki miniki halememe.
\v 13 Ambaęž‰ haemeke potopede haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke Lo pi manumaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki aęž‰paataęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ nate opolo aęž‰pa haenaęž‰taęž‰ lo naeyekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande haliwekimaęž‰ laęž‰ wimiki pimanu opuluekemaęž‰ hone pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande haliwekimaęž‰ ipilieke laa laęž‰ wimi Elaidiataęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ lemeke yekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Ikaęž‰ katakemaęž‰ opuaęž‰peke yemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 16 Amedo do haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ handelememe lonope. Ikitaęž‰ mo makedi hama putupa alu pea pilimi wekiwandiki leke halememe. Ane kalale pitimi tapakemaęž‰ mone kalale pitimi tapake wi laęž‰ moneao alotaęž‰
\q1 
\v 17 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ samaęž‰ puemenaęž‰yeke tapeke lumaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ samaęž‰ na piki kiaememe.
\q1 Kutu pimikitaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ piki emelimanu lomaęž‰pate eĚ± na leke kiaememe alememe.
\p 
\v 18 Dioni aęž‰pa ikali ne na neeke ekitaęž‰ hande wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pilaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 19 Pate Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke aęž‰pa ikali ne yaapo no hayeke ekitaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kone handolo alotaęž‰ Do hali handaęž‰pe. Ipikitaęž‰ ikali ne wopu no hake some yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mo hande dakisi mu make hoke hau pu haleme haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰taalaęž‰me lemekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo hone wiki haumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pu halaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honetaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hone o hoke hone laa pa peneme yaasaęž‰me.
\s1 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ puki na laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰lemekeeki
\r (Luku 10ęž‰13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Mo hande Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ na handeke haumanu pu hayeke daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo haumanu handaa kone ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao na laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰lemeke yeke handaa
\v 21 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto da teke paęž‰taęž‰manu haemeke wandaęž‰hali hando alo alotaęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰e. Kotaasini daoni neke paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰ pilaęž‰me. Betesaidao. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ make kutu piki hau kone ipuluekemaęž‰ pilaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ mo ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰ na handeke haumanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo hande daoni yaapo Taiya Saidoni paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ puki laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰mekaęž‰taęž‰me laa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handenaęž‰taęž‰ busaęž‰ pitikimanu wepia yamaataęž‰ lankaęž‰ apolo kitulu pimime.
\v 22 IĚ±maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Taiya Saidoni yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo ipiliki Kotaasini Betesaida yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰ pao halieke.
\v 23 Aęž‰pei Kapeneamio. Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ neketaęž‰ oli hepeni nane nakaęž‰ kone mea aęž‰meiyalueke hone wilipe. O diaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ mea tapaalieke. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰ na handeke haumanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo hande Sodomo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto dataęž‰ ame pa hao halo piaęž‰me.
\v 24 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Sodomo halo paęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo neke Kapeneami paęž‰taęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰ pao halieke.
\s1 Hoto pituluekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epoe leekeeki
\r (Luku 10ęž‰21-22)
\p 
\v 25 Koto tomaęž‰naęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Neketaęž‰ do kenke oli hepeni yaaponaęž‰ Tekehalio. Keiyae tieke aloe. Pa ekipeke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande handaęž‰wiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao winaęž‰ le hau manutaęž‰ pa mo hone wopu na wiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaaleme.
\v 26 Aowe Apaęž‰o. Koto ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone piekeyeke eki yaenaęž‰yeke pinaęž‰ aleme laa leekeme.
\v 27 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ ya Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Eiyeketaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰pate Apaęž‰maęž‰ homeke handaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone Apaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰pate Eiyekemaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make Ateke handenaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ iki maĚ±leke lia peneme yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie.
\p 
\v 28 Mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki alemanu tia pominolo hataęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homa haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao iki paęž‰taęž‰ ya kulu polo hoto pitaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰maęž‰ muemenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 29 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitolo titaęž‰ mea ikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ tia hataęž‰taęž‰ ya hau hondaęž‰ mea piaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. IĚ±taęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ hataęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ homu pea halome. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukinaęž‰ lopaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ milimikie.
\v 30 Do IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ tuemenaęž‰ mea tiaaso timaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ peiyoko na hoeyaalieke. Kutaa mo IĚ±maęž‰ mea tipe alo kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ wopu na piki yapaęž‰ pilieke alome leekeme.
\c 12
\s1 Hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki
\r (Maka 2ęž‰23-28, Luku 6ęž‰1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Hosikimaęž‰ hao hao pea hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pilaęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ mo widi e manunaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ iki teaęž‰ pieke handaa widinaęž‰ kilikimanu hondaęž‰mipi pea nemekeme.
\v 2 Kutu pimikieki mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ handaa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Mo nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ piteleme ekitaęž‰ do Hoto Pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ piaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitolo pitelememe lemekepate
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande Deipidi ipikaęž‰ haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± iki teaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke natenaęž‰taęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ na yataęž‰pa handemepe.
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wieke palaowa meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± nemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ naamaęž‰naęž‰ pi wieke palaowataęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ homeke napeke yeekeeki kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea nemekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ Lo Pi ulaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande yeni peao haleme haliwekimaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ nate paeyao ninaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰tiki pu halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na peaęž‰tiki pu halememe. Kutu piki wape maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe.
\v 6 Pate mo koto tembolo da otaęž‰ lombei piki alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ homeke do aęž‰pa ulaęž‰me laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome.
\v 7 Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo lia kitaęž‰laęž‰ hoteke manutaęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau homeke hone paęž‰laęž‰mee laęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ tekemanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ hone wopu wimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ataęž‰kaęž‰ na peao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau peleme pi na lolo pimime.
\v 8 Pa ekipeke mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ tekehali kone halaęž‰me alome laa leekeme.
\s1 Kiki hoke halinaęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 3ęž‰1-6, Luku 6ęž‰6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰
\v 10 kiki hapueke endiki hali homeke koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Mandane halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ somee loluekemaęž‰ yeke ipiki handaęž‰ pelia haemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ do Hoto Pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ mo yenimanu epeaapeke hau piaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ waleke ulaęž‰pe o diaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo nakaęž‰ sipisipi homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ keonaęž‰ lopeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kutaa kone hopulaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyapeke na yeliaęž‰pe.
\v 12 Kutu pieke ekinaęž‰ halinaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ mo sipisipinaęž‰ yenki otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tambaęž‰ miomono nikaęž‰ Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ waleke wiawalaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 13 Koto pi la paeyeke Yesumaęž‰ mo kiki hapueke endiki some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki tindipae leekeme. Koto leeke ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipaeyekeme. Tindipataęž‰ mo kiki epeataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke kiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ leke kone hayekeme.
\v 14 Kutu pieketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ koto da minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama puaataęž‰ Yesu luekemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰ wimikime.
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ maĚ±leke lieke e pokaasaęž‰ hali
\p 
\v 15 Ipiki luekemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰ wimikieki Yesumaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipiki telimea pemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ homaęž‰pa wimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyao epeao haenaęž‰ laataęž‰
\v 16 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke na lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 17 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piki hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande potopede hali Aisaya paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke yekeeki peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ pate piekeme. Aisayamaęž‰ wape pieke pi manutaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 18 Do ya e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ maĚ±leke lia do haenaęž‰ lolome.
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wopu homo hataęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Ya temokotaęž‰ ipiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ tapaalueke.
\q1 Kutu poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke paeyaonaęž‰ haleme tapake paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ya tiki tiki peaasaęž‰ pimanu la hawalieke.
\q1 
\v 19 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lu tombualuekemaęž‰ mineke pi make o lu tombuake pi na lelieke.
\q1 Kutupa mo potaęž‰ kaęž‰pa ninaęž‰ hataęž‰ make pi tiekemanu na lelieke.
\q1 
\v 20 Hambe homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hosiki tondaęž‰paęž‰ hataęž‰ pou teaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na tondaęž‰paęž‰ mea baalieke.
\q1 Kutupa mo olaęž‰pake homekenaęž‰ lankake siki make na lu honialieke.
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tiki tiki piki hau manumaęž‰ bepolaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki na minaęž‰paęž‰lake pa pokaęž‰tiki pu halieke.
\q1 
\v 21 Kutupa kenke paeyaonaęž‰ haleme tapake wandaęž‰hali ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao yu wia hao halieke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Bielisibulunaęž‰ welemaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeeki
\r (Maka 3ęž‰20-30, Luku 11ęž‰14-23)
\p 
\v 22 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hali homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea epemekeme. Koto some ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke ekimaęž‰ leke holu peao pi na lao piekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo some wamo pieketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke kila handolo hataęž‰ pi epeke tupaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa mo hande mombelemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kutu piaęž‰eki handolo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tolaęž‰tia pominolo alotaęž‰ Do sometaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyeke yaalo paęž‰laęž‰me laa lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 24 Do lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimiki pimanu opua mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do somemaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hoke temoko paeyaonaęž‰ you temoko Bielisibulunaęž‰ welemaęž‰ kone piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Mo haliwekinaęž‰ wimiki hoke honemanu Yesumaęž‰ handolo iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Homeke kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone putupaęž‰ alualu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kenke wandaęž‰hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la haleme ekitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone paelieke. Kutupa homeke da wandaęž‰hali make o homeke tapake sunumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone putupaęž‰ alualu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tapaketaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hapeke na yelieke.
\v 26 Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo Sadaninaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kalale ya alu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu alu pipikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tekilipaęž‰ alu pea aĚ±iĚ± paelieke.
\v 27 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hotiolo hataęž‰ Do somemaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Bielisibulunaęž‰ welemaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me aleme ekinaęž‰ teke aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰eki yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu teliaenaęž‰ yeke wele peake hautaęž‰ epinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ peaasemepe. Mo ikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ pu haleme haumaęž‰ walolotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi na alememe.
\v 28 Diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu teliolo weletaęž‰ Bielisibulunaęž‰ welemaęž‰ na pitolopate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ peaaso haenaęž‰ pitolome. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰pate na handelememe.
\p 
\v 29 Honkopu hake somenaęž‰ dataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pa yambaęž‰la hondaęž‰ pamba pua ipikaęž‰ alemanu miaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo da tekehali ambaęž‰la mina tonkao winaęž‰ laataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ talo pea mea pelieke.
\p 
\v 30 Mandali epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ yaeki na hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaa make mandali epimaęž‰ IĚ± tapu na mombeleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰taęž‰ hoelaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pimiki hoke haumanu make hoke hoke pimanu lo haleme ekimanu make kotoeki paeyao Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa hali epimaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ biki hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki otaęž‰ na paeyaalieke.
\v 32 Mandali epitaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ biki paęž‰taęž‰ pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hoke pi aleme ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Holi Sipitidi hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ame do make wetepe make otaęž‰ na paeyawalieke.
\s1 Ti kilikinaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰eki
\r (Luku 6ęž‰43-45)
\p 
\v 33 Epeke kilikimanu ta laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ epeke ti halaęž‰eki peneme yaasaęž‰me. Pate hoke ti hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hoke kiliki kone talipikie. Ti paeyaonaęž‰ halaęž‰ hautaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiliki aęž‰iliaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ peneme yaalieke.
\v 34 Ketomaęž‰ handeke some hombo ikitaęž‰ hoke some hombo haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ekipa epeke pimanu lo hapaęž‰peke yelemepe. Pa ekipeke. Mo hone paęž‰taęž‰ tumba ulaęž‰eki kone kake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me.
\v 35 Epeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ wiliaęž‰ hone epeke manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piliaęž‰ haumaęž‰ peneme yao walieke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone hoke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ wiliaęž‰ hoke hone manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piliaęž‰ haumaęž‰ peneme yao walieke.
\p 
\v 36 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate tieke opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ leme handiki na piki pimanu paeyao Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰ piki tupaęž‰ kone telipalieke.
\v 37 Neketaęž‰ hoke halie o epeke halie pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leme pi kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea telipeao la kilieke.
\s1 Na handeke hau homeke handaęž‰mono walaęž‰e lemekeeki
\r (Maka 8ęž‰11-12, Luku 11ęž‰29-32)
\p 
\v 38 Mandane Pi Ulaęž‰eki walaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki pitaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi halimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Mo na handeke hau homeke handaęž‰mono nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pie lemekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ koto lemeke pi opuolo alotaęž‰ Aęž‰pei do hoke hau pu haluekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ kiao haleme wandaęž‰halio pa ekipeke handaa mo na handeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ alemepe. Diaęž‰me. Mo ambaęž‰ hande Diona paęž‰taęž‰ pieke yeke na handeke pate hau homeke waloaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie.
\v 40 Hande Dionataęž‰ taęž‰peli tiekenaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ tepo nate tepo pea pitiekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke make mandake tupaęž‰ kone timbaęž‰ tepo nate tepo pea kenke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wilieke.
\v 41 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Ninipa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Dionanaęž‰ waleeke pi opua ikaęž‰ hoke hau minaęž‰paęž‰lao puki laęž‰kaęž‰la haemeke handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ iki laęž‰ mea lopaalieke alome. Pa ekipeke. Ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Diona otaęž‰ lombei piki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ta aęž‰pa halaęž‰ handepe.
\v 42 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Siba kenkenaęž‰ kuini wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hone wopu wieke kini hali Solomonomaęž‰ leeke epeke manaęž‰ pimanu opuluekemaęž‰ papate hao epeeke handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ iki laęž‰ mea lopaalieke. Pa ekipeke. Ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Solomono otaęž‰ lombei piki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ta aęž‰pa halaęž‰ handaęž‰pe.
\s1 Hoke temokomaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la paa epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Luku 11ęž‰24-26)
\p 
\v 43 Hoke temoko maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ puki minaęž‰paęž‰lao alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na opeke kenke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ ipiki pitaęž‰peke epeke da pandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ weiliepate pa na handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 44 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ya da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la polueke laa paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo hande minaęž‰paęž‰layeke dataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hake wamo pea bao epeke hau pea wiliaęž‰eki handilieke.
\v 45 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ pu halaęž‰ hoke haumanu otaęž‰ lombei peao pu hake hoke mandane watake hataęž‰ temokomanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku mea aęž‰paataęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba hao halimikie. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande halimaęž‰ hande ambaęž‰ pieke hoke hau otaęž‰ lombei peake hoke hau pilieke. Kutu piki hautaęž‰ ame do haleme hoke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make opolo ipilieke alome leekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ inkiki hameketonu
\r (Maka 3ęž‰31-35, Luku 8ęž‰19-21)
\p 
\v 46 Yesumaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pimanu panake alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki hameketonu opolo epemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ da hamaęž‰ nane aęž‰pa hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi lomono epenaęž‰e laa honke lemekeme.
\v 47 Kotoeki opuaataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesuo. Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ neke ameĚ±leĚ± pi loluekemaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane aęž‰pa yu wia halememe leekeme.
\v 48 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Epitaęž‰ ya amaęž‰pe o epitaęž‰ ya kame tonupe.
\v 49 Koto pi alo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki wandaęž‰hali maĚ±leke litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya amaęž‰ kame tonutaęž‰ do handaęž‰pe.
\v 50 Mo ya hepeni nane halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu peao haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ya anaęž‰ amaęž‰ kametonue leekeme.
\c 13
\s1 Wae ale manunaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 4ęž‰1-9, Luku 8ęž‰4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰ kone Yesumaęž‰ mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo hande ikali leke mone teaęž‰naęž‰ pua wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walo pitiekeme.
\v 2 Wandaęž‰hali wopu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombelemeke handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ haenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ palai kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitiekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa pimanu wopu waleekeme.
\p Dupa leekeme. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wae alemanu tande loluekemaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tande leaęž‰tiki pulu haenaęž‰ mandane wae manutaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ ba titimaęž‰ aęž‰pa talopu nemekeme.
\v 5 Kutaataęž‰ mandane wae manutaęž‰ toopimanu manda taleeke kenke sikinaęž‰ lopeekeme. Mo kenketaęž‰ aneke na wiekeeki yaalo mo wae sunutaęž‰ koto kone opeekepate ikaęž‰ piki oninaęž‰ tolumaęž‰ wopu na puayeke ekinaęž‰
\v 6 nate talo hataęž‰taęž‰ pou ta hapiekeme.
\v 7 Kutaataęž‰ mandane wae manutaęž‰ tekeke hake ale polu paęž‰taęž‰manu lopeekeme. Kutupa tekeke hake alemanu opaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ hande wae alemanu opolo pieke ekitaęž‰ tombuaeyekeme.
\v 8 Kutu piekepate mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ epeeke kenkenaęž‰ lopeeke handaa napeke epeke tupaęž‰ wiekeeki manutaęž‰ dupae. Mandaneeki 100 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 60 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 30 tupaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 9 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ koto ipikaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi paeyaaso alotaęž‰ Katake lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ wotu opinaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Onkolumaęž‰ pi manumaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ teke
\r (Maka 4ęž‰10-12, Luku 8ęž‰9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰taęž‰ ekipeke onkolumaęž‰ pimaęž‰ la halepe.
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ opua hone wilimipate mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hone na winaęž‰yeke onkolumaęž‰ pi alome.
\v 12 Pa ekipeke. Alaęž‰taęž‰manu ambaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki lombei pinaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰ pao haliaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ milieke. Pate alaęž‰taęž‰manu wopu na wiki natehali sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ alesiki kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea pelieke.
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ do onkolumaęž‰ pimanu laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke alome. Ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate na handelememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opuluekemaęž‰ katake wia pelimipate pa na opu make hone na wilimiki handaa alo alome.
\v 14 Mo hande potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ wape pieke wapenaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ame do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yaalememe. Koto yaaleme ekitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opitolo opitolo halo pelemepate ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ na wilimikie.
\q1 Kutaa make handolo handolo halo pelemepate ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ na handilimikie.
\q1 
\v 15 Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ timbaęž‰ lo make ikaęž‰ katakemanu poko make ikaęž‰ lekemanu handupu pelememe.
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutu piki haumanu na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ epeke hando make ikaęž‰ katakemaęž‰ epeke opu make ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ epeke hone wia hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la epolo pimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki wamo pulu puaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Aisayamaęž‰ kutu piki pi leekepate ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰paęž‰peke yo make ikaęž‰ katakemaęž‰ pi epeke opu piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 17 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ambaęž‰ haemeke potopede haliweki wopumaęž‰ make mandane tikitiki piki haliweki wopumaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ame do handeleme haumanu handuluekemaęž‰ hone wopu pieke taapo haemekepate na handemekeme. Koto haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ do opueleme pimanu make opuluekemaęž‰ hone wopu pieke taapo haemekepate na opimikime.
\s1 Wae nokopaęž‰laęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke la haleekeeki
\r (Maka 4ęž‰13-20, Luku 8ęž‰11-15)
\p 
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wae ale nokopaęž‰laęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi alo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hone wopu uemenaęž‰maęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wopu opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 19 Mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi opitelemepate hone wopu wia na mea mendieleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo hande potaęž‰naęž‰ lopeeke wae manumaęž‰ handelememe. Ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ nokopeeke pi manutaęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± aęž‰pa yokaęž‰ mea pulaęž‰me.
\v 20 Kutupa mo waleme pi opuolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa aĚ±iĚ± mea miniki haleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo hande toopi manda wieke kenkesiki paęž‰taęž‰ lopeeke wae manumaęž‰ handelememe.
\v 21 Mo opiteleme pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki tukiki nane wopu na winaęž‰ alemeke handaa hosiki hao hao peaataęž‰ koto kone paelieke. Pa ekipeke. Mo Pi Seliapo walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kiaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda o kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu halaęž‰leketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kone lopo halememe.
\v 22 Kutupa mo hande tekeke hake pu polu paęž‰taęž‰ lopeeke wae alemanu tupaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi epeke tupaęž‰ opua miniki halemepate do kenkenaęž‰ haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tieke eleke eleke wopu witelemeeki pitaęž‰ mani tieke wopu amu pulueke hone witelemeeki yaapomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi tombuatiki pinaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke kilikimanu na aęž‰ilimikie.
\v 23 Kutu pu halemepate mo waleme pi opuolo epeke mea miniki haleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo epeke kenkenaęž‰ lopeeke wae manumaęž‰ handelememe. Ikaęž‰ kiliki aęž‰elo peleme tupaęž‰taęž‰ dupa. Mandane wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ kilikitaęž‰ 100manu tupaęž‰ mandane ekitaęž‰ 60manu tupaęž‰ mandane ekitaęž‰ 30manu aęž‰eyeke tupaęž‰ halimikie leekeme.
\s1 Hoke waemanu tande leekeeki
\p 
\v 24 Koto la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupiki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ epeke waemanu tande laa peekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa peeke hoki nanetaęž‰ timba maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali u pelia pemeke nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hali homeke aęž‰pa mo hande epeke wae taapunaęž‰ hoke wae tande laęž‰ pamba peekeme.
\v 26 Mo hande epeke wae alemanu opa napeke honke pankeeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande hoke ambu apaęž‰tao opekeeki manutaęž‰ peneme yeekeme.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande e teke halinaęž‰ e pokaeyeke haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ enaęž‰ epeke kiliki homeke tande lepate do hoke ambu manutaęž‰ ekipa aęž‰pa hao paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ do hoke wae tande alo piaęž‰me leekeme. Koto leeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hoke ambu manutaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ talo baalo pomonope laa lotaęž‰ pimiki handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰
\v 29 ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Mo hoke ambu talemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke kilikimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ talo baamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰
\v 30 mo napeke naa piliaęž‰ nate epenaęž‰ yu wia hataęž‰ hokeeki epekeeki pa apaęž‰tao openaęž‰e. Koto nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo napeke mombaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke ambu ambaęž‰la talo tonka tonka pea tia pua panane yankaęž‰paęž‰peke lolueke. Kutaataęž‰ mo epeke napekemanu talaataęž‰ ya amu pitolo da paęž‰taęž‰ wiaęž‰paęž‰peke lolueke leaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Masidadi waenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 4ęž‰30-32, Luku 13ęž‰18-19)
\p 
\v 31 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ la halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupiki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ mo kiĚ±miĚ±leĚ±maęž‰ handeke ale masidadi kiliki nokopa peekeme.
\v 32 Mo kilikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hodikale siki yeke kiliki yekepate ipikaęž‰ opolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mandane wae manunaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ tombo lombei peao opaa ti tupaęž‰ halieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ bamanu aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ paleke paęž‰taęž‰manu ikaęž‰ dakemanu halimikie.
\s1 Palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰ yisitinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Luku 13ęž‰20-21)
\p 
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa la haleekeme dupa. Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ yisitimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ mo yisitimanu mea sini tieke tumbiki palaowa tapu dakole pealieke. Kutu piliaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ koto palaowa paeyao pombei ya halieke leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ waleeke ekitaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pimaęž‰ homeke waleekeeki
\r (Maka 4ęž‰33-34)
\p 
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ waleeke pi paeyaotaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰maęž‰ homeke waleekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi homeke siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pimaęž‰ na leke pa na la haleekeme. Diaęž‰me. Pi paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pimaęž‰ homeke waleekeme.
\v 35 Koto pieke ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande potopede halimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimanu yaenaęž‰ yeke piekeme. Koto hande potopede halimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ manumaęž‰ homeke lolueke.
\q1 Do kenke wepia wieke ane kini pu mea aęž‰pa ame do halome anemaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ peneme yao la halueke leekeme.
\s1 Hande hoke waenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke
\p 
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ koto mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Mo hande enaęž‰ nokopeeke wae alenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke niki la kuelenaęž‰e laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ kotaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande epeke wae alemanu tande leeke hali tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekee.
\v 38 Kutupa mo e tupaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkee. Mo epeke waemanu tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halie. Mo hande hoke ambumanu tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke Sadaninaęž‰ wandaęž‰halie.
\v 39 Kutupa mo hande hoke wae tande leeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki some tupaęž‰taęž‰ Sadanie. Mo napeke mombaęž‰lapeke nate tupaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke paelo paęž‰laęž‰ekie. Kutupa napeke mombeleeke haliweki tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande enisolo haliwekie.
\v 40 Pa mo hande hoke ambumanu yoka mea tonkao pua tinaęž‰ mombaęž‰la yankolo pieke tupaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do kenke ya paeliaęž‰ dinaęž‰ make mandake hau kone pilieke.
\p 
\v 41 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolomanu tapaalieke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali pitaęž‰ mo hoke haumanu pu tiaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimanu paeyao tonkaęž‰naęž‰ paeyao yokilimikie.
\v 42 Kutaataęž‰ mo hoke wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ mo enisolo manumaęž‰ tonumaęž‰ ti tieke to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ mea lopaalimikie. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kake lenkene laaso hataęž‰ eĚ± wi lo halimikie.
\v 43 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau peleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo natenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tupaęž‰ pu halimikie. Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ katake lombeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do pi otaęž‰ opinaęž‰e.
\s1 Ti teke pitaęž‰laęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 44 Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰e. Hali homekemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ e mopunaęž‰ pa peekepate kone ambaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ ti teke pimikieki handaęž‰ wiekeme. Kutupataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ paa aęž‰nkaęž‰laęž‰ pambaataęž‰ mo ti teke wieke e hambaęž‰peke mani mandaneeki wopu muluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alemanu paeyao mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapao mani meaataęž‰ koto kone mo ti teke piekeeki handeeke e hambuluekemaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.
\s1 Sekete hapeke belekenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 45 Hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ make yaęž‰laęž‰me. Hali homekemaęž‰ mo mani tieke miaęž‰peke sekete hapeke beleke seliapo weitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 46 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ koto beleke teke otaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pupapeke seliapo pikieki handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto beleke teke hambuluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapaa tapaa pilieke.
\s1 Tenki nunaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰
\pi1 
\v 47 Hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ make yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mandane taęž‰peli mu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tenki nu tieke mea ikali lekenaęž‰ lopao taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki taęž‰pelimanu paeyao wopu mondu haleme.
\v 48 Kutupa mo tenki nu aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumbiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikali teaęž‰ nane yolaęž‰ mea wia hataęž‰ hokeeki epekeeki telipa u halememe. Mo epekeeki manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kawasomanu paęž‰taęž‰ lopaotaęž‰ hokeeki manutaęž‰ bao halememe.
\v 49 Kutupa mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone pilieke. Mo hande enisolo manumaęž‰ opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ mo epeke wandaęž‰hali taapu halimi hoke wandaęž‰hali talopu mea mombaęž‰lao
\v 50 mo ti tieke to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaęž‰nialimikie. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kake lenkene laaso hataęž‰ eĚ± wi lo halimikie.
\s1 Ambaęž‰ epeke ale pitaęž‰ panake epeke ale yaapo
\p 
\v 51 Yesumaęž‰ iki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do alo pinaęž‰ tekemanu iki hone wilimipe laa leekeeki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe lemekeme.
\v 52 Koto lemeke opitolo Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke Lo Pimanu walo halaęž‰ hali hataęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hau paeyao miniki halaęž‰ hali make hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo da tiekenaęž‰ tekehali tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mombaęž‰la nu pindu hao u halaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua ambaęž‰ epeke alemanu make panake epeke alemanu make apaęž‰tao mea aęž‰pa peneme yaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰ handilieke leekeme.
\s1 Naęž‰saęž‰tete da wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu kiaemekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰1-6, Luku 4ęž‰16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Koto onkolumaęž‰ pimanu paeyao la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao
\v 54 ipikaęž‰ teke da nane paa peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeeki opitolotaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ penkili pimikime. Do somemaęž‰ dupiki manaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ opiaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pualu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo hande ipikaęž‰ pieke na handeke hau manunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ ekipape laataęž‰
\v 55 Ipikitaęž‰ mo hande da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ eiyeke kutupa ipikaęž‰ inkikitaęž‰ Meti diaęž‰yeke yekea. Ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Diaęž‰mesi Diosepe Saimono Diudasi do hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰naęž‰ hameke diaęž‰yeke yekea.
\v 56 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ beliki tonu make niki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ na halemeke yekea laataęž‰ Do somemaęž‰ do alaęž‰ pi paeyaotaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ mea paęž‰laęž‰pe laataęž‰
\v 57 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki kiaemekeme. Kutu pimiki ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ biki wiliaęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ teke da nane o ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ biki na wilieke leekeme.
\v 58 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu na tulaemeke handaa kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo na handeke haumanu iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wopu na piekeme.
\c 14
\s1 Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dioni homeekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰14-29, Luku 9ęž‰7-9)
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande Kaęž‰lili kenke handeteke hayeke hali Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰ pi laemeke ekimanu opuaataęž‰
\v 2 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande luaęž‰ hali Dioni paa daęž‰taa aęž‰pa halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ wele tieke wopu pitolo hataęž‰ mo na handeke haumanu pitolo pilaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Do pi leeke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hosiki ambaęž‰ leke Hetodimaęž‰ Dioni daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mininaęž‰ laataęž‰ senipumaęž‰ tonkao dipula mea pitaenaęž‰ leekeme. Koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰ epeeke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo hande Hetodimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke Pilipinaęž‰ weteke Hetodiasi mieke ekimaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 4 Nate mandaneeki ninaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ Do wandaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ ale ekitaęž‰ hoke hau piteleme laa pi wopu laęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 5 Koto leeke pitaęž‰maęž‰ kone Hetodimaęž‰ Dioni luekemaęž‰ piekepate mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke. Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ honemaęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ otaęž‰ potopede halie hone wimikime.
\p 
\v 6 Hetodinaęž‰ mendieke natenaęž‰ ne tieke pambeekeme. Kutu pieke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Hetodiasinaęž‰ wanekemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ liekeme. Kutu pieke handaa Hetodimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wotu pieke handaa
\v 7 mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi tieke laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie laa honke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ kulueke laa laęž‰ witolome leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ doeki lapeke laa hone u tiaeyekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo wandikimaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ honke alotaęž‰ Ame do siki kone mo hande bapitaisi peao hayeke some Dioninaęž‰ you tunkula kawasonaęž‰ wia IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kie leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto pi opitolo Hetodimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homekepate ipikaęž‰ laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kimisu wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ ipiki yaęž‰laęž‰ meaęž‰peke yeke handaa ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do wandikinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau pua peape leekeme.
\v 10 Koto leeke pi opuaataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pua Dioninaęž‰ make tunkulaataęž‰
\v 11 ipikaęž‰ youtaęž‰ kawaso manda wia mea aęž‰pa mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ halemekeme. Mo wandikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua haleekeme.
\v 12 Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ toko aęž‰pa mea tia maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua hoiyaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ la haluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 5 daoseni haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ne haleekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰30-44, Luku 9ęž‰10-17, Dioni 6ęž‰1-14)
\p 
\v 13 Dioni liaęž‰me lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao kawasonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mea keneme paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Ipiki peekeeki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opitolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ teke damanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo ikali teaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ ankemaęž‰ Yesu telimea pemekeme.
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ mo kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰lao kenke nane opolo pulu hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Kutupieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo homaęž‰ pa wieke wandaęž‰hali mea tiaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto welealotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Do anetaęž‰ keneme nanee. Ametaęž‰ nate paetaęž‰laęž‰me. Da paęž‰taęž‰manu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne hambaęž‰tiki penaęž‰ tapaa tapaa pie lemekeme.
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Na penaęž‰ leke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 17 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paa Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ palaowa walaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰peli yaapo pea homeke ulaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea ipupe laataęž‰
\v 19 mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao ambunaęž‰ pitinaęž‰ lape leekeme.
\p Kutaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande palaowa walaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰ make hande taęž‰peli yaapo make miniki hataęž‰ oli ya nane handaęž‰liao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laataęž‰ palaowa walaęž‰ pindi pindi pea ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mea wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰yeke hale hale piekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ naakaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰ weleke talaęž‰me lemekeme. Mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pa wieke putupilikimanu meaataęž‰ alaęž‰ta 12 tumbaemekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa mo hande palaowa walaęž‰sunu nemeke haliwekitaęž‰ mo wekiwandaęž‰ na apaęž‰take pa haliweki homeketaęž‰ 5 daoseni halimaęž‰ nemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ikali manda yapeekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰45-52, Dioni 6ęž‰15-21)
\p 
\v 22 Kutaataęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰hali tapaaluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke nane telimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo kawasonaęž‰ pita iki ambaęž‰la mone teaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hape laataęž‰
\v 23 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali tapao hoki nanetaęž‰ oli pote elinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ siki yeni puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰meiyekeme. Kutupa nate pambolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ siki oli paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.
\v 24 Koto nate lekenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kawasotaęž‰ mo ikali leke tukikinaęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ po tiekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wenoko nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa ambulaaso hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kawaso wopu mea aęž‰meiyaaso lopaaso piekeme.
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰puluekemaęž‰ okonaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki haemeke alenaęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ ikali manda ankenaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 26 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki ikali manda ankenaęž‰ epeekeeki handolo iki paeyaomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homolo hataęž‰ Temokoe laa eĚ± wi lemekeme.
\v 27 Kutu pimikipate koto kone Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Honkopu hapee. Dotaęž‰ IĚ±e. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pepee leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Koto leeke Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ neke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± tiao do ikali manda aęž‰pa neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pono nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± epo laa lae leekeme.
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Epoe leeketaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ tiao mo ikali manda kini pu mea Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate
\v 30 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande po tilipumaęž‰ piekeeki handolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Kutupa mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki kini pea honki alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ± tambaęž‰ minie laa wi leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Kotaęž‰ koto kone Yesu ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipa moneao taęž‰nkaęž‰paęž‰ minolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hosiki hone tulaake someo. Pa ekipeke hone yaapo yaapo wipe leekeme.
\v 32 Koto laataęž‰ ipiliki telipinaęž‰ mo kawasonaęž‰ pitulu pepeketaęž‰ mo po tieke u pa lopeekeme.
\v 33 Mo kawasonaęž‰ pitimiki disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pieke hau handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyaaso alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰e. Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee laa lemekeme.
\s1 Kenesatete nane pemekeeki
\r (Maka 6ęž‰53-56)
\p 
\v 34 Mo ikali leke tunkulaęž‰ moneao mone teaęž‰naęž‰ hayeke Kenesatete da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme.
\v 35 Mo paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke handolo hataęž‰ hone wimiki ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo da teke nepoko nepoko haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰manu haemeke yeni hapa wimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mea ipupaęž‰e laa pi tapaa tapaa pimikime.
\v 36 Kutupa mo pa haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki honke laaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ dau honiki wataenaęž‰ lapeke lemekeme. Koto leeke handaa mo wataemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni manutaęž‰ tande lemekeme.
\c 15
\s1 Apaęž‰meinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu
\r (Maka 7ęž‰1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki make mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki make Diutuseleme da minaęž‰paęž‰lao aęž‰pa Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 2 Pa ekipeke mo nakaęž‰ hoki nane telieleme haliweki nikaęž‰ ateke meiyekenaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu ekipeke na opitolo pitelemepe. Ikaęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mo nikaęž‰ pimanu ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki na tandepo halememe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ mo pi hombo peaaso iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutaa make pa ekipeke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki kiao pa ikaęž‰ waleme pimanu kone tolu halemepe.
\v 4 Do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ hapeke laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ liaęž‰paęž‰peke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰pate
\v 5 pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke alemanu miniki halaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiliki kulu puaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ laęž‰ wia halome leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pi opitolo hataęž‰
\v 6 ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰taęž‰ tambaęž‰ miaęž‰peke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ Pinaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa lo halememe. Kutupa koto piteme hau manutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ waleme pimanu kone teli mea pu haluekemaęž‰ yeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu hoki walo halememe.
\v 7 Ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ makeaaso hau pu haleme some hombo yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Hande Aisayamaęž‰ ikinaęž‰ laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ leekeeki otaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 8 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pulu pimiki ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ homeke ya biki mea aęž‰meiyalo pelemepate ikaęž‰ puki manumaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lao otaęž‰ panane winaęž‰ lelememe.
\q1 
\v 9 Mo ya biki mea aęž‰meiyao yeni piteme ekitaęž‰ pa pahameke pitelememe. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ wepia wimiki manaęž‰ pimanu kone yaka laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi tupaęž‰ walo halememe laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki haĚ±iĚ± peaasaęž‰ ekimanu
\r (Maka 7ęž‰14-23)
\p 
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰yeke wi laęž‰mipi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya pi opua hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 11 Wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hama nane ulaęž‰ alemanu mea nalomaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ iki na hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰pate tukiki nane wia kake paęž‰taęž‰ opolu baasaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰hali hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Koto leeke hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ pimi ekitaęž‰ neke na handepe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ le pi manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homayaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ na nokopeke pa opaęž‰laęž‰ waemanu paeyao yokilieke laa Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 14 Pinaęž‰maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiaęž‰paęž‰pe. Ikitaęž‰ mo leke holu piki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke holu piki you haliweki halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ leke holu piki somemaęž‰ mo leke holupiki some maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku mea peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiliki telipunaęž‰ hombo paęž‰taęž‰ hopulu paleke mandake lopilipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto ale pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ niki wopu la kiaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ iki make pi teke hone na witelemepe leekeme.
\v 17 Nalaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ hali homekenaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitaęž‰taęž‰ hoke ale yapilieke hone na witelemepe.
\v 18 Pate ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ opolo ipu halaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki tukiki nanemaęž‰ opolu baalo ipulaęž‰me. Kotoeki manumaęž‰ kone ipiki haĚ±iĚ± peaasaęž‰me.
\v 19 Kotaęž‰ koto some ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ pita ipulaęž‰ hoke hone manumaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki haumanu pu tialieke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ linaęž‰ lo o wandaęž‰ pake naęž‰naęž‰ lo o hali yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ kone hoke hau pinaęž‰ lo o pake naęž‰naęž‰ lo o yapiki hau pinaęž‰ lo o wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki hoeyaenaęž‰ lo
\v 20 do hau manumaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hoke hali haenaęž‰ lolo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo na tandepeke kikimaęž‰ ne mea nalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki na hoeyaasaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰ homekenaęž‰ hone tulaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 7ęž‰24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Taiya Saidoni daoni yaapo nane peekeme.
\v 22 Koto kenke nane hayeke Keinani wandaęž‰ homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± wi laa aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekeo. Ya wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pilaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipiki otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 23 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi homeke siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na leekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa honke alo alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki teliolo hataęž‰ wi wopu laęž‰ paleke ipulaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰naęž‰ tapae lemekepate
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo hande Isulai tapake alu pulaęž‰ sipisipimanu leke haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tapaaleke handaa epolome leekeme.
\v 25 Do pi opitolotaęž‰ koto kone mo wandaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniao lopolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ± tambaęž‰ mie leekeme.
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaasotaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Weki wandikinaęž‰ ne paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea kika paęž‰taęž‰ lopa moneaasaęž‰ hautaęž‰ epeke hau diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 27 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Koto pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alepate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ne naa pelimi hoki nanemaęž‰taęž‰ popumanu minaęž‰pelete pilimi ekimanu kika manumaęž‰ talopu nemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 28 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hone wopu tulaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ pealueke leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ koto alo haenaęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ waneketaęž‰ paa epeke tupaęž‰ tiao hayekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kaęž‰lili ikali leke nepoko lopaęž‰laęž‰ pua mo peiyene paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰meiya pua pitiekeme.
\v 30 Koto pua pitinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tieke wopu Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombelemekeme. Iki ipulu hataęž‰taęž‰ dolaęž‰pake piki leke holupiki anke lupa wiki pi na leke make kutupa mandane yenimanu haemeke wandaęž‰hali wopu make Yesunaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa wimiki handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeao paeyaeyekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo pi na leke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi lemekeeki hando make kiki anke lupa wiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paa epeke tupaęž‰ haemekeeki hando make dolaęž‰pake piki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paa epea pomimikieki hando make leke holu piki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke ki la epeke tupaęž‰ hando pu pimiki eki paeyao handolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ leke opo handaęž‰ hake wiataęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 4 daoseni haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ne haleekeeki
\r (Maka 8ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰mipi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ eĚ± alaęž‰me leekeme. Hoto teponaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haememe. Kutupa ametaęž‰ napeke ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ da ninaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ paleke tapaa tapaa puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ potaęž‰ hopikinaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ pua homilimikie leekeme.
\v 33 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ netaęž‰ hando pate mea halomanaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Palaowa walaęž‰ ekipu wia halemepe lotaęž‰ piekeme. Koto haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Palaowa walaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ make taęž‰peli siki yaapo homeke pea wia halomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali wopu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenkenaęž‰ pitaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 36 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo palaowa walaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ make mo taęž‰peli siki mu peataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi ambaęž‰la laataęž‰ pindi pindi peaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pinaęž‰ yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 37 Kutu pieketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ naa weleke haemekeme. Kutaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ naa putu piliki wiekeeki mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ meaataęž‰ alaęž‰ta watake hataęž‰ tumbaemekeme.
\v 38 Mo hande palaowa walaęž‰ sunu nemeke haliwekitaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ na apaęž‰take haliweki homeketaęž‰ 4 daoseni halimaęž‰ nemekeme.
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ iki paeyao tapaa tapaa peaataęž‰ koto kone ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pita Maęž‰kaęž‰dani kenke nane pemekeme.
\c 16
\s1 Wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ handomono pie lemekeeki
\r (Maka 8ęž‰11-13, Luku 12ęž‰54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki make Saęž‰dusi haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ anke yololo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ do wele aęž‰ndaęž‰ ku hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomono mo welemaęž‰ na handeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pie lemekeme.
\v 2 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaasotaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Nate pambolo pulu hataęž‰ we piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Beliataęž‰ epeke nate telieke lo halememe.
\v 3 Kutaa koto tupaęž‰ kone da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso make ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nate we pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Lako ipuluekemaęž‰ taa pitaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e lo halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli yanaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu handolo hataęž‰ dupiki nate telieke laa laęž‰ u hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ame do iki paęž‰taęž‰ pitolo haumanu handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 4 Aęž‰paęž‰e. Do you hoke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ekipeke handaa mo na handeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ alemepe. Diaęž‰me. Mo ambaęž‰ hande Diona paęž‰taęž‰ pieke yeke na handeke hau homeke waloaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie. Koto laataęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\s1 Walaęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 8ęž‰14-21)
\p 
\v 5 Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki mo ikali leke tunkula mone teaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ palaowamanu hone yonkaęž‰lao na mea pemekeme.
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ manaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wotu hapaęž‰peke. Paęž‰tisi Saęž‰dusi tapake yaaponaęž‰ palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰eki wotu handaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 7 Koto leekeeki opuolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hone wia pi pi lemeke ekitaęž‰ dupa. Nikitaęž‰ palaowa na mea epomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wimikieki handolo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne diaęž‰ yaęž‰leke ekipeke pi pi alemepe. Ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hosiki siki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wia aĚ±iĚ± na handelemepe. Na niminaasemepe. Mo hande palaowa walaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰ 5 daoseni haliweki pindi pindi peaowaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ putu pilikimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰ta ekipu tumbaemepe.
\v 10 Kutupa mo hande palaowa walaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ hande 4 daoseni haliweki halomaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ putu pilikimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰ta ekipu tumbaemepe leekeme.
\v 11 Ekieki pea ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witemepe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ palaowanaęž‰ na loaęž‰pate pa mo Paęž‰tisitonu pitaęž‰ Saęž‰dusi haliweki yaaponaęž‰ palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰ yisitimaęž‰ handeke pimanu alemeeki handeteke hapaęž‰ laa alome.
\v 12 Koto pi opitolotaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo palaowa paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ yisitinaęž‰ na leekepate otaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi Saęž‰dusi tapake yaaponaęž‰ waleme manaęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone wimikime.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Ketisoe leekeeki
\r (Maka 8ęž‰27-30, Luku 9ęž‰18-21)
\p 
\v 13 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Sesatia Pilipai da kenke nane pemekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ epi alemepe leekeme.
\v 14 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionie alememe. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Elaidiae alememe. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Dietemaiya o mandane potopede halie alememe lemekeme.
\v 15 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epi alemepe leekeme.
\v 16 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke Ketisoe leekeme.
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Saimono Dioninaęž‰ eiyekeo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hombo peaeme. Pa ekipeke do otaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ hombo peae ekitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na la kiaęž‰pate ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ tiki tiki kiaęž‰me.
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ dupa alome. Neketaęž‰ Pidae. (nikaęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ Toopie) Koto toopi mandaataęž‰ ya siosi aęž‰elueke. Kutupa mo homo halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ kone koto siosi otaęž‰ na bepolao halieke.
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ potaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ kimanu kulueke. Koto ekinaęž‰ do kenke nane hataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto haunaęž‰ pi witaęž‰laęž‰eki kone oli hepeni nane make pi wilieke. Kutupa do kenke nane hataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane haumanu pa mone pinaęž‰ paekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pinaęž‰ pasaęž‰ hau kone oli hepeni nane make pa pinaęž‰ palieke leekeme.
\v 20 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ iki hando alo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketiso yekeme laa wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Yesu ipikaęž‰ tanda mea homaęž‰pekeeki
\r (Maka 8ęž‰31â€”9ęž‰1, Luku 9ęž‰22-27)
\p 
\v 21 Koto natenaęž‰ kini pu meataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo tonu peneme yao alo hataęž‰ dupa leekeme. IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane polueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo you haliwekimaęž‰ make yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make IĚ± tanda tieke otaęž‰ wotu kilimikie leekeme. IĚ± kiao limikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ homuluepate hoto tepo naku paęž‰taęž‰ wia paa daęž‰taa tiao halueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Yesu hosiki mo pate leke hatuku mea pua hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me Tekehalio. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ kutu piki hau otaęž‰ na epenaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme.
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mina Pida handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sadani. Neke puma. Neketaęž‰ ya potaęž‰ aęž‰mbaluekemaęž‰ taapeleme. Pa ekipeke. Do nakaęž‰ wili hone manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ na ipulaęž‰pate pa hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Koto la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ya hoki nane toluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone hone ulaęž‰ ekimanu tunkulaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mea tia ya hoki nane telinaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 25 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki homeke miniki hao haluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone alupalieke. Kutu piliaęž‰pate IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki alupinaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ daęž‰taa hao halieke leekeme.
\v 26 Hali epimaęž‰ do kenke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipikaęž‰eki winaęž‰ la haliaęž‰pate kone ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki alupaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ aleke miliaęž‰pe. Diaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na milieke. Ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki paa muluekemaęž‰ topo peapeke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 27 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke ipikaęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± taapunaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo hatuku aĚ±iĚ± kutaa kone ipilieke. Kutaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homeke homekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haeme hau manunaęž‰ anaęž‰ piki yenki kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pilieke.
\v 28 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi la kitolo alome. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ Kini hali hataęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ do haleme mandane wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ ambi na homeke pa halimikie alome leekeme.
\c 17
\s1 Yesu wonu piliekeeki
\r (Maka 9ęž‰2-13, Luku 9ęž‰28-36)
\p 
\v 1 Hoto yunki mindiki hataęž‰ hao Yesumaęž‰ Pida pitaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Dioni hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ handaęž‰ meataęž‰ pote tumiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua ikaęž‰siki haemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ pelia haenaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ loke wonu piliekeme. Ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ nate paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ daumanu make paĚ±aĚ± peaataęž‰ hake wopu piekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa Elaidia Mosesi yaapo opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pi pi alo haemekeme. Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ koto hoki nane tolu haemeke hali tepomaęž‰ handemekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ sale da tepo aęž‰eyono lae laataęž‰ Homeke nakaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Elaidianaęž‰eki pea aęž‰eyono lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutu piki pi alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± piki koa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki aęž‰pa tu peaaso haenaęž‰ mo koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ koto yaka puki piki weki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu homolome. Ipikaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰paęž‰pekee laęž‰niaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make epeekeeki opu haotaęž‰ mo disaipolo hali tepomaęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ wopu homolo hataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ puki yama lopemekeme.
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa iki wataaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke tiaapee leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leeke mo hali tepomaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ liao handemekepate maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hake Yesu homeke hayeke handemekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Potenaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niaaso haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oli hande upamaęž‰ handeke nono pimi hautaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke laataęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ homaa paa tiao haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leeke pi opitolo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la Elaidia ipilieke lo halemepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la Elaidia otaęž‰ ipilieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau paeyao tikitiki yao winaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 12 Kutu piliepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Elaidiataęž‰ ambaęž‰ epeaęž‰pate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Elaidiae hone wopu na witolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ hone pieke ekimanu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pimikime. Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto mandake piki hoke haumanu kone pilimikie alome leekeme.
\v 13 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto leeke pi opitolotaęž‰ mo alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo hande Dioni Bapitaisi paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰me hone wimikime.
\s1 Hoke temokomaęž‰ hoeyaeyeke weki Yesumaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 9ęž‰14-29, Luku 9ęž‰37-43)
\p 
\v 14 Iki tonkopumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰
\v 15 alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Ya weki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke laataęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ lu lopao mea keao weki yaalo tanaęž‰ eleke eleke ti talaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ikali paęž‰taęž‰ make lu lopatiki pu halaęž‰me.
\v 16 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epoaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki epeapeke na yeaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hone wopu na tulaake otaęž‰ puki takaęž‰lake wandaęž‰halie. IĚ±taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hao pua hando natenaęž‰ hao na luaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pa pu hamenaęž‰ kiaotaęž‰ hando natenaęž‰ tunkuluaęž‰pe laataęž‰ Mo wekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea epoe leekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ Mo hoke temoko hando alo hataęž‰ mo weki minaęž‰paęž‰lae leeke handaataęž‰ mo hoke temokomaęž‰ mo weki minaęž‰paęž‰layekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ pa koto tomaęž‰naęž‰ kone mo weki epea tiao hayekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Yesu ipikaęž‰ siki haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke handa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hoke temoko tolu liaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipa piaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ aneke hapu na tulaemeke handa piaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ mo kiĚ±miĚ±leĚ±maęž‰ handeke ale masidadi waemaęž‰ handekeeki wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do pote paęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Mo pate leke pue laa la halemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ monealieke. Kutu piki hone tulalimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰paęž‰peke yelimikie.
\v 21 [Pate dupiki hoke temoko toluekemaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo nee pi wia hataęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki homekemaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.]
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homa tialo piekeeki paa la haleekeeki
\r (Maka 9ęž‰30-32, Luku 9ęž‰43-45)
\p 
\v 22 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paeyao Kaęž‰lili nane aęž‰pa mombelemeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hosiki wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ haliweki oto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 23 Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki limikie. Kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ homaęž‰liepate pa hoto tepo wia paa daęž‰taalieke leekeme. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homemekeme.
\s1 Mo Tembolo danaęž‰ dakisi mani wimikieki
\p 
\v 24 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki hatuku Kapeneami da opolo epemeketaęž‰ mo tembolo dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki aęž‰pa Pida paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ walaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ tembolo dakisi mani lopao halepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Pidamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe. Lopao halaęž‰me leekeme. Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi ambaęž‰la alo alotaęž‰ Saimonoo nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ eki hone wilipe laataęž‰ Do kenkenaęž‰ handeteke haleme Kini haliwekimaęž‰ epi ameda paęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mani meaęž‰tiki pu halimipe. Ikaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kone meaęž‰tiki pilimikipe o tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ meaęž‰tiki pilimikipe.
\p 
\v 26 Pidamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke meaęž‰tiki pilimikie leekeme. Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kini halinaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ dakisi na wilimikie.
\v 27 Patetaęž‰ do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ pua nakaęž‰ kimai lopaapeke. Kutaataęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ endilipi taęž‰pelitaęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ kake ankoto peaataęž‰ koto kake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ silipa mani homeke handaęž‰ wilimikie. Koto manimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ya tembolo dakisi make nakaęž‰eki make anaęž‰ pilieke. Kotoeki mea pua dikaęž‰ dakisi halaęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 18
\s1 Hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ tumiki halitaęž‰ epipe
\r (Maka 9ęž‰33-37, Luku 9ęž‰46-48)
\p 
\v 1 Koto tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ epitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke halaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Koto lemeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ weki siki homeke wilaęž‰ meaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki nanemaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 3 Kutaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone topo pinaęž‰ lenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo weki siki leke na haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na hondaęž‰ pambilimikie.
\v 4 Epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone pandaęž‰ puniaaso hataęž‰ homu pea do weki siki leke halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tumiki hali halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 5 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ dupiki weki siki ya bikinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa handaęž‰ milieke.
\p 
\v 6 Hali epimaęž‰ do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme wekiwandiki sunu homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pinaęž‰yeke pu tiaenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halinaęž‰ make paęž‰taęž‰ toopi hombeleke mea endiataęž‰ homenaęž‰ mo dawala nokaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 7 Aęž‰pei. Do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hoke hau pinaęž‰yeke ulaęž‰ hoke haumanu ulaęž‰me. Dupiki haumanu aęž‰paęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate aęž‰paęž‰e mo hau epenaęž‰ alaęž‰ halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke yenki milieke.
\p 
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ o nakaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kiki o koto anke tunkulu baapeke. Kiki homeke o anke homeke homeke hataęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epelieke. Pate neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kiki yaapo pa haenaęž‰ lo o anke yaapo pa haenaęž‰ lo pea haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke mo na paeke ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoelieke.
\v 9 Nakaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto leke yokaęž‰ mea baapeke. Leke homeke homeke hataęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epelieke. Leke yaapo pa haenaęž‰ lo pea haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke mo ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoelieke.
\s1 Sipisipi alu pieke onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Luku 15ęž‰3-7)
\p 
\v 10 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki wekiwandiki sunu paęž‰taęž‰ pa alemaęž‰ handali minaęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke alome. Pa ekipeke. Mo wekiwandiki ikaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ enisolo tonumaęž‰ mo ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ handeteke hao halememe alome.
\v 11 [Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ mo alu peleme wandaęž‰hali weiya handaęž‰ wia daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me.]
\p 
\v 12 Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ 100 sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke haliaęž‰pate homeke hondo alupiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki pilieke hone witemepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa haliaęž‰ 99 sipisipimanu mo peiyene teaęž‰naęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo alupiaęž‰eki weilu pelieke.
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo alupiaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo na alu piki pa haleme ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homiliepate pa mo handaęž‰ wiekeeki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu homilieke.
\v 14 Pa do mandake tupaęž‰ kone mo nakaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ make do wekiwandiki sunu homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ alu pinaęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰me alome leekeme.
\s1 Hoke hau pilie kame epeaapekeeki
\p 
\v 15 Nakaęž‰ kamemaęž‰ neke hoeyaasaęž‰ hoke hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰ hokeeki walaęž‰peke. Pate peneme na piki ipilikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi opua telia piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo kametaęž‰ neke nane epenaęž‰ lelipikie.
\v 16 Pate nakaęž‰ pi na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa pua hali homeke o yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ titinaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ le pi alupaamaęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰ ulaęž‰ hali yaapo o teponaęž‰ pimaęž‰ hone u tiatiki pinaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 17 Kutu pilimipate iki paeyaonaęž‰ pi na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰ hau paeyao siosi wandaęž‰hali mombilimi ale paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰peke. Kutaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ pi na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ mataasaęž‰ hali o aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰ lapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke nane alaęž‰taęž‰ o hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pi wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pi witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ oli hepeni nane make pi wilieke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke nane alaęž‰taęž‰ o hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pi na wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hepeni nane make pi na wilieke.
\p 
\v 19 Pa ametaęž‰ do pi make apaęž‰taaso iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Iki paeyao tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ epi yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo peaęž‰peke hau homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ do pate puluekemaęž‰ epenaęž‰e laa homeke hone wia hataęž‰ yeni pipikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ oli ya hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ opua ipilikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peawalieke.
\v 20 Pa ekipeke wandaęž‰hali yaapo o tepomaęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ mombelemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake halueke leekeme.
\s1 Hoke hau hone na yonkaęž‰laasaęž‰ halinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 21 Koto tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Yaka kamemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau peaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tanaęž‰ ekipu paeyaaluepe. Tanaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekepate
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Hoto wataake hataęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa hoto paeyao otaęž‰ pa paeyaaso paeyaaso pu hapeke.
\p 
\v 23 Pa ekipeke. Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kini hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ tondiki manutaęž‰ tikitiki yaalueke hone wiekeme.
\v 24 Kotoeki kini pu mea pokuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali homeke hatuku epemekeme. Koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kini halinaęž‰ 10 milioni kina tondiki mea hayekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa koto ipikaęž‰ tondiki paeyaapeke mani na wieke handaataęž‰ mo Kini halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hali ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alemanu paeyao make mo tondiki paeyaenaęž‰yeke mani muluekemaęž‰ iki paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pahameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake haenaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapaapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 26 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo e pokaeyeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kininaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tumiki yotuao pandaęž‰ puniaaso honke alo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ waleke kikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo tondiki paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ epeao kulueke laa honke leekeme.
\v 27 Koto leekeeki opitolo hataęž‰ mo Kini halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pa pinaęž‰e laa Paotaęž‰ pa mo hande tondiki tieke make pinaęž‰ laa kiao hone yonkaęž‰lao ipiki paa tapaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Kutu pieke mo hande somemaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ Kini hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama peekeme. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ 100 kina tondiki miono leeke haleeke mo Kini halinaęž‰ e mandake pokaepeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaęž‰hande piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto e mandake pokaepeke somenaęž‰ make daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina ipikaęž‰ pendoko teke yokaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ya neke paęž‰taęž‰ kolo tondikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa na minaęž‰paęž‰lake otaęž‰ paeyao kima leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Mo e mandake pokaepeke some ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaaso honke alo alotaęž‰ Kameo. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ waleke kikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo tondiki paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kulueke leekeme.
\v 30 Koto leekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto pi tombuao aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ na homeke mo somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tondiki paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kone pa kinaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ pa dipula mea lopaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Kutu pieke hautaęž‰ mo hande Kini halinaęž‰ e pokaemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kini hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo hau paeyao pua la haleekeme.
\v 32 Mo Kini halimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ mo hande hali epenaęž‰ wi leekeme. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke hau piki e pokaasaęž‰ halie. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homee laa honke leeki homeke homekenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande nakaęž‰ tondiki tieke paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ pa paeyaowaęž‰me.
\v 33 Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ e mandake pokaepe some paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke alee laataęž‰
\v 34 mo Kini halimaęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo hataęž‰ mo hande somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mieke tondiki otaęž‰ paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kone epeao paeyaenaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ panisi pinaęž‰ dipula mea lopaeyekeme.
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ do onkolumaęž‰ pi lo aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ yankekenaęž‰ hoke hau pimiki ekimanu ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka hepeni halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Kini halimaęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ kone iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone pilieke leekeme.
\c 19
\s1 Tooli kaęž‰taalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 10ęž‰1-12)
\p 
\v 1 Koto piekeeki manunaęž‰ pimanu la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili kenke minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ mo Diodani ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ wieke Diudia kenke nane peekeme.
\v 2 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea pemekeme. Kutu pimikitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke yenimanu paeyao epeawayekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki tamuluekemaęž‰ yeke ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa lemekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kiaaso yokaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Lo Pi Ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ waleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ wialaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande wandaęž‰hali kini peao Wepieke Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ hali pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo wepiekeme laęž‰laęž‰ Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰pa alemepe.
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ koto hali wandaęž‰ yaapo wepieke pitaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hali pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo wepueke handaataęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni peaataęž‰ tooli homeke halipipikie leekeme.
\v 6 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ yaapo na halo pelepepate otaęž‰ homeke halipipikie. Koto paęž‰leke handaataęž‰ koto hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni peawaasaęž‰ hau yeleketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na kaęž‰taapeke alee leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ koto Yesunaęž‰ pi opuolo hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Mosesi ipikaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali homeke ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kiayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kiaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Neke otaęž‰ kiao tapaasome laęž‰laęž‰ pi wape pea halaa penaęž‰ tapaapeke laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa ekipeke wape pea wia paęž‰laęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ koto piki wandaęž‰ kiao tapaasaęž‰ pi uleke wiki hautaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki otaęž‰ takaęž‰la pa paęž‰leke handolo hataęž‰ wia paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto piekepate mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali kini peayeke tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutu piki hau na piekeme.
\v 9 Kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ tooli halepeeki na hoeyaasaęž‰pate pa mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone kiao tapao wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone mo ipilikaęž‰ tooli halepeeke kaęž‰tao hoeyaasaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leekeeki opua ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tooli paęž‰taęž‰ kutu piki hau wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki pa hataęž‰taęž‰ epilieke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ mo pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do walolo pitaęž‰ pa paeyaomaęž‰ opua miniki hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mandaali epi Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ homeke opua miniki halimikie.
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ opuaęž‰pe laataęž‰ Taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki haliweki halememe. Mandane haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ kone hali atua maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pu make mandane haliwekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kiĚ±aĚ±yeke ekimaęž‰ pu make kutupa mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hone u pitolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ kiao halememe. Do pi opua miniki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ miniki haenaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ weki wandiki sunu wamo pumaęž‰ pumaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maka 10ęž‰13-16, Luku 18ęž‰15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ weki wandiki sunu Yesu ipikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ wataaso hataęž‰ yeni pinaęž‰yeke hatuku epemekeme. Kutu pimieki handolo mo ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ iki hando alo hataęž‰ tolu limikime.
\v 14 Kutu pimikipate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Weki wandikisunu make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke do weki wandikimaęž‰ handeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki anaęž‰naęž‰ handilimikie.
\v 15 Koto laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo weki wandiki manda ipikaęž‰ kiki wiaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\s1 Hamoko hayeke panake hali
\r (Maka 10ęž‰17-31, Luku 18ęž‰18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Nate homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Disao. IĚ±maęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ handoeki peonope laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo epeke hau peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke lotaęž‰ pitelepe. Mo otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ homeke homeke halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pi Ulaęž‰eki paeyao wopu telia pu hapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ Handoeki pionope leeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ na liaęž‰peke. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu na tunkulaęž‰peke. Pake na napeke. Yayapiki pi na lapeke. Makeaaso kone maęž‰ndaęž‰ maĚ±leke na liaęž‰peke.
\v 19 Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰peke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ neke nakaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ handeteke hale tupaęž‰ mo mandane mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone peaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Mo panake halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto ale pi ulaęž‰eki paeyaotaęž‰ telia pu halome. Handoeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make peonope leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke haupiki some halueke hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ wia hale alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo milipi manitaęž‰ mandane natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halehale peaęž‰peke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hepeni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ale epeke epeke wopu mu halipikie. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ya hoki teliaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Mo panake halimaęž‰ koto pi opitolotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hamoko hali tieke hayeke ekimaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ paleke peekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Kutu pieke Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hamoko wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peketaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ siki na pilieke.
\v 24 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa taa alo handaęž‰e. Mo kemolo maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ mo noĚ±iĚ± kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba yopuaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hamoko halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ miaęž‰peke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tupaęž‰ na milieke alome leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi opitolo iki otaęž‰ wopu tolaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ iki handaęž‰ hake witolo alotaęž‰ Koto hautaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone koto peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 27 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Opi. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao nakaęž‰ hoki nane teliolomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ aleke mulumaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo paa kini piliaęž‰ panake di kini piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ seliapo piki paĚ±aĚ± tiekemaęž‰ hopiliaasaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ sea manda pitiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki yaka 12 disaipolo haliweki make mo Isulainaęž‰ 12 tapake handeteke haluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki handeteke halaęž‰ sea manda pitilimikie.
\v 29 Kutaa make mo mandaali epi aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± teliolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ da o ikaęž‰ hameketiti o anaęž‰titi o apaęž‰ amaęž‰ o weki wandiki sunu o kenkemanu make minaęž‰paęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ kone mo ikaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laleme ale manutaęž‰ paa 100 tupaęž‰ lombei peao meataęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki make milimikie.
\v 30 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ame do biki tieke ulaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ wetepe haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo ame do biki na ulaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ titinaęž‰ halo yapilimikie.
\c 20
\s1 Waini pu nokepeeke enaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 1 Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰e. Nate homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mandane haliweki yenki haluekemaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ waini pu e pokaenaęž‰yeke da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki weilu peekeme.
\v 2 Mandane haliweki handaęž‰ wia ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mulupeleme manitaęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ 1 kina kulueke leekeeki opitolo haenaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ homeke hone wimiki handaataęž‰ mo e paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa mo somemaęž‰ paa 9 kolokaęž‰ tupaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mo makedi hama pua koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane e na pokaemeke haliwekimanu handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 4 Kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ya e pua pokaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ yenki otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone kulueke leekeme.
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opua e pokolo pemekeme. Mo somemaęž‰ kutu piki hautaęž‰ paa natepa pitaęž‰ tepo nate leke yaaponaęž‰ make paa piekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Welealo nate leke yunki hataęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo makedi hama paa pua mandane haliweki handeekeme. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke do natenaęž‰ nate lekemanu paeyaotaęž‰ pa paeyaaso pimipe laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yenki e pokomono maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ niki na miaęž‰me. Koto lemeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me mo ya waini pu e pua pokaape leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Nate pambolo pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande e teke halimaęž‰ mo e haliweki handeteke haenaęž‰ leeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo haliweki wi laa mombelao ikaęž‰ yenkimanu halaęž‰peke. Yenki halolo hataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ wetepe siki kini pea e pokeme haliwekinaęž‰eki ambaęž‰la kini pea halaęž‰tiki puaataęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kini pimi haliwekinaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paeyaaso hataęž‰ halaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto leeke opuaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo welealo nane nate leke yunki hataęž‰ kini pea e pokeme haliweki homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ 1 kina hale hale piekeme.
\v 10 Kutu piekeeki handaataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ da panake kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki kini pu mea pokolo pemeke haliweki ikaęž‰ yenki muluekemaęž‰ ipulutaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao kilieke hone wimikipate pa iki paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ 1 kina ombu haleekeme.
\v 11 Kutu mo wetepenaęž‰ yenki mimi haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenki meaataęž‰ mo e pokaemeke teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ tulu tulu pi wopu alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 12 Do otaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ mi haliwekitaęž‰ pa 1 aowa homekenaęž‰ e pokaemepate nikitaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso kini pea nate holiki tiekenaęž‰ poka pua welealo nanetaęž‰ naomaęž‰pate pa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale mandake piki yenki niki paęž‰taęž‰ make kiteleme lemekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Mo e teke halimaęž‰ iki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Someo laa alotaęž‰ Opie. IĚ±maęž‰ neke na makealome. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ e pokaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ 1 kina anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laa homeke hone wiki handaataęž‰
\v 14 nakaęž‰ yenki mea da pue leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ wetepe sale nane muaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ make do neke paęž‰taęž‰ kuaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone haluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 15 Ya manimaęž‰taęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone peaęž‰peke diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pe o IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ale mandaneeki pa halo halo ekinaęž‰ neketaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homelepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 16 Koto pi Yesumaęž‰ lo aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ame biki na ulaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo ame biki tieke ulaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ wetepe halo yapilimikie laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homa paa tiaapeke ekinaęž‰ tanaęž‰ tepo la haleekeeki
\r (Maka 10ęž‰32-34, Luku 18ęž‰31-34)
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ Diutuseleme potaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki homeke talo pu mea pulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 18 Opuaęž‰pe. Nikitaęž‰ ame Diutuseleme da teke nane ta opaęž‰liaasomaęž‰ handepe. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni peao haleme teke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo Lo Pi wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mea puataęž‰ homenaęž‰e laa maĚ±leke lilimikie. Kutaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki mo Diendaili haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua halimikie.
\v 19 Koto haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki kitaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ dopi tao yumbua baotaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lilimikie. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ nate tepo wiaataęž‰ paa tiao daęž‰taa halieke leekeme.
\s1 Sepedinaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ honke leekeeki
\r (Maka 10ęž‰35-45)
\p 
\v 20 Kutaataęž‰ Sepedinaęž‰ wetekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa tumiki yotuao pandaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ honke leekeme.
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ aleke hone peleke pitelepe leekeme. Koto leeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kini hali pitilipi natenaęž‰ do ya weki yaapo nakaęž‰ popeke nanemaęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ pitu make hoeyaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ pitu pinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wie leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ honke alepe ekitaęž‰ hone wotu na wiki hataęž‰ alepeme. IĚ±maęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaponaęž‰ noluaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ make napaęž‰peke yelepe leekeme. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diki anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lepekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ noluaęž‰ kaponaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ nelipipikie. Pate ya popeke nane kiki pitaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ nane kiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi pitulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ya Apaęž‰maęž‰ wamo pea tikitiki yao ulaęž‰ pilaęž‰ ale yaapotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ hali yaaponaęž‰ ekie leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Koto honke laeyekeeki mo hande mandane kiki yaapo disaipolo tonumaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankemekeme.
\v 25 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki mea mombaęž‰lao alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handelememe. Kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane wandaęž‰hali handeteke hao halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali anaęž‰naęž‰ kilu tombuao halememe. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hali tieke tiekemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Dupaęž‰pe laa pi wotu hapolo halemepate
\v 26 pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo koto hau pinaęž‰ na lelimikie. Diaęž‰me. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± tieke halueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali halieke.
\v 27 Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± titinaęž‰ hali halueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ pahameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halieke
\v 28 Pa ekipeke Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ yeke na epeeke yekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki wopunaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ yenki haluekemaęž‰ yeke epeaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ leke holupiki hali yaapo epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 29 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo tonu ameĚ±leĚ± mo Dietiko minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ iki teli mea pemekeme.
\v 30 Koto pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo potaęž‰ nepokonaęž‰ pitipiki leke holupiki hali yaapomaęž‰ Yesu yopulaęž‰me pi opipikime. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ wi alo alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekeo. Diki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e lepekeme.
\v 31 Koto lepeke handa wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰taęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pi na lapepema laa saęž‰saęž‰ pimikipate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ wi aneke hapu paa alo alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekeo. Diki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e lepekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ hando hataęž‰ wi laa alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ eki peaano alepepe leekeme.
\v 33 Mo leke holupiki hali yaapomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Dikaęž‰ leke ki laae lepekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ leke wataeyekeme. Kutu pieke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ leke ki laataęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handepekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimea pepekeme.
\c 21
\s1 Tekehali au la Diutuseleme daoni hondaęž‰ pambeekeeki
\r (Maka 11ęž‰1-11, Luku 19ęž‰28-40, Dioni 12ęž‰12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo olipi teke halaęž‰ peiyene teaęž‰naęž‰ hayeke Betepeisi da opolo epemekeme.
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo tapaaluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Oli halaęž‰ da nane opolo puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu polo hataęž‰ koto kone donki hali maęž‰naęž‰ ikiki ankulaęž‰ endi baalaęž‰eki handilipipikie. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ holaęž‰ tapao mea aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 3 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. Tekehalimaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lapaęž‰peke. Koto lepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutaa kone mea epoepenaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto pieke hautaęž‰ mo hande potopede hali homekemaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki yaaluekemaęž‰ piekeme. Koto laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ dupa.
\q1 
\v 5 Mo Saioni da teke tieke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapeke.
\q1 Ikaęž‰ kini tieketaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taa ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰pe. Ipikitaęž‰ homu piki hali hataęž‰ mo donki maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda pilaęž‰me. kutupa mo donki hali maęž‰naęž‰ ikiki manda pilaęž‰me lapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Mo hande hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ puaataęž‰
\v 7 mo donki ikiki ankulaęž‰ holaęž‰ mea Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu mo donkinaęž‰ hoki manda yamaemekeme. Kutu pimikitaęž‰ Yesu pitulu aęž‰meiyekeme.
\v 8 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu lepolonaęž‰ peolao yamomaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ pimikime. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ti palekemanu yanda peolao yamomaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 9 Kutupa mo Yesu hatuku pulu hataęž‰ titinaęž‰ hao wetepe hao pimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ wi aneke hapu kini pea laęž‰ alu alu pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Hosaęž‰naęž‰e. Deipidinaęž‰ eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰e laataęž‰ Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyamanaęž‰e
\q1 laa laęž‰tia pemekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ Diutuseleme da teke nane hondo pamba peeketaęž‰ mo daoni wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Koto ipulaęž‰ sometaęž‰ epiyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laęž‰ paleke paleke pu hando mombelemekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo ipiki hatuku epemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili kenke nane halaęž‰ da Naęž‰saęž‰tetenaęž‰ potopede hali Yesue lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeeki
\r (Maka 11ęž‰15-19, Luku 19ęž‰45-48, Dioni 2ęž‰13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande Tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hondo pambaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ hambemeke haliweki make tapaatiki pimiki haliweki iki paeyao tolu tankulupe miniekeme. Kutupataęž‰ mo mani topo pu halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ teipolomanu make mo melipu bamanu hambo haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ pitieke alemanu make hoelaęž‰ mipi baeyekeme.
\v 13 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ do pitaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰me laataęž‰ Yaka dataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yeni peaęž‰tiki pulu paęž‰laęž‰ dae lolo pelemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do dataęž‰ mo pake no halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ aęž‰mbalo peleme da haenaęž‰ alememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Ipikitaęž‰ koto Tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epemeke mandane leke holupiki wandaęž‰hali make dolaęž‰pake pieke wandaęž‰hali make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paeyao wamo peayekeme.
\v 15 Yesunaęž‰ epeke epeke haumanu piekeeki make mo wekiwandiki sunumaęž‰ Tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki daeyaluekemaęž‰ mo Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ lamanaęž‰e lemekeeki opu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make hande pi ulaęž‰eki wape pea walo halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ make mineke tieke kini pea pankolo hataęž‰
\v 16 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto wekiwandikimaęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ na opitelepe lemekeme. Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Opitolome. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo potaęž‰ pulaęž‰ o andu nalaęž‰ wekiwandiki sunu paeyaomaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taleke yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰ haumanu pinaęž‰yeke walaęž‰tiaeme laa wape pea ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe laa hombo peayekeme.
\v 17 Koto laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki make Diutuseleme da teke make minaęž‰paęž‰lao Bedani da nane polu peekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ nose ti paęž‰taęž‰ Kiliki na aęž‰elipikie leekeeki
\r (Maka 11ęž‰12-14,20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ pelia da kaęž‰laęž‰peeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Diutuseleme da teke nane pa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekepate potaęž‰naęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paleke peekeme.
\v 19 Kutu pieke pulu hataęž‰ mo potaęž‰ nepokonaęž‰ hayeke nose homeke handaataęž‰ mo ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate kiliki na aęž‰etolo hataęž‰ pa katake homeke hayekeeki handeekeme. Kutu pieke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nose paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wetepenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kilikimanu otaęž‰ pa na aęž‰elipikie leekeme. Koto leeketaęž‰ mo nose kutaa kone hapiekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Hapieke ekitaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ handaataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nosetaęž‰ ekipa aĚ±iĚ± koto kone hapua paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo nose ti paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke yelieke. Kotaęž‰ koto hau homeke diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone do pote paęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Oni ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua lopee lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo potemaęž‰ otaęž‰ pilieke.
\v 22 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ yeni pitolo honke alo alemeeki kone otaęž‰ milimikie.
\s1 Epimaęž‰ do wele kiaęž‰pe laa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikieki
\r (Maka 11ęž‰27-33, Luku 20ęž‰1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ mo Tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo haenaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you haliweki make mandane da handeteke haemeke you haliweki make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Hande pu haleeki manutaęž‰ ekieki pea pu hataęž‰ pipe kutupa make neketaęž‰ epimaęž‰ wele peaeyaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitoloeki homeke kone opua la kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo IĚ±maęž‰ pu halo hau manunaęž‰ wele peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki la kulueke.
\v 25 Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hautaęž‰ hepeni nane ekipe o kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekipe iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolome leekeme. Koto pi opuataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi dupa lemekeme. Hepeni nane ekie lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ lo hayaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ pa ekipeke na miniki haemepe lelieke lemekeme.
\v 26 Kutaa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰ Pa kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekie lolo polomaęž‰eki make do wandaęž‰hali paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke iki paeyaomaęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo hayaęž‰ halie lo halememe lemekeme.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki na handolomaęž‰me lemekeme. Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka pu halo hau manunaęž‰ wele peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ na la kulueke leekeme.
\s1 Eiyeke yaaponaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki hone witemepe. Hali homekemaęž‰ weki yaapo mondu wiekeme. Kutupataęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke weki paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ dupa leekeme. Ya wekio. Neketaęž‰ ame mo ya hande waini pu enaęž‰ e pokolo poelenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 29 Titinaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekimaęž‰ kipieke na pokolo polueke leekepate kone pa wetepenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone topo pea wiaataęž‰ paa pokolo peekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wetepe weki paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ kone pua leekeme. Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wetepe wekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ pulueke leekepate pa na pulupeke kiaeyekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa koto weki yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande atekemaęž‰ hone piekeeki peayekepe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikaęž‰ mupeke wekimaęž‰ homekee. Koto laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hande dakisi mu halaęž‰ haliweki pitaęž‰ yolo haleme tapakemaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰la oli Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pu halememe.
\v 32 Hande Dioni bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ mo leaęž‰ pi opua otaęž‰ na miniki haememe. Pate mo hande dakisi mu haleme tapake pitaęž‰ yolo haleme tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opua otaęž‰ pimikime. Kotaęž‰ koto hoke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pimi ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo handolo hataęž‰ kone wetepe ikaęž‰ hone topo pea hone na tulaememe.
\s1 Hoke haliwekimaęž‰ e handeteke haemekeeki
\r (Maka 12ęž‰1-12, Luku 20ęž‰9-19)
\p 
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ domaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opuaęž‰pe. Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenke tieke wiekeme. Koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ waini pu e pokeekeme. Kutaataęž‰ mo etaęž‰ pape piekeme. Kutupa mo waini kiliki yombu tombua bepi piaęž‰peke naku awaataęž‰ mo enaęž‰ pake nalaęž‰ hali handeteke pitepeke da hokulupeke aęž‰eliayekeme. Kutaataęž‰ mo hande etaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ yenki tieketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ hosikimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰yeke iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaa ipikitaęž‰ papate peekeme.
\v 34 Wetepenaęž‰ mo waini kiliki talemeke nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ mo hande haliwekimaęž‰ wialimi ipikaęž‰ putu piliki meaenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliweki iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 35 Kutu piekepate mo e handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ iki handaa daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ yombua bao kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lu make maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ toopimaęž‰ limikime.
\v 36 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo hande e poko halaa peeke somemaęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tapaeyeke haliweki hakaęž‰taęž‰pake e pokaemeke mandane haliweki tapaeyekeme. Kutu piekepate mo e handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandake hau ombu pimikime.
\v 37 Paeyaaso nanetaęž‰ mo hande e teke halimaęž‰ mo hande haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki iki paęž‰taęž‰ penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Ya wekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ opua pilimikie leekeme.
\v 38 Kutu piekepate mo hande e handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo hande teke halimaęž‰ tapaeyeke weki epeekeeki handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone lombolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande e tekehali ipikaęž‰ anketeke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ wekitaęž‰ koto ipulaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ lumanaęž‰e la alotaęž‰ Lumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo etaęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ e wilieke lemekeme.
\v 39 Koto laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo some daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimikime. Taęž‰nkaęž‰paęž‰ minaataęž‰ mo e tikene yolaęž‰ mea miniki puaataęž‰ lia homaemekeme leekeme.
\v 40 Koto pimanu la paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do enaęž‰ tekehali opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo e handeteke haleme haliweki iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki haumanu pealiaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 41 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke haliweki homenaęž‰ liaataęž‰ mo waini kiliki talimi natenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ eki minolo hataęž‰ putu piliki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pulu paęž‰laęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ haliekee lemekeme.
\p 
\v 42 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰pelemepe.
\q1 Mo da aęž‰eyo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Hoelaęž‰me laa kiaemeke toopi kone ametaęž‰ keneme paęž‰taęž‰ mo danaęž‰ teke toopi ulaęž‰me.
\q1 Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ kone piaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto hau nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ Baęž‰saęž‰saęž‰e. Tekehalimaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ haue alomaęž‰me
\q1 laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 43 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dupa alome. Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ kieke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paa yokaęž‰ mea mo epeke kiliki aęž‰elo paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halieke alome leekeme.
\v 44 Mo koto toopi manda lopiliaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pindi pilieke. Kutupa make mo toopimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ manda lopeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo sometaęž‰ yombua bao dokolo au lalieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo hande Yesumaęž‰ leeke onkolumaęž‰ pi opitolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Nikinaęž‰ kone alaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰
\v 46 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰ taapemekepate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ potopede hali halaęž‰me hone wimiki handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ paemekeme.
\c 22
\s1 Wandaęž‰ minolo ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Luku 14ęž‰15-24)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi manumaęž‰ paa la halolo alotaęž‰ dupa
\v 2 Mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Nate homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo kini hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hapitaęž‰laęž‰ ne pambaluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yayekeme.
\v 3 Kutupataęž‰ koto ne nolo epenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ bikimanu ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali handaęž‰ mulu paęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliweki tapaeyekepate mo hande biki wiaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke kiaemekeme.
\v 4 Kutu pimikitaęž‰ mo hande kini halimaęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ mandane e pokaemeke haliweki iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi paa pua lawape laa tapaaso alotaęž‰ Ya netaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tikitiki yaasome. Ya hali kao maęž‰naęž‰manu make imeke piki kao mandane ekimanu make lu kepa alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao tikitiki yao witolomaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipupaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Mo biki ambaęž‰ wiaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto leeke pi opemekepate pa kiao ikaęž‰ hone piekeeki taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pulu pemekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokolo peekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sidowa paęž‰taęž‰ e pokolo peekeme.
\v 6 Kutaa make mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande tapaeyeke haliweki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minaataęž‰ lumaęž‰ lumaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 7 Kutu pimikieki mo kini halimaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰ mineke tieke wopu pankeke handaa mo hande haliweki lu make ikaęž‰ da tekemanu yanko pinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ami haliweki tapaeyekeme.
\v 8 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo kini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tikitiki yao ulaęž‰pate mo hande biki ambaęž‰ wiaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰hali yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰
\v 9 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo toko potaęž‰ tieke tieke paęž‰taęž‰manu pua handilimi wandaęž‰hali paeya tapaotaęž‰ pa mo ne nolo ipupe lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 10 Koto leeke opuaataęž‰ mo e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo toko potaęž‰ tieke tiekemanu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali weiya mombaęž‰laluekemaęž‰ pemekeme. Puaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰hali epeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao mombaęž‰laotaęž‰ mo hande ne mombelemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea pemekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande Kini halinaęž‰ da otaęž‰ tumbaemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Koto aęž‰pa pitimiki wandaęž‰hali handuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kini halimaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondo pambeekeme. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ handeekepate hali homekemaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ pambaasaęž‰ akaęž‰ na pambao pitiekeeki handaęž‰ wiekeme. Kutu pieke mo kini halimaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 12 Someo. Mo hande akaęž‰ na pambaaketaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ ekipa epepe laa lotaęž‰ piekepate mo somemaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leekeme.
\v 13 Kutu pieke mo kini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto halinaęž‰ kiki anke yaapo tonkao lepe peaataęž‰ mo timbaęž‰ la pambeke paęž‰taęž‰ hama yolo lopaapaęž‰peke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake lenkene laaso hataęž‰ eĚ± wi lo haenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi lo paeyaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ wi alaęž‰pate homeke homeketaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Sisanaęž‰ dakisi mani
\r (Maka 12ęž‰13-17, Luku 20ęž‰20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesumaęž‰ leeke pi opuaataęž‰ hama nane aęž‰ndaęž‰ pua lombolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi lo hoeyaasaęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu hone pambao wimikime.
\v 16 Mo hone pambao wimiki lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi manumaęž‰ ipiki tamuluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make Hetodi ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pieke haliweki make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tapaemekeme. Koto haliweki aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu lo halaęž‰ halie. Kutaa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na u hake iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandake hau piki wandaęž‰halie laakaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi homeke walo haleme la alotaęž‰
\v 17 Nakaęž‰ wili honetaęž‰ eki hone wilipe. Niki opuomono lakiaęž‰peke. Mo kapomani tieke Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mani halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe o hoelaęž‰pe. Halomanaęž‰pe o na halomanaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Koto lemeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kekeke hake hone pambao wimikieki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaasaęž‰ haliwekie. Ya anketaęž‰ ekipeke yolaęž‰ lemepe laa la alotaęž‰
\v 19 Mo dakisi hambaęž‰laęž‰ toopi homeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰pe leekeme. Koto leeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ toopi homeke ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰pa halemekeme. Kutu pimiki handa iki paęž‰taęž‰ mea walolo alotaęž‰
\v 20 Do aĚ±oĚ± aĚ±oĚ± pitaęž‰ biki yaapotaęž‰ epinaęž‰eki kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Sisanaęž‰ ekie lemekeme. Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ alemanu meataęž‰ kotaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ kone pa mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ alemanu yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone pa mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 22 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ penkili polo hataęž‰ Yesu haenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekeme.
\s1 Homaa paa tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ pi
\r (Maka 12ęž‰18-27, Luku 20ęž‰27-40)
\p 
\v 23 Koto homeke natenaęž‰ kone pa mandane Saęž‰dusi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu ombu lotaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ epemekeme. Mo Saęž‰dusi haliwekitaęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa na tialieke lo haemeke haliwekie.
\v 24 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Mosesimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke mupeke halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ pa haenaęž‰ wekiwandiki na mendiki homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameke wetepe nane halimaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kosaęž‰ piki meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homeeke hamekenaęž‰ wekiwandiki sunu mendiaenaęž‰ lenaęž‰e laęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ watake hataęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme. Kutupa mo mupeke halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ mea hao homeekeme. Kutu piekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mondu wiki homeeke handaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ kosaęž‰ pikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki paęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ miekepate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make
\v 26 wekiwandiki na mondu wiki homeekeme. Koto some homeeketaęž‰ paa tepo peao halimaęž‰ miekepate make koto homeke hau kone piekeme. Hameke hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ watake hataęž‰ hali paeya tapao paęž‰taęž‰ koto homeke hau kone piekeme.
\v 27 Kutu peaęž‰tiki pua paelo pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ make homeekeme.
\v 28 Kutu piepate mo wandaęž‰hali paa tialimi natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haliaęž‰pe. Pa ekipeke mo hande watake hataęž‰ hali paeyaomaęž‰ mo homeke wandaęž‰ kone mimiki ekinaęž‰ alome lemekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi tieke lo hoeyaasememe. Pa ekipeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekimanu pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pu halaęž‰ ekimanu yaapo na handelememe.
\v 30 Ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paa tiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki hali na peke oli hepeni nane enisolo tapake haleme tupaęž‰ pa hao halimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa tiaalo pelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰ pitaęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 32 IĚ±taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Dieikopenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make halome laęž‰laęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ koto Kodaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ deto halo peleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ homolo peleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 33 Mo mombelemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto leeke pi opitolotaęž‰ mo pinaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke penkili polo hataęž‰ leke opo handaęž‰ hake wimikime.
\s1 Mo pi wiekeeki tieke
\r (Maka 12ęž‰28-34, Luku 10ęž‰25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ leeke pi opimiki handaa mo hande Saęž‰dusi tonumaęž‰ lapeke pi mateeke e pondo na lemekeeki handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi tonu make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pua mombelemekeme.
\v 35 Kutupataęž‰ mo Lo Pi walo hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ Yesu tamuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 36 Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paeya tapaotaęž‰ hando ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke anekepe leekeme.
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ mo pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Dihopa nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ temoko paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ hone witeleeki paeyaomaęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 38 Do alo pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mandane pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao otaęž‰ lombei piki titinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekie.
\v 39 Kutaataęž‰ mo namba 2 pi ulaęž‰eki make mandake tupaęž‰ kone dupa ulaęž‰me. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 40 Do pi ulaęž‰eki yaaponaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ pi wiekeeki paeya tapao make potopede haliwekimaęž‰ walemeke ekimanu make paeyao do titinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yaapomaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ tapake apaęž‰taęž‰ epipe
\r (Maka 12ęž‰35-37, Luku 20ęž‰41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo mombelemeke mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 42 Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eki hone witemepe. Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei hali tieketaęž‰ epipe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ tapake wekie leekeme.
\p 
\v 43 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke handaa mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ hone u tiaaso haenaęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ Tekehalie laa leekepe.
\v 44 Kotaęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\q1 Mo Dihopamaęž‰ yaka Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\q1 Nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliwekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ mea pitaaluekemaęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka popeke nane kiki nanemaęž‰ pitaęž‰peke
\q1 laa laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 45 Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yaka Tekehalie laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ pa ekipa ipikaęž‰ tapake weki haliepe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 46 Mo koto Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pieke pinaęž‰taęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peapeke na yeekeme. Kutupa koto pi la hayeke anetaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki la handuluekemaęž‰ mo lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi mandane ekimanu lapeke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ na leke paekeme.
\c 23
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo pambaęž‰ na piki hau manunaęž‰ kinki piekeeki
\r (Maka 12ęž‰38-39, Luku 11ęž‰43-46, 20ęž‰45-46)
\p 
\v 1 Koto pi wala paeyeke hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leekeme.
\v 2 Mo hande pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu walo haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make mo Paęž‰tisi tonumaęž‰ make iki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ waleeke tupaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiao walo halememe.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ waleleme manaęž‰ pimanu paeyao otaęž‰ telimea pu hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pulu pelemepate mo ikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ pu haleme haumanu homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ na hondaęž‰ mea peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ waleme pimanu kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na pu halemeke handa loaęž‰me.
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ peiyoko manda kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki alemanu tonkao tiao halemepate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kiao ikaęž‰ kiki maĚ±lekesiki tindipao maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na tambaęž‰ mea tialimikie.
\v 5 Ikaęž‰ pu haleme hau paeyaotaęž‰ pa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaenaęž‰ pu halememe. Ikaęž‰ you taado manda pokede nu dake petipekemanu wepu make kutupa mo kiki maketopaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ kone pokede nu dakemanu wepiaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi tunkula ulaęž‰ ekimanu wape pea panko hopaęž‰liao yamaataęž‰ ta pomuaęž‰tiki piteme handaęž‰e. Kutupa make ikaęž‰ dau tumiki kake ninaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao au laaseme pu honiki honiki make taa piteme handaęž‰e.
\v 6 Kutaa make mo haliwekinaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ ne pambaęž‰tiki pimiki nate ninaęž‰ make yeni da paęž‰taęž‰manu pitaęž‰tiki pimiki nate ninaęž‰ make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo you haliwekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰peke sea manunaęž‰ iki ombu mea pitatiki pinaęž‰yeke taęž‰naęž‰ wopu homo halememe.
\v 7 Makedi hama mombili ale ninaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki mandaęž‰hande pitolo ikaęž‰ bikimanu mea aęž‰meiyaluekemaęž‰ Disao. Epeke da kaęž‰laęž‰paasoe laęž‰tiki pinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homelememe.
\p 
\v 8 Mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ kutu pu halemepate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Disao pi na lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ Disataęž‰ homeke haenaęž‰ iki paeyaotaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ halememe loaęž‰me.
\v 9 Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Apaęž‰o pi na lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ homeke homeketaęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰me.
\v 10 Kutaa make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ You halie pi na lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ketiso homeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you hali halaęž‰me.
\v 11 Mandali epitaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aneke hali halo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau peao halaęž‰ hali yelieke.
\v 12 Pa ekipeke hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone IĚ±taęž‰ tumiki hali hanoe lo haliaęž‰ halitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hosiki siki haenaęž‰ lelieke. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone dekepo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ you hali haenaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyalieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ tapake yaaponaęž‰ haumanu peneme yayekeeki
\r (Maka 12ęž‰40, Luku 11ęž‰39-42,44,52, 20ęž‰47)
\p 
\v 13-14 Koto pi laa paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ eki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaęž‰laęž‰eki kiaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo poluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali puaamaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ kone mo hondaęž‰ pambolo peleme potaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake katolao halememe.
\p 
\v 15 Iki mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hande homeke hali mea ikaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ tunao haenaęž‰e laa lapeke ekinaęž‰ kone mo da yu paeyao lia lopao pomu haleme haliwekie. Kutaa mo some handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ iki mo ti to halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ eiyeke tonu halemeeki otaęž‰ lombei peao haenaęž‰ lelimikie.
\p 
\v 16 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ leke holupa potaęž‰ na handeke hataęž‰ kone Do potaęž‰naęž‰ ipupe laa lo haleme haliwekie. Ikaęž‰ waleme pi manutaęž‰ dupa Mandali epimaęž‰ mo tembolo danaęž‰ biki la alo hataęž‰ hali keke pi laęž‰ wia kone paa topo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo somemaęž‰ tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ kolonaęž‰ biki la alo hataęž‰ hali keke pi wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ topo piaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa walo halememe.
\v 17 Ikitaęž‰ leke holu piki you hoke haliwekie. Hando ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekipe. Mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pa u pelia halaęž‰ kolope o mo kolo yako peao halaęž‰ tembolo dape laa IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolome leekeme.
\v 18 Ikaęž‰ waleme pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa Mandali epimaęž‰ mo olodanaęž‰ biki la alo hataęž‰ hali keke pi laęž‰ wia kone paa topo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo somemaęž‰ mo oloda manda ulaęž‰ hotekenaęž‰ biki la alo hataęž‰ hali keke pi wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ topo piaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa walo halememe.
\v 19 Ikitaęž‰ leke holu piki haliwekie. Hando ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekipe. Mo oloda manda ulaęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ hotekepe o mo hoteke yako peaasaęž‰ olodape laa IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolome leekeme.
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mandali epimaęž‰ mo olodanaęž‰ biki laa hali keke pi wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ mo oloda make mo oloda manda ulaęž‰ ale paeyao make hali keke pi witaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 21 Koto tupaęž‰ kone hali epimaęž‰ mo tembolo danaęž‰ biki laa hali keke pi wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo tembolo da make koto tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make hali keke pi ombu witaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 22 Kutupa make hali epimaęž‰ hepeninaęž‰ biki laa hali keke pi wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kilu tumbuao halaęž‰ sea make koto seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ Hali paęž‰taęž‰ make hali keke pi ombu witaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 23 Iki mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne tende peaasaęž‰ tekiaęž‰ o paęž‰saęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale sunu kiki yaapo telipataęž‰ putupa homeke Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ taiti haluekemaęž‰ yeke epeke telipuluekemaęž‰ hone wopu u halememe. Kutu pu halemepate kone pa mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epeao epeke tupaęž‰ telipeao make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo make otaęž‰ tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make koto mo hande Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pimanu paeyao otaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰lalememe. Diaęž‰me. Kotoeki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ mo mandanekeeki make na minaęž‰paęž‰lapaęž‰peke.
\v 24 Ikitaęž‰ leke holupa potaęž‰ na handeke hataęž‰ kone do potaęž‰naęž‰ ipupe laa lo haleme haliwekie. Ikaęž‰ supumanu paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ amumu sikitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ siki talopu mea bao halemepate kone mo kemolo maęž‰naęž‰ tieke aneke kone ikaęž‰ supu tapu pa mea yolaęž‰niao halememe.
\p 
\v 25 Iki mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kawasomanu pitaęž‰ kapomanu yaaponaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nanetaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ tandepa witolo kone tukiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu pitaęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu paeyaomaęž‰ tumbulu bao ulaęž‰me.
\v 26 Iki leke holupiki Paęž‰tisi haliwekio. Titinaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ kapo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ talaęž‰laęž‰ hoke ale ambaęž‰la tandaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo kaponaęž‰ manda make anaęž‰naęž‰ tandaęž‰pa wilieke.
\p 
\v 27 Iki mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikitaęž‰ mo hama nane otaęž‰ hakepiki maęž‰naęž‰ kenke lialaęž‰ hali lapaęž‰da tupaęž‰ halememe. Koto hali lapaęž‰da manutaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nanetaęž‰ epeke hau pea hake pea ulaęž‰pate tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali toko tandepeke holiki manumaęž‰ tumbao u halaęž‰me.
\v 28 Koto hali lapaęž‰da tupaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ piteme hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pu halaęž‰ haliweki leke halemepate oni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ makea makea hau make hoke hoke hau manumaęž‰ make tumbulu baalememe.
\p 
\v 29 Iki mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki walo haleme haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make iki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki tieke ipuleke handolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ hoke makeaaso yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ homemeke potopede hali manunaęž‰ lapaęž‰ mandataęž‰ epeke toopi da siki aęž‰eyo make mo ambaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pu hao homemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ nimina tiaasaęž‰ aęž‰emeke pa halaęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ au laaso ombu hao halememe.
\v 30 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Mo hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei tonu haemeke tomaęž‰naęž‰ haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande potopede haliweki lia homaemaęž‰ tupaęž‰ na liaęž‰tiki pulu pumaęž‰me laa lo halememe.
\v 31 Koto pi aleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone mo potopede tonu limiki haliwekinaęž‰ tapake weki wandiki halemeeki peneme yaasememe.
\v 32 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei tonumaęž‰ kini pimiki hoke hau manumaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paa paeyaapaęž‰peke.
\v 33 Ikitaęž‰ keto manunaęž‰ eiyeke tonu kone keto halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki mo ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ pomenaęž‰ tapaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekieki pa wendulumeke hone wilimipe.
\p 
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi alome. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane potopede haliweki make mandane hone wotu ulaęž‰ haliweki make mo yaka pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimanu make iki ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰ tapaalo polopate mandane haliwekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ lu bao make mandane haliwekitaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ lu endialimikie. Kutaataęž‰ mandane haliwekitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ yeni pu haleme da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ yombua baalimikie. Kutupa mandane haliwekitaęž‰ da teke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ yokaataęž‰ da teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yoka paęž‰naęž‰ tolu liaęž‰tiki pilimikie.
\v 35 Kutu pilimi ekinaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa alome. Mo hande hoke hau na pimiki epeke wandaęž‰hali paeya tapao pa pahameke limiki ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ iki nane laęž‰ mea lopaalieke. Koto alo ekitaęž‰ mo hande hoke hau na pieke Eipolo paęž‰taęž‰ kini pu mea lu tiki puaataęž‰ mo hande ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tembolo da oloda yaapo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ limiki Betaęž‰kiaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke Sekataiya litolo lunaimeke ekinaęž‰ alome.
\v 36 IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mo hande pa hameke limikieki paeyaonaęž‰ hoke yenki paeyaotaęž‰ do ame haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme daoninaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Luku 13ęž‰34-35)
\p 
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme Diutuselemeo. Aęž‰taęž‰ tiekee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto paeyao mo potopede haliweki liaęž‰tiki liaęž‰tiki pu make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi mea epenaęž‰ tapaeyeke haliweki make toopimaęž‰ lu haleme. Hoto paeyao mo hande kokaęž‰laęž‰ inkiki ipikaęž‰ popakemaęž‰ ikikimanu pankaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make nakaęž‰ wekiwandiki ya kikimaęž‰ hapisaęž‰ pu halopate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kiao haleme.
\v 38 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ dataęž‰ hankoko taa paęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e.
\v 39 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame do anetaęž‰ IĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na handolo pelepate pa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ biki mea ipulaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰e lelipi tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± pa handilipikie alome leekeme.
\c 24
\s1 Mo tembolo da hoeyaapeke ekinaęž‰ leekeeki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰1-2, Luku 21ęž‰5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do tembolo da aęž‰eleme tupaęž‰ aęž‰pa handaęž‰e lemekepate
\v 2 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do da aęž‰elaęž‰ alemanu paeyao handelemepe. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do toopi epeke tupaęž‰ atula atula pea uleke handolomaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na wilieke. Koto toopi otaęž‰ paeya tapaotaęž‰ mea holao tankulupu bao aneya moneya pea wilieke alome leekeme.
\s1 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu ipilieke leekeeki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰3-13, Luku 21ęž‰7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Olipi pote manda pitinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰mbao lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande le pitaęž‰ handimaęž‰ opolo ipiliaęž‰pe. Kutaa mo nakaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epolo peleeki pitaęž‰ do yu ya paelo paęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo telipinaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰liaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ eki patehau piliaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ niki waliaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki pa tupaęž‰ hatuku puaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke.
\v 5 Hali wopumaęž‰ ya biki laęž‰ paleke ipulu alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketisoe lelimikie. Koto lelimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu makealimikie alome.
\v 6 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tiekemanu pitaęž‰laęž‰me lelimi otaęž‰ pimanu make pa hameke pi lelimi ekimanu make wopu opulu pelemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa pomomaęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupiki hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo yu ya paelo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ patehau diaęž‰me.
\v 7 Kenke homekenaęž‰ ami tiao pua kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ami tapu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Mo kini hali homekenaęž‰ ami tiao kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ami tapu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Kutu piliaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kenke yu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ki pambo make yu momeni tiekemanu make opolo ipilieke.
\v 8 Kutu piki patehau manutaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰naęž‰ weki hoki kini pea nalaęž‰eki mandaęž‰ pilieke.
\p 
\v 9 Koto haumanu piliaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu ku make lu puluekemaęž‰ iki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minaęž‰ bepi pilimikie. Ikitaęž‰ yaeki haleme ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ iki honditi wopu pilimikie.
\v 10 Koto mandake pitaęž‰maęž‰ konetaęž‰ mandane Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone tulalemeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao kialimikie. Kutu pilimi wandaęž‰hali pua hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yankekemanu ameĚ±leĚ± honditi pu alualu pitolo ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone linaęž‰ walo aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰tiki pu alualu pilimikie.
\v 11 Koto mandake dinaęž‰ konetaęž‰ yayapiki pi walaasaęž‰ potopede haliweki wopu tiaaso hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu makealieke.
\v 12 Kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hoke haumanu opa daeyatiki peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ alupilieke.
\v 13 Kutu polo haenaęž‰ kone pa mo hone tulaasaęž‰ some epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaatiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ daęž‰ta haenaęž‰ tambaęž‰ milieke.
\v 14 Kutaataęž‰ do Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ kenke honiki honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opinaęž‰ walo pelimikie. Anaęž‰naęž‰ walo paeyaalimi tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo ipilieke.
\s1 Otaęž‰ hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ hoke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipiliekeeki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰14-23, Luku 21ęž‰20-24)
\p 
\v 15 Ambaęž‰ potopede hali Daęž‰nielemaęž‰ ipilieke laa laęž‰ wieke yeke hoke hoeyaapeke yeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ handilimikie. Koto aletaęž‰ mo hande hoke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke na yeke yako piki da pandaęž‰ tiao haliaęž‰eki handilimikie. Do wape yataęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ hone otaęž‰ wopu winaęž‰e.
\v 16 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diudia nane halo peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo potemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pindipa penaęž‰e.
\v 17 Kutupa da holunaęž‰ haliaęž‰ halimaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mea poluekemaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ na hondaęž‰ pambenaęž‰e.
\v 18 Enaęž‰ haliaęž‰ halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ dau mea poluekemaęž‰ hoki laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ neao na paęž‰naęž‰e.
\v 19 Aęž‰taęž‰e. Koto nate tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ manutaęž‰ weki pitiki wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make andu halimi wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke milimikie.
\v 20 Koto piliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kosaęž‰ki make hoto pilaęž‰ nate make na ipu pinaęž‰maęž‰ yeni wopu peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 21 Koto nate manunaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone matekeeki ipilieke. Ambaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ kini pea wepia winaęž‰ leeke dinaęž‰ kini pu mea aęž‰pa ame do halomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kutupiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handemekeme. Wetepe koto hoki nane make kutu piki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ipilieke.
\v 22 Koto natenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao homolo polomaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto nate mandane ekimanu tunkulinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ talopu maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone wiaataęž‰ koto natemanu tunkulinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 23 Koto natenaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰pe. Ketiso do ane do halaęž‰ o mo nane mo halaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 24 Yayapiki Ketisomanu make yayapiki pi laęž‰ mea halo halaęž‰ haliweki make aęž‰pa mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pa nane hatuku mea puluekemaęž‰ yeke iki makeaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰o laa makea handuluekemaęž‰ na handeke hau tieke tiekemanu make wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make walimikie.
\v 25 Iki paeyao opuaęž‰pe. Koto haumanu paeyao aĚ±iĚ± na epeke haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la kolome.
\p 
\v 26 Pa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Ei. Ipikitaęž‰ oli hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ halaęž‰me lemekaęž‰naęž‰ make koto paęž‰taęž‰ na puaęž‰peke. O pa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ pankaęž‰ pilaęž‰me lemekaęž‰naęž‰ make ikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 27 Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande ti tekele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo ya paeyao olinaęž‰ oninaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ opolo ipilieke.
\v 28 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ handopaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ hoteke lupa ulaęž‰ ale ninaęž‰taęž‰ wapukini mombolo halaęž‰me.
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paa epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰24-27, Luku 21ęž‰25-28)
\p 
\v 29 Koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu milimi natemanu paeliaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ oli natemaęž‰ timbaęž‰ lo pamba hao make sumbaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± make na pilieke. Kutaa oli yanaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu make ya nane hao hondaęž‰ papa pu lopaęž‰tiki pilieke. Kutaa oli ya nane wele peaasaęž‰ ekimanu make laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ pupa wilimikie.
\v 30 Kutu piliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ patehautaęž‰ oli yanaęž‰ peneme yaalieke. Kutu piliaęž‰eki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke lelimikie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ koa manda ha mea ipulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele wotu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make paĚ±aĚ± tieke pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make mea opolo ipiliaęž‰eki handilimikie.
\v 31 Kutu piliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ bu kanake tieke homekemaęž‰ eĚ± tieke alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli nate pambaęž‰laęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ yaapo nane make olinaęž‰ oninaęž‰ yaapo paeyaonaęž‰ haleme ipikaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mombaęž‰lawaenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo tonu tapaa tapaa pilieke.
\s1 Nose manda mu onkolumaęž‰ pi alaęž‰eki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰28-31, Luku 21ęž‰29-33)
\p 
\v 32 Nose timaęž‰ pu halaęž‰eki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ paleke adaęž‰ pea katake tindiki lia kelepeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ bapi ipuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me hone u halememe.
\v 33 Kutupa make hande loaęž‰ alemanu ipulaęž‰eki handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tekepaęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me laa potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 34 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao na homeke halimi pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ alemanu paeyao ambaęž‰ ipilieke leekeme.
\v 35 Oli ya do kenke yaapotaęž‰ paelo paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka pi lo haloeki manutaęž‰ na paelieke laa leekeme.
\s1 Mo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate leke nate yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰eki
\r (Maka 13ęž‰32-37, Luku 17ęž‰26-30,34-36)
\p 
\v 36 Kutu piliepate hande loaęž‰ nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Nate handopaęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Oli ya nane haleme enisolomanu make Eiyekemaęž‰ make na handolomaęž‰pate Atekemaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 37 Hande Noanaęž‰ natenaęž‰ pimiki tupaęž‰taęž‰ hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make mandake hau kone pilimikie.
\v 38 Ikali talaęž‰eki tieke aĚ±iĚ± na epeeke tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ne ikalimanu naęž‰moneatiki pu wandaęž‰ hapu moneatiki pu puaęž‰tiki puaataęž‰ mo Noa kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeeke dinaęž‰ naemekeme.
\v 39 Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ wetepe epolo pieke hau manutaęž‰ hone na wiki pa ikaęž‰ hone pieke haumanu puaęž‰tiki pulu haenaęž‰ hande ikali tieke taa ipulu iki paeyao handaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ mea peekeme. Mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke opolo ipulutaęž‰ koto piekeeki kone pilieke.
\v 40 Koto tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaapo halimaęž‰ homeke e pokolo halipipi alenaęž‰taęž‰ homeke hali minolotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke.
\v 41 Kutupa yaapo wandaęž‰maęž‰ palaowa dakole peaaso halipipi alenaęž‰taęž‰ homeke wandaęž‰ hondaęž‰ minolotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke.
\v 42 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ u na polu pitiki yu wia hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo ikaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ditaęž‰ iki matelememe.
\v 43 Da tekehali homekemaęž‰ pake nalaęž‰ halimaęž‰ pake noluekemaęž‰ do natenaęž‰ opolo ipilieke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da yambaęž‰laamaęž‰naęž‰ alo u na piliki paa tiao yu wia halo piaęž‰me.
\v 44 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make koto pieke tupaęž‰ kone hoto paeyao tikitiki yao hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupitaęž‰maęž‰ ipilieke hone na wilimi natenaęž‰ opolo ipilieke.
\s1 Epeke e poko hoke e poko haepeke hali yaapo
\r (Luku 12ęž‰41-48)
\p 
\v 45 Hande hone wopu wia pi wopu opua epeke e poko halaęž‰ sometaęž‰ epiyekea. Kutu piki halitaęž‰ mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme mandane haliweki handeteke hawaaso hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ nemanu otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰ mea halieke.
\v 46 Kutupa hoki nane nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hande you hali paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa mo hande e pokaenaęž‰ mea hao peaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leaęž‰ pi paeyao opua otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki piliaęž‰eki aęž‰pa handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto e pokaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa hapeke yelieke.
\v 47 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Koto you halimaęž‰ kutu piki sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeya tapao handeteke haenaęž‰ mea halieke.
\v 48 Kutu piliaęž‰pate mo e pokaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Hande ya teke halitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰lieke hone witolo hataęž‰
\v 49 ipikaęž‰ e mandake pokaaseme haliweki lu yombuaęž‰tiki pu make hoke ikali nemeke tapake ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao ne ikali naa keaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 50 kotaęž‰ koto somenaęž‰ you halitaęž‰ ipilieke hone na wiliaęž‰ nate o tikitiki na yao haliaęž‰ dinaęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 51 Epiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo you halimaęž‰ koto some mea otaęž‰ hoeyaaso hataęž‰ mo hande makeaasaęž‰ haliweki mea tapaaleke pua haleme paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki make mea lopaalieke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± tieke laa kake lenkene latiki pu halimikie.
\c 25
\s1 Kiki yaapo wandikinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto nate aęž‰ndaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ handilimikie. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kiki yaapo wandiki tonu aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰ mulu pieke hali epeeke mandaęž‰hande pea handaęž‰ mea ipuluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰sini olaęž‰pake mea mina pemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa kiki homeke wandiki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu na wimikipate pa kiki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ haemeke wandiki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu wimiki wandiki yekeme.
\v 3 Hande hone wopu na wimiki wandiki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake epeke keo mina pemekepate pa wetepenaęž‰ holaęž‰ pambaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na yupu miniki pemekeme.
\v 4 Pate hande hone wopu wimiki wandiki tonu ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake taęž‰pao paeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ iki homeke homekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake tonkaęž‰naęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰sini kanake mea miniki miniki pea pemekeme.
\v 5 Hande wandaęž‰ mulu pieke some aĚ±iĚ± na opolo epeeketaęž‰ mo hande wandiki paeyao u tondaęž‰pao u polu pitimikime.
\p 
\v 6 Kutaa butaęž‰hoki nane yopua paeyeketaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wi tieke la alotaęž‰ Hande wandaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ do ipulaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa mandaęž‰hande pipee leekeme.
\v 7 Koto leeketaęž‰ mo wandiki tonu paeyao tiao ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake lankake hondaęž‰paęž‰ bepe pimikime.
\v 8 Koto pitolo hataęž‰ mo hande hone wopu na wimiki wandiki tonumaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hone wopu wimiki asi tonu nane alotaęž‰ Asi tonuo. Nikaęž‰ olaęž‰pakemanu paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰sini paetolo hataęž‰ honiaęž‰laęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰sini maęž‰ndaęž‰ hoelaęž‰ pambaapee laa honke lemekeme.
\v 9 Koto lemekepate mo hone wopu wimiki wandiki tonumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Do kaęž‰taęž‰sinitaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki nikaęž‰eki yaaponaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ na pilieke yeke na kulumekee laataęž‰ Ikaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone mo sidowa paęž‰taęž‰manu hambolo puaęž‰paęž‰peke lemekeme.
\v 10 Koto lemeketaęž‰ hande hone wopu na wimiki wandiki tonumaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo ikaęž‰eki taęž‰taęž‰ hambuluekemaęž‰ pemekeme. Koto pemeke hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ mulu pieke some opolo epeekeme. Kutu pieke tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hone wopu wia tikitiki yao haemeke yunki hataęž‰ wandiki tonutaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰ mombelemeke paęž‰taęž‰ pua potaęž‰ poka ne no pitulu pemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mo hande kaęž‰taęž‰sini mulu peme wandiki tonu laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa potaęž‰ kilikili laaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Tekehalio. Niki aęž‰pomono potaęž‰ lombaęž‰e laa eĚ± wi lemekeme.
\v 12 Koto lemekepate mo wandaęž‰ mulu pieke halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alomaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ IĚ± wopu na handolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epi amedapee laa leekeme.
\v 13 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi lo aęž‰mbolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ikaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate di yaapo iki mateleke handaa loaęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hao hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 E pokaasaęž‰ hali teponaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Luku 19ęž‰11-27)
\p 
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nate aęž‰ndaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hepeninaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ handilimikie. Mo hamoko hali homekemaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ handeteke hawaenaęž‰ wi leekeme.
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ peaapeke ane pieke tupaęž‰ kone teli peaaso hataęž‰ homeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ 5 daoseni kinaęž‰ halo. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ 2 daoseni kinaęž‰ halo. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ 1 daoseni kinaęž‰ halo piekeme. Kutaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\v 16 Mo 5 daoseni kina mieke e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kuta kone mo manimaęž‰ e honkopu hao pokaataęž‰ 5 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ apaęž‰tao wiekeme.
\v 17 Koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone mo 2 daoseni mieke e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ koto manimaęž‰ e pokaataęž‰ 2 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ apaęž‰tao wiekeme.
\v 18 Kutupate mo hande 1 daoseni mieke e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ manitaęž‰ mea pua naku awa ti tieke paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Bapi mandaneeki hao hoki nanetaęž‰ mo e pokaemeke haliweki ikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pokaemeke emanu handomaęž‰ tialuekemaęž‰ paa epeekeme.
\v 20 Kutu pieke tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande 5 daoseni kina mieke halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa koto 5 daosenimaęž‰ e poka meayeke 5 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ You halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ 5 daoseni kipatetaęž‰ pa IĚ±maęž‰ e pokaaso hataęž‰ mealo 5 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ domaęž‰ mie leekeme.
\v 21 Koto leeke mo you halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ O neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke somee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke e tieke pokekaęž‰taęž‰me. Do hosiki kuaęž‰eki kone epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke haleketaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya e tieke handeteke hawalenaęž‰ mea halueke la alotaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo mandake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homopanaęž‰ epoe leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Koto somenaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hande 2 daoseni kina mieke halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa koto 2 daosenimaęž‰ e poka meayeke 2 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ You halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ 2 daoseni kipatetaęž‰ pa IĚ±maęž‰ e pokaaso hataęž‰ mealo 2 daoseni maęž‰ndaęž‰ domaęž‰ mie leekeme.
\v 23 Koto leeke mo you halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ O neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke somee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke e tieke pokekaęž‰taęž‰me. Do hosiki kuaęž‰eki kone epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke haleketaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya e tieke handeteke hawalenaęž‰ mea halueke la alotaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo mandake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homopanaęž‰ epoe leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa koto somenaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hande 1 daoseni kina mieke hali aęž‰pa make ipikaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ You halio. Neketaęž‰ na nokopele ale napeke no make na tande ale alenaęž‰ kilikimanu talopu hale somee. Koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ takaęž‰la papeke hali haleme hone witolo
\v 25 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ 1 daoseni kinaęž‰ kenke awa pankaęž‰ hoilu poaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande nakaęž‰ ki eki kone domaęž‰ paa mie.
\p 
\v 26 Koto leeke mo you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰ pambeke e pokaasaęž‰ hoke some yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ na noko polo ale manunaęž‰ napeke no make na tande alo ale manunaęž‰ kiliki talo halo somee hone witolo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alome.
\v 27 Kotaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu hano pa hameke kitoloeki make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao kitaęž‰laęž‰eki make kimikaęž‰naęž‰ miono ya mani mo baęž‰nkaęž‰naęž‰ wiaapeke alee leekeme.
\v 28 Koto alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo somenaęž‰ mani paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ meataęž‰ mo 10 daoseni mealaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰e.
\v 29 Pa ekipeke. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰manu ambaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki lombei pinaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ milieke. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰manu wopu na wiki natehali sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰ alesiki kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea pelieke.
\v 30 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰peke na yeke epe na piki e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ hama mo timbaęž‰ laęž‰papeke alaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yolo lopapaęž‰peke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake lenkene laaso eĚ± tieke lo halieke laa leekeme leekeme.
\s1 Paeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ pimanu
\p 
\v 31 Kutu piki onkolumaęž‰ pi lo paeyaaso hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Kenke Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ pa Kini Hali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolomanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke piki handeteke halaęž‰ biki wiki sea tieke manda pitilieke.
\v 32 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ tapake tapake paeyao ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ mombelenaęž‰ lelimikie. Kutaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sipisipi pitaęž‰ meme yaapo putupaęž‰ alu peao peliaasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali make mandake tupaęž‰ tapake yaapo putupaęž‰ alu pilieke.
\v 33 Kutaataęž‰ mo tikitiki wopu piki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ popeke nanemaęž‰ kalale haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ pa mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoe nanemaęž‰ kalale mea haenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 34 Kutu pu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Kini Halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ popeke nanemaęž‰ halimi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wamo paęž‰laęž‰eki mimiki wandaęž‰hali yeleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke kini pea wepieke tomaęž‰naęž‰ kone tikitiki yao winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ kilu tumbuao halaęž‰ kenke aęž‰pa mipee lelieke.
\v 35 Pa ekipeke IĚ± teaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± epeke tupaęž‰ punimime. IĚ±maęž‰ ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikali kiaęž‰tiki pimime. IĚ±maęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu hatuku puaęž‰tiki pimime.
\v 36 IĚ± akaęž‰ diaęž‰yeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yamatiki pimikime. IĚ±maęž‰ yeni haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hatiki pimime. Kutupa mo dipula pituaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handoloendi pimime.
\p 
\v 37 Kutupa mo tikitiki piki wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaasotaęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Tekehalio. Hando natenaęž‰ neke teaęž‰maęž‰ homeke ne kumaęž‰pe o ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeke ikali kumaęž‰pe
\v 38 o hando natenaęž‰ neke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali leke nikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu hatuku mumaęž‰pe o akaęž‰manu yamamaęž‰pe.
\v 39 Kutaa make mo neke yeni hao o dipula pitu piki handaataęž‰ hando natenaęž‰ handolo epomaęž‰pe laa lelimikie.
\p 
\v 40 Koto lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kini Halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ hombo pealieke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande ya biki na wiki kame homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki paęž‰taęž‰ pimiki epeke hau paeyaotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyao pa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kone pimime laa lelieke.
\p 
\v 41 Kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hoe nanemaęž‰ halimi wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dupa lelieke. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali yeleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± na hake minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupe laa Ikitaęž‰ mo Sadani ipikaęž‰ enisolo tonkaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ pupe laa lelieke.
\v 42 Pa ekipeke IĚ± teaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na punimime. IĚ±maęž‰ ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikali na kimime.
\v 43 IĚ±maęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali hao ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu na hatuku mimime. IĚ± akaęž‰ diaęž‰yeketaęž‰ akaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na yamaemekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ yeni hao make dipula pitu pueketaęž‰ IĚ± na handeteke haememe laa lelieke.
\p 
\v 44 Kotaęž‰ mo tapakemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaasotaęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Tekehalio. Hando natenaęž‰ neke teaęž‰maęž‰ homo o ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo o da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali hao o akaęž‰ diaęž‰ yo o yeni hao o dipula pitu koto haumanu piki handaataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke na tambaęž‰ mumaęž‰me laa lotaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰
\v 45 kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Kini Halimaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ hombo pealieke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do biki na wiki kame homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ kiaemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± kone tambaęž‰ na miki kiaememe laa lelieke.
\v 46 Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ honiki na paeyo halaęž‰ hoke yenki mu halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalieke. Pate mo tikitiki wopu piki wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ honiki na paeyo deto halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pelimikie leekeme.
\c 26
\s1 Yesu luluekemaęž‰ hone ambaęž‰ pambao wimikieki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰1-2, Luku 22ęž‰1-2, Dioni 11ęž‰45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Koto waleeke manaęž‰ pimanu paeyaaso hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ hone wilimi tupaęž‰ nate homeke hao maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Nate ipilieke. Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ endiao linaęž‰ halimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Koto pitaęž‰ kone mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki pitaęž‰ mo you haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you hali Kaiyaęž‰pasinaęž‰ da tieke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombaęž‰la pitaa
\v 4 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰mbao Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina homenaęž‰ luluekemaęž‰ hone ambaęž‰ pambao wimikime.
\v 5 Koto pea ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ne pambaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankaapaęž‰naęž‰ lemekeme.
\s1 Totopo wopu piki senisitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ younaęž‰ holaeyekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰3-9, Dioni 12ęž‰1-8)
\p 
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ Bedani da puaataęž‰ kindi yeni hayeke hali Saimononaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰
\v 7 ne nalo pitinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo homimaęž‰ handeke aęž‰laęž‰baęž‰setaęž‰ toopi kanake homeke mea epeekeme. Mo kanake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ senisi totopo pikieki seliapo pambeekeme. Koto senisitaęž‰ yenki tieke alee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo senisitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ younaęž‰ holaeyekeme.
\v 8 Kutu piekeeki mo hande disaipolo tonumaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Ekipeke do yenki tieke aletaęž‰ pa hoeyaaso pilaęž‰pe laa mineke pankemekeme.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do senisitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mani tieke mea mo natehali wandaęž‰hali wopu tambaęž‰ mulu pumaęž‰me laa lemekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leme pi Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ handaa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi na leke minaęž‰paęž‰lape. Pa ekipeke ipiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasemepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau seliapo piaęž‰me.
\v 11 Natehali wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nate paeyao iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halimikie. IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hoto paeyao na hao halueke.
\v 12 Hande senisi ya lokenaęž‰ holaeyaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± hoilu piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ potaęž‰ ambaęž‰la epeaeyaęž‰me.
\v 13 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do wandaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone winaęž‰yeke walaęž‰tiki pilimikie alome leekeme.
\s1 Diudasimaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lomba wiekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰10-11, Luku 23ęž‰3-6)
\p 
\v 14 Isekatioti hali Diudasimaęž‰ mo hande 12 disaipolo hayeke halimaęž‰ kone mo yeni peao hayeke you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua
\v 15 honke alo alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu minuemenaęž‰yeke potaęž‰ walowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aleke kilimikipe laa leekeme. Koto leeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ toopi yataęž‰pa silipa mani 30 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halemekeme.
\v 16 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu aĚ±iĚ± mininaęž‰yeke lapeke waleke epekemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ weiyekeme.
\s1 Mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ne nemekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰12-21, Luku 22ęž‰7-14,21-23, Dioni 13ęž‰21-30)
\p 
\v 17 Mo Na Pombeiyaake Palaowa Ne Pambaeyaęž‰ pitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ natenaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Nate hone uelenaęž‰yeke ne pambalumaęž‰eki noelenaęž‰yeke da hando paęž‰taęž‰ pua wamo peamonope lemekeme.
\v 18 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme daoni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ some maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua dupa lapaęž‰peke Hande Walaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Ya disaipolo haliweki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ne pambulumeke leaęž‰maęž‰ lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 19 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ mo ne pambaęž‰pekeeki tikitiki yao anaęž‰lao wimikime.
\p 
\v 20 Nate pambolo peeke handaataęž‰ Yesu make ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki 12 haliweki make mo ne noluekemaęž‰ pua mombaęž‰la pitimikime.
\v 21 Koto ne nalo pitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do tupaęž‰ leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandake pilumaęž‰ some homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± linaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombilieke laa leekeme.
\v 22 Koto leeke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto le pitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na alo pimaęž‰e otaęž‰ alome laa paeyaomaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pumaęž‰ pumaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo palaowa tenke laasopaęž‰ disi paęž‰taęž‰ dikaęž‰ kiki mandake witolopaęž‰ somemaęž‰ IĚ± linaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombilieke.
\v 24 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ Baibolonaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ homiliaęž‰pate pa Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke minaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ tiekee. Koto halitaęž‰ na mendiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeke hali Diudasimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ le pitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ lepe leeke Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto aletaa leekeme.
\s1 Tekehalinaęž‰ ne ikali teli peayekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰22-26, Luku 22ęž‰14-20, 1 Kotindi 11ęž‰23-25)
\p 
\v 26 Ne nalo pitinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Palaowa mea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Keiyae laa pindi pindi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pitolo alotaęž‰ Mea nape. Dotaęž‰ ya loke mindikie leekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa kapo homeke mea Keiyae laakaęž‰naęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale piekeme. Iki paeyaomaęž‰ do kaponaęž‰ napee laataęž‰
\v 28 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Panake pi laęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ yaka we doe. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ yaka we lopilieke laa
\v 29 iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do nalomaęž‰ waini ikali IĚ±taęž‰ paataęž‰ na neke hao wetepenaęž‰ ya Apaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ panakeeki nolumeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Kutaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ emeli maęž‰ndaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Olipi Pote paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu na handolome lolo piekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰27-31, Luku 22ęž‰31-34, Dioni 13ęž‰36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame do timba kone iki paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pelimikie. Pa ekipeke mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ mo sipisipi handeteke hao halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ lulueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo sipisipi paeyaotaęž‰ mandane mandane pindipa pomo keaalimikie
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 32 Kutu pilimipate IĚ± paa mea tiaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰la mo Kaęž‰lili nane polueke. Ikitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 33 Koto leeke Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ neke minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰ kone IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke leekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ame timba kone kokaęž‰laęž‰ eĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto tepo yaka biki ambaęž‰la hoeyaalipikie leekeme.
\v 35 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diki mandakenaęž‰ homopono leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ biki IĚ±maęž‰ na hoeyaalueke leekeme. Kutupa mo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ lemekeme.
\s1 Kesemaęž‰ni e nane Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ yeni piekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰32-42, Luku 22ęž‰39-46)
\p 
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± e maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme. Mo enaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kesemaęž‰nie. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ mo pate leke pulumaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ hando pitaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 37 Koto laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pida make Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo iki tepo hoeyaęž‰ nane hatuku peekeme. Kutu polo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ tanda tieke minolo hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 38 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolo ekimaęž‰ homeke nonopea halome. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ hataęž‰ yu wia handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 39 Hosiki mo pate leke puaataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ puki yama peliniaaso dupiki yeni piekeme. Ya Apaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do ipulaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke wopu tumbiki kapotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰ leke yokaęž‰ muelenaęž‰e laa hone paęž‰laęž‰pate ya hone paęž‰laęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Pa nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki homekee leekeme.
\v 40 Kutupataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu handeekepate mo hali tepomaęž‰ u pelimikieki handolo hataęž‰ mo Saimono paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke handaa iki tepomaęž‰ do nate leke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ yu wia handeteke hapaęž‰peke na yeaęž‰pe.
\v 41 Handeteke hataęž‰ yeni pu hapaęž‰peke. La handaęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pate ikaęž‰ loke mindikimaęž‰taęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homaa adaęž‰ adaęž‰ pea witelememe leekeme.
\v 42 Koto laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hoto yaapo peao paa pua yeni pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya Apaęž‰o. Do kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tumbiki kapo ipulaęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na yokaęž‰ mea baekaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ nono leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone peleeki peaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 43 Koto yeni pu paeyeke paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu hataęž‰ mo haliweki handeekepate pa uĚ± pelimikieki handeekeme. Kutu piki hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ uĚ± pambolo hataęž‰ piekeme.
\v 44 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ paa pua hoto tepo peao yeni pua pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ yeni pitolo leeke pimanu kone leekeme.
\v 45 Kutupiki yeni pea paeyeke ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hoto pitaęž‰ uĚ± polu pitaęž‰ pimipe. Aęž‰e handepe. Aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo hoke hau pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ mininaęž‰ alaęž‰me.
\v 46 Pomanaęž‰ tiaape. Hande IĚ± mininaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimikieki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰43-50, Luku 22ęž‰47-53, Dioni 18ęž‰3-12)
\p 
\v 47 Yesumaęž‰ koto pimanu alo haenaęž‰ kone mo hande 12 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hayeke hali Diudasitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme. Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki yaapomaęž‰ tapaemeke haliweki wopumaęž‰ Diudasi ameĚ±leĚ± kepete tieke make dolo tieke make mea miniki epemekeme.
\v 48 Mo Yesu mininaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke halimaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lombaęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pua nunu puluaęž‰ sometaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some minaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 49 Ambaęž‰ koto laa wieke tupaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki aĚ±iĚ± koto kone Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo ipulu alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ halio. Neketaęž‰ epeke timba nane laataęž‰ ipiki hopulaęž‰ mea nunu piekeme.
\v 50 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Someo. Mo nakaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ epele hautaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone pie leekeme. Koto leeketaęž‰ mo Yesu minuluekemaęž‰ epemeke haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipiki daĚ±oĚ±la miniki haemekeme.
\v 51 Kutu pimiki handaataęž‰ mo Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ kepete poneke hokulu yolaęž‰ mea mo yeni peao hayeke you halinaęž‰ pa hameke e pokao hayeke hali pokeekepate pa ipikaęž‰ katake homeke tunkulaęž‰ poka lopaeyekeme.
\v 52 Kutu pieke ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ kepete hokulutaęž‰ pao mea dake paęž‰taęž‰ pankaęž‰niae. Pa ekipeke. Kepetemaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰e laa wia hao haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone mo kepetemaęž‰ lia homaalieke.
\v 53 Ya Apaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ wi lolo polo ekitaęž‰ hone na witelepe. Koto hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ enisolo ami tapake 12 hakaęž‰taęž‰pao koto kone tapalo paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 54 Wi lolo puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa mo ambaęž‰ Baibolomaęž‰ pilieke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰ haumanu ekipa yaaliepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 55 Kutaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo ipiki minuluekemaęž‰ epemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki na opiki nono pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰ hali patemaęž‰ do kepete tieke dolo make miniki aęž‰pa pimipe. Nate wopu IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pi walo haowaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimime.
\v 56 Pate do ikanaęž‰maęž‰ piteme hau manutaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ potopede haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Baibolo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pimanu peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ pitememe leekeme.
\p Koto tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao kilipa pemekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea pemekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰53-65, Luku 22ęž‰54-55,63-71, Dioni 18ęž‰13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 57 Mo Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ hande yeni peao hayeke you hali Kaiyaęž‰pasinaęž‰ da nane hatuku pemekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki walolo haemeke haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki peaataęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ mombela pitimikime.
\v 58 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu telimea peekepatetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ na peketaęž‰ pa mo hande yeni peao hayeke you halinaęž‰ da hankepe nane hondaęž‰paęž‰ lopa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki haumanu pilimipe laa handuluekemaęž‰ mo hande potaęž‰ kake handeteke haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pitiekeme.
\v 59 Mo hande yeni peao hayeke you hali make tondiki haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make Yesu lu homaaluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ hau doe laa makeaaso hataęž‰ maĚ±leke lulu peleme haliweki weimikime.
\v 60 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ makeaasaęž‰ pimanu wopu aęž‰pa lemekepate ipiki liaęž‰peke potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handemekeme. Pate wetepenaęž‰ yaapo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tiaaso
\v 61 hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do somemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Tembolo da londaęž‰laęž‰ mina wiaataęž‰ nate teponaęž‰ paa aęž‰eyaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰ somee lepekeme.
\v 62 Kutupa mo hande yeni peao hayeke you halimaęž‰ tiao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do haliwekimaęž‰ koto neke laaseme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelipikipe laa leekeme.
\v 63 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ pi na hondaęž‰ mea leke pa hayekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ hali keke pi alo hataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lapeke la alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke Ketisope aĚ±iĚ± lakie leekeme.
\v 64 Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto aletaa leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pitiliaęž‰eki make hando ya nane koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao ipiliaęž‰eki make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hando pilimikie leekeme.
\v 65 Koto pi opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau sinkipolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ laasaęž‰ pi alaęž‰me. Ekipeke mo la kitaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa mulumaęž‰pe. Kodaęž‰ laasaęž‰ pimanu opumaęž‰me.
\v 66 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ eki hau pulumeke hone witelemepe leekeme. Mo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ hau tieke pu hoeyaalaęž‰maęž‰ lu homaenaęž‰ lape lemekeme.
\v 67 Koto laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke paęž‰taęž‰ dopi talo hataęž‰ ipiki yombimikime. Mo ipiki yombimiki haliwekimaęž‰
\v 68 alotaęž‰ Neke Ketiso yaęž‰leke handaa do neke litaęž‰laęž‰ some hombonaęž‰ bikimanu lae lemekeme.
\s1 Hoto tepo Pidamaęž‰ Yesu na handoloe leekeeki
\r (Maka 14ęž‰66-72, Luku 22ęž‰56-62, Dioni 18ęž‰15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 69 Pida mo hande da hankepe paęž‰taęž‰ pa pitolo haenaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you halinaęž‰ e pokao hayeke wandiki homekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Neke make koto Kaęž‰lili hali Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pomu haeme hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰taa leekeme.
\v 70 Koto leeke Pidamaęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ ale pitaęž‰ IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰me. Alekenaęž‰ alepe leekeme.
\v 71 Koto laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki handaa mo haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ mo hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete halinaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni halie laa leekeme.
\v 72 Pidamaęž‰ aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me la alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ koto some otaęž‰ na handolome leekeme.
\v 73 Hosiki hao hoki nanemaęž‰ mo paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake halie. Otaęž‰ alome. Mo nakaęž‰ ale pi makemaęž‰ kone niki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 74 Koto lemekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do alo pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰ alome. Ya pi loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaenaęž‰e. Koto aleme halitaęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ na handolome leekeme. Koto pi alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone kokaęž‰laęž‰ tiaeyekeme.
\v 75 Kutu pieke tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ witolo Kokaęž‰laęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na tiake haenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto tepo ya biki aęž‰mbao lo hoeyaalipikie leekeeki Pidamaęž‰ niminaeyekeme. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hama opolu bao tikene pua hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke minolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke leekeme.
\c 27
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰1, Luku 23ęž‰1-2, Dioni 18ęž‰28-32)
\p 
\v 1 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki hande yeni peao haemeke you haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu homenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ pi hoti wimikime.
\v 2 Kutaataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu mea senimaęž‰ tonkaotaęž‰ mo hande Lomaęž‰ Kapomani You hali tieke Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.
\s1 Diudasinaęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Aposolo 1ęž‰18-19)
\p 
\v 3 Yesutaęž‰ linaęž‰e laa laęž‰ wimiki pitaęž‰ mo hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke hali Diudasimaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Ekipeke puaęž‰pe laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hande mieke silipa mani 30 meataęž‰ mo hande yeni peao haemeke you haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki ikaęž‰ haemeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande hoke hau na piki some homenaęž‰ yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lomboaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoke hau polomaęž‰ leekeme. Koto leeke mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ koto pele ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰eki diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa nakaęž‰eki homekee lemekeme.
\v 5 Koto lemekeeki Diudasimaęž‰ opu haotaęž‰ hande 30 silipa mani mo tembolo da pukunaęž‰ hoelo baotaęž‰ opolu bao ipikaęž‰ kone pu naa homeekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ mo mani paa pua meataęž‰ Do manitaęž‰ pa halinaęž‰ we hake mani yaęž‰leke handaa nikaęž‰ tembolo maninaęž‰ apaęž‰taapeke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pi ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ koto manimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande toopi kawasomanu wepitaęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ mo da maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tokomanu hoiyaęž‰peke kenke winaęž‰ lomanaęž‰e laa hambemekeme.
\v 8 Koto hau pimiki ekinaęž‰ kini pu mea aęž‰pa ame make koto kenketaęž‰ We Kenkee laa biki wiekeeki pa ulaęž‰me.
\v 9 Koto pimiki hautaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hayeke potopede hali Dietemaiyamaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimanu peneme yayekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ dupa
\q1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo silipa mani 30 mimikime.
\q1 Koto manitaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hali homeke hambolo peleme yenki anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laa anaęž‰ lao wimikime.
\q1 
\v 10 Koto manimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande toopi kawasomanu wepitaęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ kenke hambemekeme.
\q1 Do alo pitaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰eki alome laa leekeme
\m laa wape pa ulaęž‰me.
\s1 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰2-5, Luku 23ęž‰3-5, Dioni 18ęž‰33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini hali halepe leekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto aletaa leekepate
\v 12 pa mo mandane yeni peao haemeke haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki wopunaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi siki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na hombo peayekeme.
\v 13 Kutu pieke handaa Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelipikipe. Nakaęž‰ hau pu haleeki paeyao do koto aleme handaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 14 Pate Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ penkili piekeme.
\s1 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu homenaęž‰e leekeeki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰6-15, Luku 23ęž‰13-25, Dioni 18ęž‰39â€”19ęž‰16)
\p 
\v 15 Lombei Pupa Yapeeke Natenaęž‰ ne pambao haemeke pitaęž‰ mo Pailedi ipikaęž‰ pu hayeke tupaęž‰ dipula pitieke hali homeke hondo da tapatiki pu hayekeme. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone pieke honke lemeke tupaęž‰ mo Lomaęž‰ Kapomani tumiki halimaęž‰ koto some tapatiki pu hayekeme.
\v 16 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo biki kende wiki hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Yesu Batabasi pitiekeme.
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao wopumaęž‰ mombaęž‰la haenaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ hande Yesu Batabasi tapanope o mo Ketiso aleme hali Yesu tapaanope leekeme.
\v 18 Pa ekipeke Pailedi ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu tumiki haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu honditi pitolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea halemeke ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ handaęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ koto leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Pailedimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ seanaęž‰ pa pitaęž‰ pelia haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wetekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi tapaeyekeme. Koto hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke ame timba upamaęž‰ handaataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke muaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ Batabasitaęž‰ tapaaso hataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ linaęž‰e lenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tiao haemekeme.
\v 21 Kutu pimikipate Pailedimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hali yaapotaęž‰ iki nanetaęž‰ hando hali kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao epenaęž‰ lonope leekeme. Koto leeke iki paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Batabasi tapae lemekeme.
\v 22 Koto pi opitolo hataęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ do Ketiso aleme hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki peonope leekeme. Koto leeke iki paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiae lemekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke. Eki hau paęž‰laęž‰pe leekepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi pa daeyao tanda pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiae laa wi alo alo haemekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Pailedimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone topo peaęž‰peke potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hande wieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ pa aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu lu alualu piaęž‰pekeeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikali meataęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tandaęž‰pa bao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do somenaęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na handeteke halomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pitelememe leekeme.
\v 25 Iki paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso doeki lemekeme. Koto halinaęž‰ wetaęž‰ nikaęž‰ biki manda make nikaęž‰ wekiwandiki paeyao manda make lopa winaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 26 Koto laataęž‰ kotaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ Batabasi kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao paęž‰naęž‰ tapa tapaeyekepate Yesutaęž‰ yombua baenaęž‰ laa aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiao homaenaęž‰ yeke ipiki iki paęž‰taęž‰ mea haleekeme.
\s1 Ami haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu ki ki taemekeeki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰16-20, Dioni 19ęž‰2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo dolo aęž‰ndeli miniki haliwekimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Kapomani tiekenaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku peeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ami tapake mandaneeki paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰pa ambulao haemekeme.
\v 28 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu holo titipili mea baotaęž‰ mo we dipiti piki nono piki dau maęž‰ndaęž‰ meataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ pambaemekeme.
\v 29 Kutupa mo tekeke hake pumanu mea panka pea you akaęž‰ tupaęž‰ wepia ipikaęž‰ younaęž‰ pambao hataęž‰ mo tumapu homeke make ipikaęž‰ popeke kiki nane mea minao pimikime. Kutaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tumiki yotuao kitaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halio. Neke pa hao hapekee laa laęž‰tiki pimikime.
\v 30 Koto laa paeyeketaęž‰ ipiki dopi to kitao make hande tumapu paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ younaęž‰ limikime.
\v 31 Koto kitaasaęž‰ haumanu pu paeyaaso hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande we dipiti piki nono piki dau londaęž‰laęž‰ meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau pa pambaenaęž‰ laataęž‰ ipiki aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homenaęž‰ endialuekemaęž‰ hatuku mea pemekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiao limikieki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰21-32, Luku 23ęž‰26-43, Dioni 19ęž‰17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ Saitini hali bikitaęž‰ Saimono mandaęž‰hande pimikime. Hande dolo aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo hali meataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mea tiawaenaęž‰ lemekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutaataęž‰ yu eli biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Kolokoda alenaęž‰ opolo epemekeme. Kolokoda alaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Hali youmaęž‰ handeke elie laa lemekeme.
\v 34 Koto alenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ waini ikali teto piki ale maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ taapunaęž‰ apaęž‰tao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ halemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pende naa handaataęž‰ kiaeyekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ Yesu tamendiaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daumanu telipaaluekemaęž‰ daisi telepo laemekeme.
\v 36 Koto telepo laa paeyeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa Yesu handeteke pitimikime.
\v 37 Mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mandaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu pimiki ekinaęž‰ teke pitaęž‰ dupa Dotaęž‰ Yesue. Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie laa wape pimikime.
\p 
\v 38 Kutaataęž‰ mo hande pake nepeke hali yaapo make Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiaemekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ popeke nane kiki nanemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ nane kiki nanemaęž‰ tamendialu pimikime.
\v 39 Potaęž‰naęž‰ lombei pu pa pa pu yapemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu ki ta ta pu amboke wankeatiki pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 40 Aha. Neketaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da hoeyao hoto teponaęž‰ pa aęž‰elo pi halie. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰pekee. Koto aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti minaęž‰paęž‰lao nakaęž‰ kone holaęž‰paęž‰niao epoe lemekeme.
\v 41 Koto mandake tupaęž‰ kone mo yeni peao hayeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make pi ulaęž‰eki walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu ki ta ta pitolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 42 Ipikitaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mea daęž‰tatiki piekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone daęž‰taapeke na yaęž‰leke pilaęž‰pe laa alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Isulai tapakenaęž‰ Kini hali diaęž‰ yekea. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti minaęž‰paęž‰lao holaęž‰paęž‰niao epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee laa hone tulaalumeke.
\v 43 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke lo hayaęž‰pate kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pe pa ame pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hando hamanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 44 Mo hande ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake tamendiaemeke pake nepeke hali yaapomaęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ kone Yesu ki ta ta pipikime.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ homolo piekeeki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰33-41, Luku 23ęž‰44-49, Dioni 19ęž‰28-30)
\p 
\v 45 Nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo kenke paeyao timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambaa puaataęž‰ nate leke tepo minolo hataęž‰ nate lekelo yopulaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ natetaęž‰ paa paĚ±aĚ± piekeme.
\v 46 Koto nate lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ wi aneke hapu alo alotaęž‰ Ilai Ilai lema saęž‰baęž‰kadani leekeme. Koto pitaęž‰ do la leekeme Ya Kodaęž‰o. Ya Kodaęž‰o. Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰laasepe laa leekeme.
\v 47 Ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opua alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pee. Elaidia wi alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 48 Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ anke hao pua waęž‰laęž‰mbimaęž‰ handeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ meataęž‰ kake liki neke waini ikali tenke lao tumba pitinaęž‰ laa tumapunaęž‰ hapulao Yesumaęž‰ dodopo lenaęž‰ halaęž‰liayekeme.
\v 49 Kutu piekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hando hapaęž‰e. Elaidiamaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰pa paęž‰taęž‰liaęž‰pe handomanaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 50 Yesumaęž‰ paa yaapo peao wi anekehapu laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ temoko tapaaliao homeekeme.
\p 
\v 51 Ipiki homeeketaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tupele pieke dautaęž‰ oli holu nanemaęž‰ sinkipaęž‰alu puniaotaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ ualu piekeme. Kutaa make yu momeni tiekemaęž‰ mo yu laęž‰maęž‰ peayeke laęž‰maęž‰ pitolotaęž‰ toopi tiekemanu make peilaęž‰ alualu piekeme.
\v 52 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mandane hali lapaęž‰ nakumanu make lumbaęž‰ pa pa pu yapeeketaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homemeke mandane Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paa daęž‰taa tiaemekeme.
\v 53 Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lapaęž‰ nakumanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pa haotaęž‰ Yesu tiaeyeke hoki nanetaęž‰ iki paeyao mo hande yako piki daoni paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ handemekeme.
\p 
\v 54 Mo hande Yesumaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ handeteke hayeke ami you hali make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke ami haliwekimaęž‰ make mo hande yumomeni make mo pieke mandane hau tonkaęž‰naęž‰ handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 55 Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make hosiki yolaęž‰ taęž‰pao hataęž‰ handeteke haemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰wekitaęž‰ Yesu Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki teli mea pominolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ muaęž‰tiki pomu haemekeme.
\v 56 Koto wandaęž‰weki ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ hande Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Meti make Diaęž‰mesi Diosepe yaaponaęž‰ inkiki Meti make Sepedinaęž‰ weteke make haemekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ toko hoimikieki
\r (Maka 15ęž‰42-47, Luku 23ęž‰50-56, Dioni 19ęž‰38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Wele wele alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰matia hali homeke hamoko hali ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Diosepe opolo epeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo hayeke some yekeme.
\v 58 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko honke laa muluekemaęž‰ mo hande Pailedi pitieke paęž‰taęž‰ pua honke leekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ami haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko koto some minaęž‰ lapee leeke handaa
\v 59 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali toko hondaęž‰ meataęž‰ panake daumaęž‰ hopaęž‰liao tonkao
\v 60 ipikaęž‰ panake awa wieke tikene damaęž‰ handeke lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua wiekeme. Koto lapaęž‰ dataęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mandaęž‰ piki toopi manda tombaęž‰la awa wieke ekie. Mo hali toko winaęž‰ laataęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ toopi homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea pete pete peatiki pua mo toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mbaataęž‰ peekeme.
\v 61 Koto some peeke nanetaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo hande Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Meti make Meti maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaataęž‰ mo hande lapaęž‰ kake nanemaęž‰ handaęž‰ moneao pitipikime.
\s1 Eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaamaęž‰naęž‰ lapaęž‰ handeteke haemekeeki
\p 
\v 62 Koto da kaęž‰laęž‰peeketaęž‰ mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pilaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande yeni peao hayeke you haliweki pitaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi tapake yaapomaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ mombaęž‰lolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 63 Hande ya pi lo hayaęž‰ somemaęž‰ pa hande hayaęž‰ dinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hoto tepo natenaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ paa mea tialieke leekeeki niminaasomaęž‰me.
\v 64 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ ami haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lapaęž‰taęž‰ hoto tepo natenaęž‰ sembepela handeteke hapaęž‰peke laa lae. Do alomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ wetepe ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ toko pake mea wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ daęž‰taa tiao paęž‰laęž‰me laapaęž‰naęž‰ yeke alomaęž‰me. Do koto tupaęž‰ lelimi ya pitaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ leaęž‰ ya pi otaęž‰ lombei pikieki laapaęž‰naęž‰ alomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 65 Koto lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Saęž‰saęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ hatuku puaataęž‰ mo hali lapaęž‰naęž‰ potaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ katolapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 66 Koto leeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pailedi minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo hali lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo lapaęž‰ kake aęž‰mbeeke toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ domamaęž‰ aęž‰mbo hopaęž‰liao paeyeketaęž‰ mo hande saęž‰saęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ laa pemekeme.
\c 28
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ paa tiao hayekeeki
\r (Maka 16ęž‰1-10, Luku 24ęž‰1-12, Dioni 20ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pitu haemeke nate (Saęž‰taęž‰de) paeyeketaęž‰ mo Sande da siki panake kaęž‰laęž‰ polo haenaęž‰ hande Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Meti make Meti maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ mo hande Yesu hoiyeke lapaęž‰ toopi apaęž‰ndaęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ mo lapaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pu alu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰
\v 2 koto kone yu momeni tieke piekeme. Kutu pieke taapunaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo homeke oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰pa hataęž‰ mo hande apaęž‰ndaęž‰ kake aęž‰mbeeke toopi londolo pete pete peaotaęž‰ mo toopi manda ipiki pitiekeme.
\v 3 Mo enisolo ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ ti tekele tekele leeke ale peaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau make hake pea yahapimaęž‰ handeekeme.
\v 4 Kutu piekeeki handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hali lapaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ paalaęž‰ tieke pitolo pututu liaaso hataęž‰ homeke toko leke wia yapemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa mo hande enisolomaęž‰ hande wandaęž‰ yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pepee. Mo hande tamendiao liaęž‰ hali Yesu handuluekemaęž‰ ipilipime hone witolome.
\v 6 Ipikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande laęž‰ wiaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone tiao paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ hande toko hoimiki lapaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ domaęž‰ aęž‰pa handaęž‰pe.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ ame do siki aĚ±iĚ± koto kone pua ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo hande naku paęž‰taęž‰ pa daęž‰taa tiao ametaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane ipiki ambaęž‰laęž‰ pulu halaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki koto paęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie lapaęž‰peke la alotaęž‰ Do la kitolo pitaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto pi lo paeyeke opuaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homaęž‰peke patetaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke make homaęž‰ paleke aĚ±iĚ± koto kone mo lapaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo disaipolo tonu paęž‰taęž‰ la haluekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± aĚ±iĚ±ya pepekeme.
\v 9 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pimanu loluekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pepekepate potaęž‰ hopikinaęž‰ penkilipao Yesu mandaęž‰hande pipikime. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epeke da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso leekeme. Ipiliki Yesu tekepaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ howa lopolo pandaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ ipikinaęž‰ pi laepekeme.
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke pua mo hande ya kame tonu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Oli Kaęž‰lili nane puaataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie leaęž‰me laa lawapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Lapaęž‰ yu pamba haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pua lemekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Koto wandaęž‰ yaapo laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande lapaęž‰ handeteke haemeke mandane ami haliwekimaęž‰ mo hande Diutuseleme daoni nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰ hande yeni peao hayeke you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande pieke yeke hau paeyao la halemekeme.
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you haliwekimaęž‰ koto lemeke pimanu opuaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande tondiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mombelemekeme. Kotaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pi hotu tikitiki yaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande lapaęž‰ yu pamba haemeke ami haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mani tieke aneke halolo
\v 13 alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ dupa lelimikie. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ u polumaęž‰ nane ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki aęž‰pa hande toko pake mea pelememe lelimikie.
\v 14 Kutupa koto lelimi pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo Kapomani tiekemaęž‰ opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau na peleme ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pua la halumekemaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke lemekeme.
\v 15 Hande ami haliwekimaęž‰ mo mani meataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰peke laa la haleeke tupaęž‰ kone pua laęž‰tia tia pimikime. Kutu pimiki handaataęž‰ koto pitaęž‰maęž‰ kini pu meataęž‰ ame do make mo Diu tapake tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koto pi kone paa laęž‰ alualu pu halememe.
\s1 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo tonu paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao opolo peekeeki
\r (Maka 16ęž‰14-18, Luku 24ęž‰36-49, Dioni 20ęž‰19-23, Aposolo 1ęž‰6-8)
\p 
\v 16 Hande 11 disaipolo haliwekitaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili opolo puaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Puaęž‰pekee laa ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke peiyene paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 17 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hosiki pa pate leke hayekeeki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikinaęž‰ pi laemekeme. Pate mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hone yaapo wimikime.
\v 18 Yesumaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo ipulu iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hepeni handeteke hapeke wele make do kenke handeteke hapeke wele make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ya disaipolo haenaęž‰ mea hamenaęž‰ kenke honiki honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰tia pu hapaęž‰peke. Koto ya disaipolo halimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ make Ya bikinaęž‰ make mo Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ make bapitaisi hau peao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 20 Kutaa make hande IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuaęž‰ pimanu paeyaotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ miniki hataęž‰ tolu haenaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke. IĚ±taęž‰ mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kiaęž‰ naluekemaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± nate paeyao mandake hao halumeke leekeme. 
